NK106(me)010:1: // ma h+aa sa n+d+hi m+aa y+aa bi sh+r+aa n+ta s+ya
NK106(me)010:2: bri t+t+ai ra tha pha la n+aa ma bi dza
NK106(me)010:3: h+aa ram /// rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal
NK106(me)010:4: gso'i 'grel pa shing rta bzang po zhes bya ba
NK106(me)010:5: h+aa ram /// bzhugs so // rgya gar skad du /
NK106(me)010:6: ma h+aa san+d+hi m+aa y+aa bi sh+r+aan+ta s+ya brit+ti ra tha pha la n+aa ma /
NK106(me)010:8: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso'i 'grel pa shing rta bzang po zhes bya ba /
NK106(me)010:9: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)010:10: gdod nas byang chub chos sku dag pa las //
NK106(me)010:11: mdzad pa'i rnam 'phrul sgyu ma'i skur bzhengs pa //
NK106(me)010:12: 'jig rten gsum mgon chos rje bla ma dang //
NK106(me)010:13: rgyal ba sras bcas gus pa'i gtsug gis mchod //
NK106(me)010:14: gdul bya'i khams dang 'dul byed dbye ba las //
NK106(me)010:15: theg pa'i rnam grangs dpag tu med kun gyi //
NK106(me)010:16: snying por gyur pa 'od gsal sgyu ma nyid //
NK106(me)010:17: shing rta bzang po'i 'grel 'dis rab gsal bya //
NK106(me)010:18: gang gi tshe thugs rje rmad du byung ba'i 'od
NK106(me)010:19: zer gyis mtha' yas pa'i 'jig rten du sgron ma
NK106(me)010:21: ma rig pa'i mun pa thams cad bsal ba las /
NK106(me)010:22: zhing 'dir yang phyi dang nang gi ston pa bcom
NK106(me)010:23: ldan 'das stong la sogs pas chos kyi phung po
NK106(me)010:24: dpag tu med pa gsungs pa dag gi mchog ni
NK106(me)010:25: / theg pa chen po bla na med pa'i tshul rgya mtsho sgrogs pa las /
NK106(me)010:26: zab mo snying po gcig tu bsdus nas nyams su len pa la phyogs nges par sbyar na /
NK106(me)010:27: sgyu ma'i tshul rnam pa gnyis dpe brgyad kyis go rims nges pas rnal 'byor dus gsungs te /
NK106(me)010:28: de'i man ngag gi gnad nges pa rnams rang bzhin
NK106(me)010:29: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs sgyu ma
NK106(me)010:30: ngal gso zhes bya bar gtan la phab pa las
NK106(me)010:31: / 'dir yang de'i rnam par dbye ba don gyis 'grel pa'i gnad nges pa las /
NK106(me)010:32: re zhig dang po phyag gis mchod par brjod pa ni /
NK106(me)010:33: chos kun ma skyes mnyam pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK106(me)010:34: ye shes sgyu ma gnyis med rol pa che //
NK106(me)010:35: sems nyid rgyal po rang byung gdod ma la //
NK106(me)010:36: ma skyes 'du 'bral med pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)010:38: tshigs su bcad pa 'di ni bstan bcos 'di'i rdo rje'i lus rnam par gzhag pa yin te /
NK106(me)010:39: so so rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK106(me)010:40: khams bde gshegs pa'i snying po ni 'khor ba dang
NK106(me)010:41: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi dbyings
NK106(me)010:42: sam 'byung gnas dam pa yin te /
NK106(me)010:43: 'phags pa lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:44: thog ma med pa dus kyi dbyings //
NK106(me)010:45: chos rnams kun gyi gnas yin te //
NK106(me)010:47: mya ngan 'das pa thob pa yin //
NK106(me)010:49: 'di'i ngo bo ni rang bzhin gyi skye ba med pa dang /
NK106(me)010:53: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes smra bsam brjod pa
NK106(me)010:54: las 'das pa so so rang gi rig pa don
NK106(me)010:56: sgra gcan 'dzin gyi yum la bstod pa las kyang /
NK106(me)010:57: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK106(me)010:58: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK106(me)010:59: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK106(me)010:60: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)010:62: 'di nyid gang gi ngo bor yang ma grub la /
NK106(me)010:65: sems nyid gcig pu kun gyi sa bon te //
NK106(me)010:66: gang la srid kyang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK106(me)010:67: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu ster bar byed pa yi //
NK106(me)010:68: yid bzhin nor 'dra'i sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)010:70: de ltar phyag gi rjes la bstan bcos brtsam par dam bca' ba ni /
NK106(me)010:71: rgyal bas chos kun sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK106(me)010:72: yang dag gsung de rang bzhin rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:73: mdo rgyud man ngag snying po'i bcud bsdus te //
NK106(me)010:74: ji ltar nyams su myong bzhin bshad kyis nyon //
NK106(me)010:76: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snang la
NK106(me)010:77: rang bzhin med pa sgyu ma lta bur gsungs te
NK106(me)010:78: / yum bar ma las rab 'byor chos thams cad ni rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)010:79: mya ngan las 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)010:80: mya ngan las 'das pa las ches lhag pa'i chos
NK106(me)010:81: shig yod na de yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu
NK106(me)010:82: ma lta bu'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:83: sgyu ma mkhan rab tu bzang pos zhus pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK106(me)010:84: bzang pos chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK106(me)010:85: sgyu ma lta bur shes par bgyi //
NK106(me)010:87: de la 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ni sems la
NK106(me)010:88: snang zhing sems kyi bag chags mthu brtas pa'i phyir
NK106(me)010:90: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad ni ye
NK106(me)010:91: shes la snang zhing rig pa'i rang mdangs sku dang
NK106(me)010:92: ye shes kyi snang ba dang /
NK106(me)010:93: lhun gyis grub la dngos po dang mtshan ma'i chos
NK106(me)010:94: las 'das pa'i phyir yang dag sgyu ma zhes bya'o
NK106(me)010:95: // ji skad du'ang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:96: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK106(me)010:97: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan med de //
NK106(me)010:98: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid tshul //
NK106(me)010:100: de dag gis dang po bstan bcos la 'jug pa'i rgyu bstan zin to //
NK106(me)010:101: da ni 'jug yul bstan bcos kyi lus nyid bshad pa la rdo rje'i gnas rnam pa brgyad las /
NK106(me)010:102: dang por chos thams cad rmi lam lta bur snang
NK106(me)010:103: la rang bzhin med pas gtan la dbab par bya
NK106(me)010:104: ba las / gzhi snang la rang bzhin med pa
NK106(me)010:105: gcig dang du ma'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK106(me)010:106: chos kyi dbyings dam par lta bas thag bcad pa
NK106(me)010:107: ba las / ni / gzhi dbyings mi 'gyur sems nyid nam mkha' che //
NK106(me)010:108: stong gsal spros dang bral ba'i ngang nyid las //
NK106(me)010:109: rgyal chos dri med nyi zla gza' skar bzhin //
NK106(me)010:110: lhun grub sku gsum ye shes 'du 'bral med //
NK106(me)010:111: ngang gis 'od gsal yon tan rdzogs par ldan //
NK106(me)010:112: 'di ni rang bzhin gdod ma'i gnas lugs te //
NK106(me)010:113: gang dag gzhi yi sgyu ma lags par gsung //
NK106(me)010:114: de la 'khor 'das kyi sgyu ma'i 'byung gzhi ni
NK106(me)010:115: rig pa byang chub kyi sems ye nas 'od gsal
NK106(me)010:116: ba bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po yin la /
NK106(me)010:117: de'i ngo bo stong pas nam mkha' lta bu /
NK106(me)010:118: rang bzhin gsal bas nyi zla lta bu /
NK106(me)010:119: thugs rje 'char gzhir gnas pas me long dngas pa'i ngos lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:120: de lta bu'i ngang nas sku dang ye shes kyi
NK106(me)010:121: chos thams cad lhun grub ye shes chen po dbyings
NK106(me)010:122: de'i yon tan du ye nas yod pa ni /
NK106(me)010:123: nam mkha'i dbyings na nyi zla gza' skar yod pa lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:125: dbyings de'i ngo bo ni nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:126: rang bzhin ni ngang gis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK106(me)010:127: thugs rje ni rigs pa'i snying por gnas te yon
NK106(me)010:128: tan thams cad kyi 'char gzhir gyur pa'o zhes so
NK106(me)010:130: ma'i 'od gsal snying po yang dag dbyings kyi sgyu
NK106(me)010:131: // ma zhes pa'o // gzhi de lta bu la sems can du 'khrul tshul ni /
NK106(me)010:132: de nyid ngang las glo bur 'khrul pa'i sprin //
NK106(me)010:133: rmi lam byed po gnyid kyi ngang tshul can //
NK106(me)010:134: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig nyid dang ni //
NK106(me)010:135: gnyis med gnyis su 'dzin pas bslad pa'i sems //
NK106(me)010:136: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig las byung bas //
NK106(me)010:137: 'gro drug 'khrul snang sna tshogs rmi lam bzhin //
NK106(me)010:138: de la skyes bu gnyid du song ste bde sdug
NK106(me)010:139: gi rmi lam 'char ba yang 'char gzhi'i dbyings rig
NK106(me)010:140: pa la rkyen gnyid du song bas byas dus /
NK106(me)010:141: bag chags kyi rmi lam du 'khrul nas med pa
NK106(me)010:142: gsal snang gi snang ba la so sor spyod cing
NK106(me)010:143: zhen pa ltar / thog ma'i dbyings 'od gsal ba'i ngang las /
NK106(me)010:144: gzhi snang yul du shar dus /
NK106(me)010:145: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang bsgribs te /
NK106(me)010:146: rang snang du ma shes pas /
NK106(me)010:147: kun brtags pa'i ma rig pa'i gnyis su bzung ba'i dbang gis dpyod med gzugs /
NK106(me)010:148: 'dzin du mched pas 'gro drug so so'i 'khrul snang rmi lam dang 'dra bar shar te /
NK106(me)010:149: sems can tha ma ngan song gsum dang /
NK106(me)010:151: chen po gzugs dang gzugs med pa ltar 'khor ba ni /
NK106(me)010:152: 'phags pa yon tan rin po che sdud pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:153: sems can tha ma 'bring dang mchog gyur ji snyed pa //
NK106(me)010:154: de kun ma rig las byung bde bar gshegs pas gsungs //
NK106(me)010:157: gnyid dang 'dra ba'i ma rig pa kun du rtog pa dang bcas pas myos pa'i dbang gis /
NK106(me)010:158: da lta 'khrul snang khams gsum gyi snang ba rmi lam ltar shar te /
NK106(me)010:160: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las //
NK106(me)010:161: rang gi rnam rtog las kyi sprul //
NK106(me)010:162: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK106(me)010:163: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:165: de lta bu'i snang tshul ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK106(me)010:166: med bzhin snang la bde sdug so sor myong //
NK106(me)010:167: yun ring dus nas goms pa 'di dag kun //
NK106(me)010:168: gnas dang lus dang longs spyod la sogs pa //
NK106(me)010:169: rang snang dge sdig las gyur bde sdug bsngal //
NK106(me)010:170: rnam pa sna tshogs ri mo bris 'dra ba //
NK106(me)010:171: gcig nyid 'khrul las mang por snang gyur te //
NK106(me)010:172: du mar gzung las 'khrul snang rgyun mi chad //
NK106(me)010:173: e ma srid pa'i rang bzhin rmi lam bzhin //
NK106(me)010:174: 'di ltar snang srid kyi chos thams cad med pa
NK106(me)010:175: gsal snang la bden par zhen pa'i bag chags mthu
NK106(me)010:176: brtas pas / 'gro drug so so la rang rang
NK106(me)010:177: gi gnas dang lus dang longs spyod dang bde sdug
NK106(me)010:178: sna tshogs su snang ba ste /
NK106(me)010:179: de yang sems gcig nyid dge sdig gi las tha
NK106(me)010:180: dad kyi byed pas 'khrul snang mang por snang ste
NK106(me)010:181: / snang ba la bdag tu bzung bas 'khor ba gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa ni /
NK106(me)010:182: rmi lam lta bu'i las sna tshogs shes pas rmi
NK106(me)010:183: lam ltar gyur pa'i snang ba las gzhan med de
NK106(me)010:185: 'gro ba rmi lam lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:186: de bzhin las ni rmi lam bzhin //
NK106(me)010:187: byed po nye bar len pa rnams //
NK106(me)010:188: thams cad rmi lam 'dra ba yin //
NK106(me)010:190: de lta bu'i 'khrul pa'i snang ba las don gzhan pa cung zad kyang med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:191: rang byung sems nyid gcig gi ngo bo la /
NK106(me)010:192: ma rig gnyid kyis 'khrul snang gzung 'dzin blo //
NK106(me)010:193: sna tshogs mang ldan rmi lam snang ba 'di //
NK106(me)010:194: rang sems nyid las gzhan du ci yang med //
NK106(me)010:195: log rtog sgyu ma nyid ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK106(me)010:196: rig pa gzung 'dzin gyi gnyid du dar cig log pa las /
NK106(me)010:197: 'gro drug gi rmi lam shar tsam las 'khor ba'i
NK106(me)010:198: 'khrul snang ba'i bden pa'i chos phyi nang gang na'ang
NK106(me)010:199: grub pa rdul tsam yang med /
NK106(me)010:201: don yod ma yin sems nyid de //
NK106(me)010:202: bag chags kyis ni 'khrul pa'i sems //
NK106(me)010:203: don du rab tu snang ba 'byung //
NK106(me)010:204: phyi rol don mthong log pa yin //
NK106(me)010:207: kye rgyal ba'i sras dag khams gsum po 'di dag ni sems tsam mo zhes so //
NK106(me)010:208: kha cig lung 'di la 'khrul nas snod bcud thams
NK106(me)010:209: cad rang gi sems su 'dod pa ni lung 'di'i
NK106(me)010:211: 'dis ni phyi rol gyi snang ba rang sems la
NK106(me)010:212: snang ba tsam las don gzhan du ma grub ces
NK106(me)010:213: gsungs pa dang / khams gsum po yang rang snang
NK106(me)010:214: so so ba'i snang bar sems snang mthun pa tsam
NK106(me)010:215: gsungs pa dang / las / don gzhan ma grub par bstan to //
NK106(me)010:216: dgos pa ni nyan thos pa kha cig phyi rol
NK106(me)010:217: bems po rang mtshan la sogs pa don gzhan bden
NK106(me)010:218: par 'dod pa bkag pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK106(me)010:219: gal te thams cad rang sems yin na /
NK106(me)010:221: gcig grol bas kun grol ba dang /
NK106(me)010:222: 'gro ba ril shes rgyud gcig pa dang /
NK106(me)010:223: skyes pa'am bud med lta bu gcig las mi srid pa dang /
NK106(me)010:224: rang sems kyis yul rig cing 'jal ba ltar yul
NK106(me)010:225: gyis sems 'jal bar thal ba la sogs pa shing
NK106(me)010:226: rta chen por bstan pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:227: des na 'dir ni phyi rol dkar dmar du snang ba thams cad sems la snang ba tsam las /
NK106(me)010:228: sems dang sems las don gzhan bems po la sogs par grub pa ci yang med pas /
NK106(me)010:229: med bzhin snang ba'i rmi lam dang 'dra bar bstan pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:230: mdor na sems kyi 'khrul snang thams cad log rtog sgyu ma zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:232: sna tshogs rang sems snang ba kun //
NK106(me)010:233: log rtog sgyu ma nyid ces brjod //
NK106(me)010:235: de ltar 'khrul par snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin med pa'i dpe nye bar dgod pa ni /
NK106(me)010:236: ji ltar d+ha du ra yis myos pa la //
NK106(me)010:237: snang ba sna tshogs snang yang 'khrul par gcig /
NK106(me)010:238: de bzhin ma rig gnyid myos las byung ba'i //
NK106(me)010:239: 'gro drug sems 'khrul ba la snang ba 'di //
NK106(me)010:240: bden pa med ces de ring rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:241: 'ga' zhig d+ha du ra zos pa'i snang ba ni
NK106(me)010:242: 'jig rten pas kyang bden med du byed pa ltar
NK106(me)010:243: 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang 'di yang ma rig pa'i gnyid
NK106(me)010:245: bden pa med pa la snang bar ma 'gags pa
NK106(me)010:246: tsam mo zhes mkhas pa rnams kyis shes par bya
NK106(me)010:247: ste / 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:248: ji ltar bu mo gzhon nu'i rmi lam na //
NK106(me)010:249: bu pho byung zhing shi ba de mthong nas //
NK106(me)010:250: byung na dga' zhing shi na mi dga' ltar //
NK106(me)010:251: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:253: khye'u rab snang gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:254: gang tshe sna tshogs chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:255: rang bzhin gyis ni ma skyes pa //
NK106(me)010:256: rmi lam bzhin du dngos med de //
NK106(me)010:257: dngos po rnams dang bral ba yin //
NK106(me)010:259: de ltar rmi lam dang 'dra ba'i chos rnams dang
NK106(me)010:260: po'i gzhi la nam mkha' lta bur la bzla ba
NK106(me)010:261: ni / 'khrul snang 'khrul 'dzin 'khrul rtog las byung bas //
NK106(me)010:262: bden med rdzun med gnyis med blo 'das zhes //
NK106(me)010:263: nges par rang rig rang byung zhes bya ste //
NK106(me)010:264: yin min yod min mtha' grol klong yangs su //
NK106(me)010:265: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mkha' ltar shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:266: 'di ltar 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang thams cad 'khrul dzin gyi bag chags brtas pa las byung la /
NK106(me)010:267: de yang 'khrul rtog skad cig ma'i rgyun 'grel pa las byung ste /
NK106(me)010:268: phung po khams dang skye mched la sogs pa'i snang
NK106(me)010:269: ba'i rtsa ba las dang nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin
NK106(me)010:270: tshul bzhin ma yin pa yid la byed pa'i sems
NK106(me)010:271: ni / sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu la thug pas gang du'ang ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:272: thog ma'i gzhi la byin pa ni /
NK106(me)010:274: sa ni chu la chu rlung la //
NK106(me)010:275: rlung ni nam mkha' la rab gnas //
NK106(me)010:276: mkha' ni rlung dang chu dag dang //
NK106(me)010:277: sa yi khams la gnas ma yin //
NK106(me)010:278: de bzhin phung po khams dbang rnams //
NK106(me)010:279: las dang nyon mongs dag la brten //
NK106(me)010:280: las dang nyon mongs tshul bzhin min //
NK106(me)010:281: tshul bzhin ma yin yid byed ni //
NK106(me)010:282: sems kyi dag pa la rab gnas /
NK106(me)010:283: sems kyi rang bzhin chos rnams ni //
NK106(me)010:284: thams cad la yang gnas ma yin //
NK106(me)010:286: de ltar snang la rang bzhin med pa'i 'khor ba
NK106(me)010:287: ye nas dag mnyam nam mkha' lta bur bstan pa
NK106(me)010:288: ni / chos kun rang bzhin rmi lam lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:289: snang dus nyid nas ngo bo 'ga' med la //
NK106(me)010:290: rnam pa ma dor snang ba ma 'gags shing //
NK106(me)010:291: re zhig rdzun la rnam kun stong pa'i gzugs //
NK106(me)010:292: shin tu dpyad na bden min rdzun pa min //
NK106(me)010:293: yod min med min rang bzhin mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)010:294: mkha' mnyam brjod 'das bsam yul rnams dang bral //
NK106(me)010:295: rang bzhin gdod nas dag par shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:296: snang srid kyi chos thams cad rmi lam gyi snang
NK106(me)010:297: ba ltar kun rdzob snang tsam du med pa gsal
NK106(me)010:298: snang gi stong gzugs tsam mo //
NK106(me)010:299: de yang don dam par bden rdzun dang yod med las 'das pa'i rang bzhin nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:300: de nyid ma rig pas sems can thams cad kun
NK106(me)010:301: snang med pa gsal snang la bden par zhen nas
NK106(me)010:303: spyod pa'i dus nas chos nyid la g.yos pa cung zad med pas /
NK106(me)010:304: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa chos sku nam mkha'
NK106(me)010:305: lta bu'i rang bzhin las rol pa sna tshogs su
NK106(me)010:307: dkon mchog ta la la'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:308: chos rnams thams cad bde bar gshegs dang 'dra //
NK106(me)010:309: byis pa'i blo can mtshan mar 'dzin pa rnams //
NK106(me)010:310: 'jig rten dag na med pa'i chos la spyod //
NK106(me)010:311: lta ba rnam sbyong de yis shes par 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:314: 'di ltar snang srid snod bcud chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:315: ma skyes kun byed nyid kyis don du rig /
NK106(me)010:317: rmi lam yul med kyi rang bzhin gzhi ngo bo
NK106(me)010:318: nyid kyi dag pa'i lta bar gtan la phab zin
NK106(me)010:319: to // da ni snang la rang bzhin med pa'i lam rmi lam lta bu ni /
NK106(me)010:320: de ltar snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:321: rmi lam dang 'dra lta bas thag bcad nas //
NK106(me)010:322: sgom pas nyams su blang phyir bstan pa ni //
NK106(me)010:323: bde ba'i gdan la skyil krung rab bcas nas //
NK106(me)010:324: skyabs su 'gro dang byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK106(me)010:325: chos kun mnyam rdzogs stong pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK106(me)010:326: snang ba'i sgyu ma rab tu bsgom par bya //
NK106(me)010:327: chos thams cad rmi lam ltar ngo bo nyid med par rtogs nas /
NK106(me)010:328: de'i don la mnyam par gzhag pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:329: yid dang mthun pa'i gnas su stan bde ba la skyil mo krung du 'dug ste /
NK106(me)010:330: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK106(me)010:331: sems can gyi don du byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas /
NK106(me)010:332: sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos thams cad ye nas ma skyes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:333: gnas skabs su snang ba dang /
NK106(me)010:334: snang dus nas bden pa med par mnyam pa ste /
NK106(me)010:335: thun mong du bden pa gnyis dang /
NK106(me)010:336: thun mong ma yin pa rten snod du snang ba gzhal yas khang dang /
NK106(me)010:337: brten pa bcud kyi sems can lhar mnyam pa ste /
NK106(me)010:338: mnyam pa nyid bzhis chos thams cad kun tu bzang
NK106(me)010:339: po'i dkyil 'khor snang la rang bzhin med pa rmi
NK106(me)010:340: lam dang 'dra bar bsgom pa ni /
NK106(me)010:342: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK106(me)010:343: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK106(me)010:345: de nas lam zab bla ma'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK106(me)010:346: spyi bor pad zla nyi ma'i dbus nyid du //
NK106(me)010:347: rtsa ba'i bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gror bcas //
NK106(me)010:348: brgyud pa'i bla ma dbyer med gsal btab la //
NK106(me)010:349: mchod bstod rmi lam 'byong bar gsol ba gtab //
NK106(me)010:350: bdag dang snang srid 'od zhu bla mar thim //
NK106(me)010:351: mkha' mnyam ngang der dar cig glod la bsgom //
NK106(me)010:352: de yis byin rlobs rtogs pa shugs las 'char //
NK106(me)010:353: rang nyid 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs phyag bzhi pa'i dang po gnyis thal mo sbyar ba /
NK106(me)010:354: g.yas 'og ma mu tig gi phreng ba dang /
NK106(me)010:355: g.yon pad+ma dkar po bsnams pa /
NK106(me)010:359: zhabs skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i thugs kar pad
NK106(me)010:360: zla'i dbus su h+r+aihl yi ge drug pas bskor bar
NK106(me)010:361: bsams la / snod bcud thams cad thugs rje chen po'i sku dang gsung dbyangs su grags pas /
NK106(me)010:362: ma ni pad+me h'u h+r+aih zhes brgya rtsa brjod nas /
NK106(me)010:363: spyi bor pad+ma nyi zla'i dbus su rang gi rtsa
NK106(me)010:364: ba'i bla ma la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK106(me)010:365: dpa' dang brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad thim zhing
NK106(me)010:366: mkha' 'gro dpag tu med pa'i 'khor sprin phung 'thibs
NK106(me)010:367: pa tsam 'phro zhing 'du bar bsams la /
NK106(me)010:368: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang //
NK106(me)010:369: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK106(me)010:370: gus pas phag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK106(me)010:371: phyi nang gsang gsum mchod pa 'bul //
NK106(me)010:372: lus ngag yid gsum sdig sgrib bshags //
NK106(me)010:373: dge ba kun la rjes yi rangs //
NK106(me)010:374: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK106(me)010:376: dge bas byang chub che thob shog /
NK106(me)010:378: bla ma dang dkon mchog gsum la 'dzab dbyangs dang bcas pas skyabs 'gro ci 'grub byas nas /
NK106(me)010:379: rmi lam 'byongs par byin gyis rlobs //
NK106(me)010:380: sgyu mar rtogs par byin gyis rlobs //
NK106(me)010:381: 'khrul snang stongs par byin gyis rlobs //
NK106(me)010:382: bdag 'dzin zhig par byin gyis rlobs //
NK106(me)010:383: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gsol ba btab nas /
NK106(me)010:384: snang srid thams cad bdag la 'dus //
NK106(me)010:385: bdag nyid 'od du yal te bla ma'i thugs kar thim //
NK106(me)010:386: bla ma yang 'od du yal te nam mkha' dang 'dres pas /
NK106(me)010:387: nam mkhas gar khyab stong gsal chos sku'i bla mar
NK106(me)010:388: ngos bzung la nyams nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang der
NK106(me)010:389: glod nas ji tsam gnas kyi bar du bsgom par
NK106(me)010:390: bya'o // 'di ni bsod nams mchog tu 'phags te /
NK106(me)010:391: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:392: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK106(me)010:393: lha sku 'bum phrag bsgoms pa bas //
NK106(me)010:394: gang gis skad cig yud tsam zhig /
NK106(me)010:395: spyi gtsug 'khor lo'i rgyan nyid du //
NK106(me)010:396: bla ma dran pa khyad par 'phags //
NK106(me)010:398: de ltar sngon 'gro rdzogs nas chos thams cad rmi
NK106(me)010:399: lam lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dngos la mnyam par
NK106(me)010:400: gzhag pa ni / de nas dngos gzhi ji ltar bsgom pa ni //
NK106(me)010:401: phyi rol ri dang lung pa yul gru dang //
NK106(me)010:402: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' sems can sogs //
NK106(me)010:403: gzugs sgra dri ro reg ste yul lnga dang //
NK106(me)010:404: nang gi lus dang dbang shes chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:405: rmi lam nyid ces yang dang yang sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:406: bden med kyi snang ba rang shar du rtsal sbyong ba ni /
NK106(me)010:407: phyogs mtho sa snang ba yangs sar 'dug ste /
NK106(me)010:408: 'di ltar phyi rol yul lngas bsdus pa'i ri dang lung pa dang grong yul dang /
NK106(me)010:413: dran rig gi kun du rtog pa 'di thams cad rmi lam gyi snang ba ste /
NK106(me)010:414: de bzhin du snang ba tsam las gang du'ang ma grub par 'dug /
NK106(me)010:415: bden med du 'dug snyam du snying thag pa nas skad cig kyang ma yengs par bsgom par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:417: kha rtsang phan chad 'das pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:418: mdang sum rmi lam dang 'dra yid kyi yul //
NK106(me)010:419: de ring snang ba'ang med bzhin snang ba'i blo //
NK106(me)010:420: mdang dang do mod rmi lam dang 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)010:421: sang dang sang nub ma 'ongs rmi lam ste //
NK106(me)010:422: dgag sgrub bde sdug ci snang thams cad la //
NK106(me)010:423: rmi lam yin pa'i 'du shes nyer bzhag nas //
NK106(me)010:424: bden pa'i blo ni skad cig bsgom mi bya //
NK106(me)010:425: 'das pa'i chos thams cad kha rtsang gi snang ba dang mdang gi rmi lam lta bu /
NK106(me)010:426: da ltar gyi chos thams cad de ring gi snang ba dang do mod kyi rmi lam lta bu /
NK106(me)010:427: ma 'ongs pa'i chos thams cad sang gi snang ba dang sang nub kyi rmi lam lta bu /
NK106(me)010:428: ngo bo med pa snang ba ma 'gags pa /
NK106(me)010:430: snang dus nyid nas ma grub pa ste /
NK106(me)010:431: dgag sgrub dang bde sdug thams cad rmi lam nyid
NK106(me)010:432: nas gzhan ma yin no snyam nas bden med du
NK106(me)010:433: shes par bya'o // de bzhin du /
NK106(me)010:434: 'gro 'dug za 'chag gtam smar gyur pa na'ang //
NK106(me)010:435: rmi lam nang zhes ma yengs dran pas gzung //
NK106(me)010:436: ci snang ci byed ci bsam thams cad kun //
NK106(me)010:437: rmi lam yin pa'i 'du shes ma bral bas //
NK106(me)010:438: bden med 'al 'ol ban bun phyed phyod dang //
NK106(me)010:439: sang sing khral khrol 'dzin med chen por sbyong //
NK106(me)010:443: zas ci lta bu za yang /
NK106(me)010:445: rnam rtog ji lta bu 'phro yang /
NK106(me)010:446: spyod lam ji lta bu byed kyang /
NK106(me)010:447: snang ba ji lta bu shar kyang /
NK106(me)010:448: skad cig de nyid du rmi lam dngos yin /
NK106(me)010:449: rmi lam gyi ngo bo bden med yin /
NK106(me)010:450: bden med kyi ngo bo 'dzin med yin /
NK106(me)010:452: 'al 'ol gyi ngo bo ban bun yin /
NK106(me)010:453: ban bun gyi ngo bo phyad phyod yin /
NK106(me)010:454: phyad phyod kyi ngo bo sang seng yin /
NK106(me)010:455: sang seng gi ngo bo khral khrol yin /
NK106(me)010:456: thams cad med pa gsal snang yin snyam du ma
NK106(me)010:457: yengs par 'dun pa rtse gcig gis sbyang bar bya'o
NK106(me)010:458: // de ltar yul snang rmi lam du rtogs pas
NK106(me)010:459: gzung ba rang bzhin med par ngang gis rtogs pa
NK106(me)010:460: // 'di ltar / gzung yul 'khrul snang rmi lam nyid brtags pas //
NK106(me)010:461: gzung ba'i blo bral 'dzin pa shugs la bral //
NK106(me)010:462: yul bkag pas ni yul can 'gog pa yin //
NK106(me)010:463: de la gzung yul sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos rnams rmi lam du shes pa ni /
NK106(me)010:464: de la dang por rtogs pa'i blo gzung bar skyes pa yang rmi lam du shes te /
NK106(me)010:465: de'i rjes la spyod pa'i blo 'dzin pa'i rnam par byung ba de yang rmi lam du 'char bas /
NK106(me)010:466: gzung yul bden med du shes dus de la 'jal
NK106(me)010:467: byed kyi gzung 'dzin bden med du 'char ba ni
NK106(me)010:468: / yul bkag stobs kyis yul can shugs la khegs pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:469: de nas 'dzin pa log pas kyang gzung ba log pa'i tshul bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:470: res 'ga' snang ba rmi lam nyid 'jal ba'i //
NK106(me)010:471: sems de phyi nang bar gsum rab btsal bas //
NK106(me)010:472: ngo bo ngos gzung gza' gtad med pa'i blo //
NK106(me)010:473: phyogs 'byams nam mkha' 'dra ba'i ngang nyid do //
NK106(me)010:474: dran bsam tshol khro bral ba'i rig pa de //
NK106(me)010:475: stong gsal spros dang bral ba ngang gis 'char //
NK106(me)010:476: 'dzin pa 'gags pas gzung ba rang 'gags pa //
NK106(me)010:477: yul can log pas yul 'dzin grol ba'i tshe //
NK106(me)010:478: snang yul 'brel med dpyad ra zhig par snang //
NK106(me)010:479: de tshe gnyis med rang byung ye shes yin //
NK106(me)010:480: gzung yul rmi lam du 'jal byed kyi sems la
NK106(me)010:481: byung gnas 'gro gsum dang ngo bo ngos gzung brtags
NK106(me)010:482: pas / gang du'ang ma grub pa'i shes pa gtad yal stong par shar dus /
NK106(me)010:483: nang gi 'dzin pa rang grol bas /
NK106(me)010:484: phyi'i snang yul snang la 'dzin med stong pa'i rang snang ltar shar ba ni /
NK106(me)010:485: gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi ye shes rig pa byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:487: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK106(me)010:488: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK106(me)010:490: de ltar shar dus na dgongs pa blo 'das gzung 'dzin dang bral te /
NK106(me)010:491: de ltar rtogs shing goms pa'i rang dus na //
NK106(me)010:492: gzung 'dzin log pas yul sems zhen pa grol //
NK106(me)010:493: snang la der 'dzin med pa'i nyams shar nas //
NK106(me)010:494: gang snang ye stong rtsa ba bral bar 'char //
NK106(me)010:495: 'di ni rang bzhin gdod ma'i gnas lugs yin //
NK106(me)010:496: de la gzung 'dzin gzung yul la 'dzin pa'i rtog dpyod yin pas /
NK106(me)010:497: de gnyis dang bral ba ni gzung yul gyi zhen pa grol ba zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)010:498: de'i tshe yul snang der 'dzin med pa'i nyams shar
NK106(me)010:499: dus shar ba'i rig pa la bltas pas ye stong
NK106(me)010:500: rtsa bral zang kar shar ba ni rang bzhin gdod
NK106(me)010:501: ma'i gnas lugs chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba zhes
NK106(me)010:502: bya ste / pad+ma cod pan las /
NK106(me)010:503: zad pa'i snang ba yul rnams dang //
NK106(me)010:504: 'dzin pa'i rtog pa kun las grol //
NK106(me)010:505: rang gsal dag pa'i nam mkha' bzhin //
NK106(me)010:506: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)010:508: de ltar goms pa ji zhig na //
NK106(me)010:510: de la gzung 'dzin du rtog pa ma dag pa
NK106(me)010:511: gzhan dbang nub nas dag pa gzhan dbang las gdod
NK106(me)010:512: ma'i dbyings su rnam par grol ba yang 'di ltar
NK106(me)010:513: / rim gyis snang yul ma dag gzhan dbang yang //
NK106(me)010:514: der 'dzin log pas dag pa gzhan dbang du //
NK106(me)010:515: ji zhig tshe na mngon du 'gyur ba ni //
NK106(me)010:516: rmi lam 'khrul snang gnyid sad med pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:517: gdod ma'i gzhi la mngon par byang chub 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:518: snang ba'i yul la der 'dzin log pa na /
NK106(me)010:519: bad kan can gyi mig ser log pas /
NK106(me)010:520: dung ser 'dzin gyi snang ba rang log pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:521: 'khrul snang cha dang bcas pa log pa ste /
NK106(me)010:522: ma dag pa gzhan dbang rmi lam dang gzung 'dzin zhen pa'i gnyid sad stobs kyis grol dus /
NK106(me)010:523: snang ba thams cad zhing khams dag par snang yang
NK106(me)010:524: rang snang dag pa dung dkar 'dzin lta bu ste
NK106(me)010:525: / gzhan snang phyam chad pa med kyang phyi rol
NK106(me)010:526: gyi snang ba la gzhan zhes brjod pa dang rjes
NK106(me)010:527: su mthun par dag pa gzhan dbang mngon du gyur
NK106(me)010:528: / pa zhes bya'o // de'ang dag pa sa gsum du dbang bzhi 'byung ba lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:530: yid dang 'dzin dang rnam par rtog /
NK106(me)010:531: gyur phyir rnam par mi rtog dang //
NK106(me)010:532: zhing dang ye shes las dag la //
NK106(me)010:533: dbang ni rnam pa bzhi yis gnas //
NK106(me)010:534: dbang de mi g.yo la sogs pa'i //
NK106(me)010:535: sa gsum la ni rnam bzhi ste //
NK106(me)010:536: gcig la rnam gnyis de las gzhan //
NK106(me)010:537: dbang ni re rer 'dod pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:539: de nas mngon par byang chub pa'i tshe chos kyi skur ro gcig pas /
NK106(me)010:540: snang mi snang thams cad las 'das pa'i dbyings las
NK106(me)010:541: gzugs sku gnyis kyi snang ba lhun grub tu shar
NK106(me)010:543: de la 'khrul par snang dus nyid nas yod ma myong bar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:544: 'khrul pa'ang sngon med phyis med par 'dir snang //
NK106(me)010:545: snang yang snang ba'i dus nas yod ma myong //
NK106(me)010:546: med bzhin snang ba bag chags 'khrul pa'i blo //
NK106(me)010:547: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i rmi lam 'dra //
NK106(me)010:548: 'di ltar 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang thams cad thog ma'i dbyings na'ang med /
NK106(me)010:549: tha ma rnam par grol ba na'ang med /
NK106(me)010:550: da lta dbyings nas rang snang 'khrul pa'i dus kyi ngo kha la yod yod ltar snang yang /
NK106(me)010:551: snang dus nyid nas gcig dang du ma'i dngos po med pas /
NK106(me)010:552: med pa gsal snang tsam ste /
NK106(me)010:553: don la med pa sems la yod pa ltar snang
NK106(me)010:554: ba'i phyir 'khrul snang zhes bya ste rmi lam bzhin
NK106(me)010:555: no // ji ltar rmi lam dang mtshungs she na smras pa /
NK106(me)010:556: ji ltar rmi lam nang gi snang ba de //
NK106(me)010:557: gnyid ma sod dang sad dus med na yang //
NK106(me)010:558: gnyid dus snang la snang dus rang bzhin med //
NK106(me)010:559: med snang gzhi rtsa bral bar shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:560: dper na rmi lam du 'dod pa'i yul dang 'phrad
NK106(me)010:561: pa'i snang ba de gnyid du 'gro kha dang sad
NK106(me)010:564: gzhi dang 'bras bu'i dus gnyis na med kyang /
NK106(me)010:565: da lta lam dus na snang ste /
NK106(me)010:566: snang ba'i dus nyid nas 'khrul snang gzhi rtsa dngos
NK106(me)010:567: med de stong pa'i gzugs brnyan tsam du shes par
NK106(me)010:570: ji ltar skyes bu 'dod chags pa dag /
NK106(me)010:571: rmi lam na yang de yi yul mthong ste //
NK106(me)010:572: nye bar brtan byas sad dus med par ltar //
NK106(me)010:573: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:575: de ltar rmi lam gyi ngo bo nyid rab tu
NK106(me)010:576: goms par byed pa dag gi mtshan mo'i rnal 'byor
NK106(me)010:577: bshad pa / de ltar nyin mo rab tu goms bya zhing //
NK106(me)010:578: mtshan mo gnyid kyis rab tu snyoms pa'i tshe //
NK106(me)010:579: bde ba'i mal du g.yas phab nyal ba ni //
NK106(me)010:580: mgon po mya ngan 'das gzims lta bu la //
NK106(me)010:581: rlung rgyu rab tu dal dang mig mi 'gul //
NK106(me)010:582: snying nang a dkar shel gong 'od 'bar ba //
NK106(me)010:583: tshon gang ches phra'i ngang la sems bzung la //
NK106(me)010:584: rmi lam lta bu'i dran pa ma yengs bya //
NK106(me)010:585: de yis rmi lam lta bu'i 'od gsal 'char //
NK106(me)010:586: rmi lam ni nyin dus 'dun pa'i gnad las 'byongs pas /
NK106(me)010:587: seng ge'i nyal lugs kyis lhod chags par nyal ba'i tshe /
NK106(me)010:588: rlung gnad rab tu dal bas rgyu ba mi tshor ba tsam las mig har por mi 'gul zhing /
NK106(me)010:589: snying gi nang du a dkar po'i 'od 'bar ba'i
NK106(me)010:590: 'phro 'du las tshon gang nas mthar shin tu phra
NK106(me)010:591: ba rta rnga'i nyag tsam la sems bzung ste /
NK106(me)010:592: rmi lam yin snyam pa'i ngang la nyal bas /
NK106(me)010:593: ting nge 'dzin brtan pa rnams la dngas gsal mtha'
NK106(me)010:594: dbus med pa'i 'od gsal du 'char mi brtan yang
NK106(me)010:595: rmi lam sngon pas dngas te zin par sla'o //
NK106(me)010:596: de ltar nyams su blangs pa las /
NK106(me)010:597: thog mar rmi lam 'jigs sngangs rmis pa na //
NK106(me)010:598: rmi lam dran pas 'jigs snang rang sar grol //
NK106(me)010:599: rmi lam ngang der ting 'dzin grub pa ni //
NK106(me)010:600: rmi lam zin zhes rnal 'byor pas shes bya //
NK106(me)010:601: rmi lam du g.yang dang rbab dang khyi dang dgra
NK106(me)010:602: la sogs pa'i rkyen drag po rmis pa de rmi
NK106(me)010:603: lam du shes pa la dang por rmi lam zin
NK106(me)010:604: pa 'dun pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:605: 'jigs dngangs skrag pa'i sgrib pa las mchog gi rgyal ba'i gnyen po thob bo //
NK106(me)010:607: de nas rmi lam bden med gcig tu sbyong //
NK106(me)010:608: de yang med bzhin snang ba'i 'khrul ba'i blo //
NK106(me)010:609: rmi lam dang 'dra ngo bo ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)010:610: bden rdzun blo las 'dus pa shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:611: rmi lam zin nas skrag dngangs grol ba tsam gyis mi chog /
NK106(me)010:612: thams cad bden med du shes dgos /
NK106(me)010:613: de'ang rmi lam 'di mi bden pa ltar chos thams
NK106(me)010:614: cad med bzhin snang ba rmi lam lta bu yin
NK106(me)010:616: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:617: 'jam dpal rmi lam ni snang la yod pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:618: de bzhin du chos thams cad kyang snang la yod pa ma yin no zhes gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:619: bden med du shes pa gal che bas /
NK106(me)010:621: de nas sprul zhing bsgyur ba'i rim pa yang //
NK106(me)010:622: rmi lam dus der rang lus tshangs pa lha //
NK106(me)010:623: bde gshegs byang chub sems sogs gang 'dod du //
NK106(me)010:624: sprul zhing bsgoms la bden med ngang du gzhag /
NK106(me)010:625: rang nyid sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK106(me)010:628: zhi khro la sogs par sprul te /
NK106(me)010:629: 'di kho na bden med yin pas de ltar snang ngo snyam du shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:631: de nas skad cig skad cig tsam nyid du //
NK106(me)010:632: tshangs las brgya byin de bzhin lha las mi //
NK106(me)010:633: gang 'dod bsgyur la bden med ngang du bsgom //
NK106(me)010:634: sprul pa rnams phan tshun go bsgyur ba na bden med du 'dug snyam pas /
NK106(me)010:635: gang ltar 'dod pa ltar bsgyur ro //
NK106(me)010:637: de nas brgya stong bye ba spel bya zhing //
NK106(me)010:638: gang 'dul thabs kyis gnyen por rtsal sbyang ngo //
NK106(me)010:639: sprul bsgyur gyi snang ba de dag brgya stong bye bar spel zhing /
NK106(me)010:642: de kho nas bden med du sbyong zhing klu'i gnyen por rang nyid bya khyung dang /
NK106(me)010:643: rgyal bsen la rta mgrin la sogs par gyur te
NK106(me)010:644: za ba dang lding ba la sogs pas gdul bar
NK106(me)010:645: bya'o // 'di ni mthu stobs dang rdzu 'phrul 'grub
NK106(me)010:646: pa'i thun mong ma yin pa'i nye rgyu yin no
NK106(me)010:647: bya'o // // 'di dag gi tshe lus 'chus pa
NK106(me)010:648: dang 'khums pa dang 'phros pa byung na rtsa rlung
NK106(me)010:649: bya'o // // 'chu bas / sprul bsgyur la sogs
NK106(me)010:650: mi 'byong ba'i phyir nyal lugs bde zhing rlung dal
NK106(me)010:651: la rig pa dngas par bya ba ni myong ba
NK106(me)010:653: bden med du sbyangs pa rdzogs pa'i rjes thogs /
NK106(me)010:654: de nas dag pa'i zhing dang yul khams dang //
NK106(me)010:655: 'og min la sogs gang 'dod der song ste //
NK106(me)010:656: bde gshegs lha dang gtsang ma'i chos rab mnyan //
NK106(me)010:657: ye shes ting 'dzin gzungs sprin sgrub pa yang //
NK106(me)010:658: nyin mtshan rgyun du dran pas rab sbyangs pas //
NK106(me)010:659: de ltar 'gyur ba rig pa'i yon tan te //
NK106(me)010:660: gnad la mi bslu mngon du byed pa yin //
NK106(me)010:661: 'di ni yang zab snying po'i theg pa'o //
NK106(me)010:662: sprul bsgyur 'byongs nas yul khams gzhan dang /
NK106(me)010:665: bde ba can la sogs pa'i zhing khams sngon ma mthong ba blta bar 'dod na /
NK106(me)010:666: nyin dus 'dun pa btang la sngar bzhin nyal te /
NK106(me)010:667: yul khams dang 'jig rten thams cad mgrin pa longs
NK106(me)010:668: spyod 'khor lo na gsal ba stong gsum nyungs 'brur
NK106(me)010:669: tshud pa'i rnam pa las ma yengs par nyal bas
NK106(me)010:670: / gang 'dod pa'i snang ba mthong ba ni /
NK106(me)010:671: rig pa la mthong rung gi yon tan ye nas yod pa'i gnad las byung ba'o //
NK106(me)010:672: 'di dag gi tshe'ang bden med kyi don la sbyang ba'i gnad yin /
NK106(me)010:673: bden med ni rang bzhin med pa yin te de
NK106(me)010:674: nyid shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa yin
NK106(me)010:675: la / de la slob pas yon tan thams cad 'grub pa'i phyir te /
NK106(me)010:677: chos rnams rang bzhin med pa yongs su rtogs gyur pa //
NK106(me)010:678: 'di ni shes rab pha rol phyin zhes rgyal bas gsungs //
NK106(me)010:681: rnam pa thams cad du lha dang mi'i las 'das
NK106(me)010:682: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yongs su dag pa
NK106(me)010:684: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:685: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK106(me)010:686: thams cad nyungs 'bru gcig tu chud la nyungs 'bru
NK106(me)010:687: de yang che bar ma sems /
NK106(me)010:688: 'jig rten gyi khams kyang chung bar mi mngon par
NK106(me)010:689: 'dod pas kyang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK106(me)010:690: pa la bslab par bya'o zhes pa la sogs pa
NK106(me)010:692: 'di ni theg pa chen po'i mthar thug pa'i rnal 'byor du bya ba'i lam gyi snying po'o //
NK106(me)010:693: da ni rmi lam goms pa las lam gyi 'bras bu bstan pa /
NK106(me)010:694: de ltar nyin mtshan rmi lam don bsgoms pas //
NK106(me)010:695: dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i gzeb las grol //
NK106(me)010:696: ra ba ri dang rtsig par thogs med cing //
NK106(me)010:697: rdzu 'phrul mngon shes ting 'dzin grangs med 'grub //
NK106(me)010:698: nyams rtogs tshad med 'phags pa'i ye shes skye //
NK106(me)010:699: gnas skabs kyi ye shes 'bras bu ni thar pa'i lam sna zin nas 'dod dgu 'grub cing /
NK106(me)010:700: mkha' 'gro grub pa can gyis rjes su 'dzin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:701: nad nyung ba dang zo mdog bde ba dang /
NK106(me)010:703: chos thams cad rang bzhin med par ngang gis rtogs shing /
NK106(me)010:704: ting nge 'dzin rnal 'byor du byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:705: sbyor ba'i lam thob pas rdzu 'phrul dang mngon par shes pa du ma la dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK106(me)010:706: chos thams cad rmi lam lta bur rtogs pa la sogs pa'i rtags thob cing /
NK106(me)010:707: dge ba brtan pa'i yon tan thob ste /
NK106(me)010:709: rmi lam na yang chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:710: rmi lam lta bur lta la sogs //
NK106(me)010:711: rtse mor phyin pa sbyor ba'i rtags //
NK106(me)010:712: rnam pa bcu gnyis dag tu bzhed //
NK106(me)010:713: 'dzam bu gling gi skye bo snyed //
NK106(me)010:714: sangs rgyas mchod pa'i dge la sogs //
NK106(me)010:715: nam langs du ni dper mdzad nas //
NK106(me)010:716: bsod nams mang po nyid kyis ni //
NK106(me)010:717: rnam 'phel bcu drug bdag nyid do //
NK106(me)010:718: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:719: de nyid ches cher goms pa las mthong lam dang
NK106(me)010:720: sgom lam rnam par mi rtog pa 'phags pa'i ye
NK106(me)010:721: shes gong ma rdzogs pa'i rjes ma mi slob pa'i
NK106(me)010:723: mthar thug sems nyid gdod ma'i dbyings phyin nas //
NK106(me)010:724: rang don chos sku gzhan don gzugs sku gnyis //
NK106(me)010:725: rmi lam lta bur don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)010:726: de phyir rmi lam lta bu'i tshul sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:727: rmi lam lta bu'i byang chub kyi lam sbyangs pa'i
NK106(me)010:728: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rmi lam ltar snang la
NK106(me)010:729: rang bzhin med pa'i sangs rgyas spangs rtogs mthar phyin
NK106(me)010:731: dge ba'i rtsa ba yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)010:732: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)010:733: rnams pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu zhes so //
NK106(me)010:734: de yang rang don chos sku nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK106(me)010:735: dbyings la lhun gyis grub pa'i thugs rjes gzhan don
NK106(me)010:736: du gzugs sku nyi zla lta bur shar nas 'khor
NK106(me)010:737: ba ji srid par don mdzad de /
NK106(me)010:739: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK106(me)010:740: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK106(me)010:741: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK106(me)010:742: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK106(me)010:743: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK106(me)010:744: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK106(me)010:745: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK106(me)010:746: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK106(me)010:747: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol pa dang //
NK106(me)010:748: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK106(me)010:749: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK106(me)010:750: bdud sde bcom dang rdzogs par ni //
NK106(me)010:751: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK106(me)010:752: mya ngan 'da' bar gshegs mdzad rnams //
NK106(me)010:753: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams du //
NK106(me)010:754: srid pa ji srid gnas par snyon //
NK106(me)010:756: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK106(me)010:757: rmi lam lta bur 'khrul pa'i 'khor ba pa //
NK106(me)010:758: gang rnams sdug bsngal chu bzhi las grol te //
NK106(me)010:759: bde chen yon tan 'byor pa'i gnas thob shog /
NK106(me)010:760: sna tshogs rmi lam rnam kun stong pa'i gzugs //
NK106(me)010:761: mtsho chen brgal dka' srid rtse'i bar khyab pa //
NK106(me)010:762: sdug bsngal me tshogs spungs pa'i 'khor ba las //
NK106(me)010:763: ma lus 'gro kun bdag gis 'dren par shog /
NK106(me)010:764: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:765: rmi lam lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas dang po'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:766: de ltar chos thams cad rmi lam gyi ngo bo
NK106(me)010:767: nyid du rang bzhin gyis ma skyes par bstan pa'i
NK106(me)010:768: rjes la / chos thams cad 'gag pa med pa
NK106(me)010:769: sgyu ma'i rol pa tsam du rtogs par bya'o zhes
NK106(me)010:770: rjes la / bshad pa ni / yang 'dir rgyal bas sgyu ma lta bu zhes //
NK106(me)010:771: chos rnams rang bzhin med pa'i tshul gsungs pa //
NK106(me)010:772: de yang mdo rgyud man ngag snying po'i don //
NK106(me)010:773: ji ltar nyams su myong bzhin bshad kyis nyon //
NK106(me)010:776: chos thams cad ni sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:777: rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:779: 'ong ba med pa'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:780: phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:781: chos rnams thams cad sgyu ma 'dra //
NK106(me)010:782: byang chub kyang na sgyu ma bzhin //
NK106(me)010:785: sgyu ma chos rnams thams cad de //
NK106(me)010:786: ming tsam ngo bo nyid kyis stong //
NK106(me)010:787: zhes pa la sogs pa mdo dang rgyud sde du
NK106(me)010:788: ma las gsungs pa rnams 'dir bla ma'i man ngag
NK106(me)010:789: gis legs par phye ba rang gi myong ba nges
NK106(me)010:790: pa'i rtags gsum la brten nas dbye na /
NK106(me)010:791: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i sgyu ma gsum las /
NK106(me)010:792: dang po gzhi sgyu ma nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang las 'khrul snang gi byung tshul bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:793: sems nyid gdod ma nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang //
NK106(me)010:794: lhun grub ye shes nyi zla gza' skar bzhin //
NK106(me)010:795: ye 'byams rmad du byung ba'i dbyings rum nas //
NK106(me)010:796: ma rig gzung 'dzin kun brtags rang shar bas //
NK106(me)010:797: khams gsum 'gro drug 'khrul snang sgyu ma bzhin //
NK106(me)010:798: de'ang sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes gdod nas
NK106(me)010:799: dag pa nam mkha' lta bu cir yang ma grub
NK106(me)010:800: pa'i ngang las / rtsa ba srog 'dzin pa'i rlung lnga g.yos pa las /
NK106(me)010:801: rang snang 'od gsal du shar ba rang ngo ma shes pa'i cha las /
NK106(me)010:802: phyi nang gi snod bcud lus dang bcas par 'khrul te /
NK106(me)010:803: sgyu ma ltar sna tshogs su snang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:804: rdo rje sems dpa' snying gi me long gi rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:805: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad gzhi ci yang
NK106(me)010:806: ma yin pa las cir yang 'khrul lo zhes gsungs
NK106(me)010:807: pa bzhin no // ji ltar sgyu ma ltar 'khrul zhe na bshad pa /
NK106(me)010:808: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel stobs kyis rang snang ba //
NK106(me)010:809: shing bu rde'u rig sngags tshogs pa las //
NK106(me)010:810: mig 'phrul rta glang skyes pa bud med dang //
NK106(me)010:811: ri dang khang bzangs la sogs snang ba bzhin //
NK106(me)010:812: sgyu ma'i rta glang la sogs snang ba'ang 'khrul gzhi'i rgyu shing bu rde'u nyid /
NK106(me)010:813: 'khrul rkyen rig sngags kyis mig gi shes pa bslad dus /
NK106(me)010:814: 'khrul snang rta glang gi rnam par snang ba de
NK106(me)010:815: yang rten 'brel 'tshogs pa'i rang snang las shar ba
NK106(me)010:816: ltar / 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK106(me)010:817: ma rig dbang gis bag chags 'khrul pa'i blo //
NK106(me)010:818: snang srid yul dang der 'dzin dug gsum shar //
NK106(me)010:819: rang bzhin med la snang ba ma 'gags pa //
NK106(me)010:820: sgyu ma'i skye bo 'dra ba 'di dag kun //
NK106(me)010:821: bden med stong pa'i gzugs brnyan chen po ru //
NK106(me)010:822: de ring nyid du nges par rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:824: rkyen ma rig pa yul du byas pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis bslad pas /
NK106(me)010:825: 'khrul snang snod bcud so so'i ngo kha la sna tshogs su snang ste /
NK106(me)010:826: dug gsum gyi 'khor ba mtho dman la spyod cing yod yod ltar snang dus 'di nyid nas /
NK106(me)010:827: don la rdzun snang stong pa'i gzugs brnyan tsam las /
NK106(me)010:828: rig pa byang chub kyi sems su 'pho 'gyur med par rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:830: ji ltar skye bo mang po'i dbus dag tu //
NK106(me)010:831: sgyu ma byed pa dag gis gzugs sprul te //
NK106(me)010:832: rta dang glang po shing rta sna tshogs byas //
NK106(me)010:833: de dag mi bden sna tshogs snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)010:834: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:836: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i sgyu ma nam mkha' ltar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:837: yong ye snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:838: rang bzhin gshis la mkha' 'dra mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)010:839: ma skyes gdod nas dag pa shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:840: chos rnams thams cad gshis cir yang ma grub pas nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid de /
NK106(me)010:842: chos thams cad ni nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid de dbus dang mtha' mi dmigs so zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:844: rgyal ba'i sras po dngos po rnam par 'jig /
NK106(me)010:845: srid pa thams cad yang ye stong pa ste //
NK106(me)010:846: nyi tshe'i stong pa mu stegs can rnams dang //
NK106(me)010:847: mkhas pa byis pa dag dang rtsod mi byed //
NK106(me)010:849: de la kha cig chos de la mi ldan rnam bcad kyis stong la /
NK106(me)010:850: rang gi ngo bos mi stong par 'dod pa yod
NK106(me)010:851: de nyi ma mun pas stong la 'od zer gyis
NK106(me)010:852: mi stong zhes pa lta bu ni /
NK106(me)010:853: nyi tshe ba'i stong pa ste /
NK106(me)010:854: bden zhen las nam du'ang grol ba mi srid /
NK106(me)010:855: 'di ltar nyi ma rang gi ngo bo gcig dang du mas stong pas 'od zer stong ste /
NK106(me)010:856: stong la snang ba 'di ni dbu ma'i de kho na nyid du gsungs te /
NK106(me)010:858: me yi rang bzhin tsha ba dang //
NK106(me)010:859: bu ram rang bzhin mngar ba ltar //
NK106(me)010:860: de phyir chos rnams thams cad kyis //
NK106(me)010:861: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gsungs //
NK106(me)010:864: gzugs ni gzugs kyi ngo bo nyid kyis stong ngo zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:865: mngon rtogs rgyan gyi 'grel chung ngu'ang /
NK106(me)010:866: rang rang ngo bos stong pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:867: stong pa nyid ni nyi shur 'dod //
NK106(me)010:869: de'ang stong pas med par 'gyur ba ma yin te /
NK106(me)010:870: stong pa'i rang bzhin snang ba dang dbyer med pas /
NK106(me)010:871: stong pa la chos thams cad 'thad de /
NK106(me)010:872: 'phags pa klu'i dbang po'i zhal snga nas //
NK106(me)010:873: gang la stong pa nyid rung ba //
NK106(me)010:874: de la thams cad rung bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:876: de la phan tshun gcig gis gcig stong pa ka ba dang bum pa'i stong pa dang /
NK106(me)010:877: mi ldan pa'i stong pa dngos po dang dngos med
NK106(me)010:878: dang rang mtshan gyi stong pa ri bo gi rwa
NK106(me)010:879: dang / rang bzhin gyis stong pa gzugs brnyan lta bu la sogs pa dbye ba mang yang /
NK106(me)010:880: de thams cad rtog ge bas kun brtags pa tsam las /
NK106(me)010:881: 'dir ni snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad /
NK106(me)010:882: rig ngo na snang yang gshis ngo na ma grub pa /
NK106(me)010:883: ye stong mtha' las 'das pa'i stong par rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:885: gang tshe chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK106(me)010:886: rang bzhin gyis ni ma skyes pa //
NK106(me)010:887: nam mkha' lta bur dngos med pa //
NK106(me)010:888: stong pa nyid ni dag pa yin //
NK106(me)010:891: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:892: gsal zhing dag la rnyog pa med //
NK106(me)010:893: gzung du med cing brjod du med //
NK106(me)010:894: ngo bo med cing gnas med pa //
NK106(me)010:896: de ltar chos thams cad stong pa nyid du nges nas /
NK106(me)010:897: stong pa'i dbyings las 'khor ba 'byung ba dang /
NK106(me)010:898: de nyid du lam sbyong ba dang /
NK106(me)010:899: mthar phyin nas grol ba'i rang bzhin ji lta bu snyam pa'i lan du /
NK106(me)010:900: dang po sdom tshig gi chings bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:901: skye med skye ba'i cho 'phrul ngang nyid du //
NK106(me)010:902: rang bzhin sgyu ma sbyang bya'i gzhi dang ni //
NK106(me)010:903: ma dag sgyu ma sbyang bya'i dri ma dang //
NK106(me)010:904: thabs kyi sgyu ma sbyong byed gnyen po dang //
NK106(me)010:905: ye shes sgyu ma mthar phyin 'bras bu ste //
NK106(me)010:906: rnam bzhi dpe yi sgyu mas gtan la phab //
NK106(me)010:908: mkhas pa dag ni dpes go bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:909: rang bzhin sgyu ma la sogs bzhi po dag gi dbyings de las 'khrul pa dang /
NK106(me)010:911: mthar phyin pa'i gnas skabs bzhis rig par bya ba las /
NK106(me)010:912: dpe'i sgyu mas sngon du go don bzhag na /
NK106(me)010:913: de'i rjes su rang rang gis mtshan nyid nges pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:914: dpe nges pa'i bya ba yang /
NK106(me)010:915: ji ltar rigs sngags las byung mig 'phrul te //
NK106(me)010:916: shing bu rde'u rta glang snang dus nas //
NK106(me)010:917: rta glang ma yin shing bu rde'u nyid //
NK106(me)010:918: de bzhin chos kun bden med mtshon pa nyid //
NK106(me)010:919: rang bzhin dpe yis sgyu mar shes bya ste //
NK106(me)010:920: 'khrul pa'i gzhi dang 'khrul skyon 'khrul pa'i tshul //
NK106(me)010:921: 'khrul snang 'khrul grol gdod mar grol tshul rnams //
NK106(me)010:922: dpe yi sngon rol dpe dang dper 'grub dang //
NK106(me)010:923: dper grub dpe zhig sngon bzhin rang mtshan dus //
NK106(me)010:924: rnam bzhi go rims dpe yis sgyu ma bstan //
NK106(me)010:925: sgyu ma mkhan bzang pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:926: las kyis sprul pa'i sgyu ma ni //
NK106(me)010:928: rkyen gyis sprul pa'i sgyu ma ni //
NK106(me)010:929: me long gzugs brnyan la sogs so //
NK106(me)010:930: chos kyis sprul pa'i sgyu ma ni //
NK106(me)010:931: nga yi 'khor gyi dge slong ngo //
NK106(me)010:932: nga ni yang dag sgyu ma ste //
NK106(me)010:933: 'dus ma byas pa chos kyi sku //
NK106(me)010:935: de la 'khrul gzhi'i rig pa ni rang bzhin sgyu ma ste /
NK106(me)010:937: de'i steng na lhan skyes kyi ma rig pa yod pas 'khrul pa 'byung rung du yod pa ni /
NK106(me)010:938: rta glang snang rung du med la 'byung rung du
NK106(me)010:939: yod pa dpe'i sngon rol gyi shing bu lta bu'o
NK106(me)010:940: // rig pa dbyings las gzhir snang du 'phags pa'i
NK106(me)010:941: tshe kun brtags pa'i ma rig pa gzung 'dzin gyi
NK106(me)010:942: rtsa bar shar bas ma dag pa'i sgyu ma sbyang
NK106(me)010:944: rig pa la 'khrul rtog gis sbags pas /
NK106(me)010:945: 'khrul snang dngos su med la 'khrul rtog tu ldan pa /
NK106(me)010:946: rig sngags kyi sngags bgrangs bzhin pa lta ba ste /
NK106(me)010:947: rta glang gi dpe grub nges dus byas pa lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:948: de nas rig ngor 'khrul snang dngos su snang dus
NK106(me)010:949: 'di nyid rig pa gzung 'dzin gyis bslad pas sna
NK106(me)010:950: tshogs rang snang du shar ba rig sngags las shing
NK106(me)010:951: bu rde'u nyid rta glang gi rnam par snang ba'i
NK106(me)010:952: rang dus sgyu ma dngos kyi dper grub pa lta
NK106(me)010:953: bu'o // de nas rig pa la lam bsgoms pas bden zhen srab pa ni thabs sgyu ma ste /
NK106(me)010:954: sgyu ma'i rig sngags 'jig bzhin pa lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:955: de'i mthar 'khrul rtog log pas 'khrul snang 'gag ste gdod mar grol ba ni /
NK106(me)010:956: rig pa dang po'i gshis thog tu rang phebs pa'i
NK106(me)010:957: dus de ye shes sgyu ma yin la ma rig
NK106(me)010:958: gzung 'dzin gyi rig sngags log pas /
NK106(me)010:959: 'khor ba 'khrul snang gi rta glang gi snang ba log ste /
NK106(me)010:960: sgyu ma zhig pa'i shing bu rde'u ltar rig pa
NK106(me)010:961: gzhi'i gzugs zang ka ma rang ngor snang bas sku
NK106(me)010:962: dang ye shes 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dgongs pa las
NK106(me)010:964: dpe zhig pa'i rang dus shing bu rde'u lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:965: 'di dag ni rgyud kyi rdo rje'i tshig rlabs po che'i dka' ba'i gnas mngon du phyung ba'o //
NK106(me)010:966: de ltar sgyu ma bzhi'i dpe don shan sbyar nas /
NK106(me)010:967: da ni so so'i mtshan nyid gsal bar bshad pa las /
NK106(me)010:969: rang bzhin sgyu ma sems nyid 'od gsal te //
NK106(me)010:970: sbyang gzhi'i dbyings yin bde gshegs snying po yin //
NK106(me)010:971: de la rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid //
NK106(me)010:972: ye nas lhun grub 'dus ma byas su gnas te /
NK106(me)010:973: 'khor 'das kun la dbri bsnan dang che chung med par khyab pa ni /
NK106(me)010:974: zla ba sgron me'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:975: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab //
NK106(me)010:978: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK106(me)010:979: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK106(me)010:980: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK106(me)010:981: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can //
NK106(me)010:983: de nyid ye nas dri ma med pa'i 'od gsal ba ste /
NK106(me)010:985: sems la sems ma mchis te sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:987: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK106(me)010:988: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK106(me)010:989: de bsal na ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK106(me)010:992: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK106(me)010:993: dri ma rnams ni glo bur nyid //
NK106(me)010:995: de'ang khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po de nyid /
NK106(me)010:996: sems can pa'i dus na ma dag pa'i khams /
NK106(me)010:997: byang chub sems dpa'i dus na ma dag dag pa'i khams /
NK106(me)010:998: sangs rgyas pa'i dus na shin tu rnam dag gi khams zhes ming gsum btags kyang /
NK106(me)010:999: ngo bo la bzang ngan du 'gyur ba med de /
NK106(me)010:1001: ma dag ma dag dag pa dang //
NK106(me)010:1002: shin tu rnam dag go rims bzhin //
NK106(me)010:1003: sems can byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK106(me)010:1004: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes brjod do //
NK106(me)010:1007: de bzhin nyid de thams cad la //
NK106(me)010:1008: khyad par med de dag gyur la //
NK106(me)010:1010: ji ltar sngon bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK106(me)010:1011: 'gyur ba med pa'i de bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)010:1013: de lta bu'i khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po rang rig gi ngo bo la /
NK106(me)010:1014: dag dang ma dag gang du'ang ma chad pas //
NK106(me)010:1015: 'khor dang mya ngan 'das pa gnyis las 'das //
NK106(me)010:1017: rig dang ma rig rkyen las de ltar yin //
NK106(me)010:1018: 'di ni gdod ma'i gshis yin gnas lugs yin //
NK106(me)010:1019: de la rig pa rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK106(me)010:1020: gang du'ang grub bsal med pas 'khor 'das gang du'ang ma grub ste /
NK106(me)010:1023: de la rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i dbyings de ni 'khor ba'ang ma yin /
NK106(me)010:1024: mya ngan las 'das pa'ang ma yin te dngos po med pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK106(me)010:1025: gshis cir yang ma grub pa'i ngang las /
NK106(me)010:1026: gdangs 'char gzhi ma 'gags pa'i rtsal gyis /
NK106(me)010:1028: ma rig pas 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang sgyu ma ltar snang ste /
NK106(me)010:1030: sems nyid gcig pu kun gyi sa bon te //
NK106(me)010:1031: gang la srid dang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK106(me)010:1033: gang du'ang ma grub pas gang ltar yang 'char gzhi byed pa'i dpe nye bar dgod pa ni /
NK106(me)010:1034: me long dngas bzhin gzugs brnyan 'char gzhi byed //
NK106(me)010:1035: shar dus nyid nas gang du'ang ma chad pa //
NK106(me)010:1036: me long ngos te dkar nag gnyis med la //
NK106(me)010:1037: dkar nag gnyis ka'i 'char gzhi byed dang mtshungs //
NK106(me)010:1038: 'di nyid shes pas kun la mkhas par gyur //
NK106(me)010:1039: me long g.ya' dag pa'i ngos de gzugs brnyan gang du'ang ma grub la /
NK106(me)010:1040: gang ltar yang 'char ba'i gzhi byed pa ste /
NK106(me)010:1041: dkar nag tu shar yang dkar nag tu ma grub
NK106(me)010:1042: pa'i dpes rig pa me long dngas pa lta bu
NK106(me)010:1043: de yang gang du'ang ma grub la /
NK106(me)010:1045: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba shar dus nyid nas /
NK106(me)010:1046: rig pa la ma gos pa'i tshul 'di shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1047: 'dis ni snang yang 'dzin pas ched du ma bslad
NK106(me)010:1048: na 'khrul snang gis gos mi srid pa zhes bya
NK106(me)010:1049: ste / yul spang len las 'das pas rig pa'i
NK106(me)010:1050: rang 'gros la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor pa chen po
NK106(me)010:1052: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug ti lo pa'i zhal snga nas /
NK106(me)010:1054: zhen pa chod cig na ro pa //
NK106(me)010:1056: zhi ba lha'i zhal snga nas kyang /
NK106(me)010:1057: 'dir ni mthong thos shes pa dag /
NK106(me)010:1058: dgag par bya ba ma yin te //
NK106(me)010:1059: gang la'ang sdug bsngal rgyur gyur pa //
NK106(me)010:1060: bden par rtogs pa bzlog bya yin //
NK106(me)010:1062: gnyis pa dag bya'i rang bzhin /
NK106(me)010:1063: ma dag sgyu ma 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang ste //
NK106(me)010:1064: gnyis med gnyis su bzung las der snang ngo //
NK106(me)010:1065: snod bcud 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'khrul rtog dang bcas
NK106(me)010:1066: pa 'di rnams rig pa'i rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i
NK106(me)010:1067: khams la sgrib pa'i dri ma ste /
NK106(me)010:1068: rgyu kun 'byung las 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi bden pa snang ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:1069: gsum pa de dag sbyang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1070: thabs kyi sgyu ma gnyen po lam yin te //
NK106(me)010:1071: tshogs dang sbyor mthong sgom pa'i lam bzhi ru //
NK106(me)010:1072: tshogs gnyis rim gnyis sbyong byed bsgoms pa yis //
NK106(me)010:1073: sbyang bya'i dri ma sprin 'dra sel byed yin //
NK106(me)010:1074: de la tshogs lam chung ngur dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi dang /
NK106(me)010:1075: 'bring du yang dag spong ba bzhi dang /
NK106(me)010:1076: chen po rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
NK106(me)010:1077: sbyor lam drod dang rtse mor dbang po lnga dang /
NK106(me)010:1078: bzod pa dang chos mchog tu stobs lnga dang /
NK106(me)010:1079: mthong lam du byang chub kyi lam yan lag bdun dang /
NK106(me)010:1080: sgom lam du 'phags pa'i lam brgyad de /
NK106(me)010:1081: byang chub kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
NK106(me)010:1082: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis dang /
NK106(me)010:1083: bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa gnyis la gnas pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1084: lam gyi de kho na nyid gang du bgrod par 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)010:1085: de las lam gyi rim pa rab tu gces pas che long zhig brjod na /
NK106(me)010:1086: mdo'i cha nas ji lta ba bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:1087: blo gros rab brtan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1088: blo gros rab brtan gyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)010:1089: bcom ldan 'das dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi ji ltar bsgom par bgyi /
NK106(me)010:1090: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK106(me)010:1092: gang de la byang chub sems dpa' lus kyi rjes
NK106(me)010:1093: su blta ba'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa rnams
NK106(me)010:1097: da ltar byung ba so sor brtag ste /
NK106(me)010:1098: kye ma lus 'di rgyu dang rkyen las skyes pa
NK106(me)010:1099: mi rtag cing 'gyur ba sgyu ma lta bu ste
NK106(me)010:1100: / lus 'di nga yir mi bya dang /
NK106(me)010:1101: lus snying po med pa la snying po blang bar bya ste /
NK106(me)010:1102: snying po gang de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku bsgrub cing thob par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1103: de ni lus kyi dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1105: tshor ba la tshor ba'i rjes su blta ba'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1106: tshor ba gang ci yang rung ste /
NK106(me)010:1107: bde ba'i tshor ba la dga' bar byed /
NK106(me)010:1108: sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba la zhe sdang bar byed /
NK106(me)010:1109: gnyis ka ma yin pa'i tshor ba la rmongs par byed /
NK106(me)010:1110: bdag gi tshor ba thams cad sgyu ma lta bur rang bzhin med par sbyangs la /
NK106(me)010:1111: sems can thams cad kyi tshor ba rgyun bcad pa'i phyir chos bstan par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1113: rtogs pa'i tshor ba ni bde ba /
NK106(me)010:1114: ma rtogs pa'i tshor ba ni sdug bsngal bar 'gyur bas na /
NK106(me)010:1115: dmigs pa dang yid la byed pa thams cad dang /
NK106(me)010:1116: ji srid chos su btags pa thams cad sgyu ma
NK106(me)010:1117: lta bur shes pa ni tshor ba dran pa nye
NK106(me)010:1118: bar gzhag pa'o // blo gros rab brtan /
NK106(me)010:1119: sems la sems kyis rjes su blta ba'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1120: sems ni skyes nas 'jig cing mi rtog pas //
NK106(me)010:1121: bdag gis thog mar sems bskyed cing //
NK106(me)010:1122: gnas de yang zad cing gang na yang mi gnas pas sems kyis sems mi mthong ngo //
NK106(me)010:1123: de la sems kyi mtshan nyid ni sgyu ma dang 'dra ste /
NK106(me)010:1124: mtshan nyid med pa dang bral bar gnas par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1125: de ni sems dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1127: chos la chos kyis rjes su blta ba'i dran pa
NK106(me)010:1128: nye bar gzhag pa gang zhe na gang stong pa
NK106(me)010:1129: nyid dang / mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1130: smon pa med pa ma gtogs pa'i chos su grub pa rdul tsam yang mi dmigs te /
NK106(me)010:1131: chos de la blta zhing gnas pa ni chos nyid yang dag pa mthong gi /
NK106(me)010:1132: chos su ma yin par yang dag par rjes su mi mthong ngo //
NK106(me)010:1133: de la dran pa nye bar gzhag pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1134: sangs rgyas ji snyed chos su brtags pa thams cad ming tsam /
NK106(me)010:1135: ming de dang chos de dag phyi nang gang du'ang mi rnyed pas //
NK106(me)010:1136: mtha' mi rnyed cing mtha' med cing ma grub pas ni chos dran pa nye bar gzhag pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1137: blo gros rab brtan gyis gsol pa /
NK106(me)010:1138: yang dag pa spong ba gzhi ji ltar blta bar bgyi /
NK106(me)010:1139: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK106(me)010:1141: byang chub sems dpa'i lam gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1142: sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams mi bskyed pa'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)010:1146: yang dag par rab tu 'jog go //
NK106(me)010:1147: sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos skyes pa rnams spang ba'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)010:1151: yang dag par rab tu 'jog go //
NK106(me)010:1152: dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams bskyed pa'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)010:1156: yang dag par rab tu 'jog go //
NK106(me)010:1157: dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa bskyed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1158: bskyed pa rnams gnas pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1159: gnas pa phyir zhing 'phel ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1161: chud mi za ba'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)010:1164: sems rab tu 'dzin yang dag par rab tu 'jog go //
NK106(me)010:1166: gang sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos rnams zhes bya ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1169: shes rab kyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs so //
NK106(me)010:1170: tshul khrims kyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni /
NK106(me)010:1172: tshul khrims nyams par 'gyur ba'i chos rnams so //
NK106(me)010:1173: ting nge 'dzin gyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni /
NK106(me)010:1174: sems g.yeng bar byed cing ting nge 'dzin nyams par byed pa rnams so //
NK106(me)010:1175: shes rab kyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs ni /
NK106(me)010:1177: lta ba la mchog tu 'dzin pas yang dag par sgrib pa chos rnams so //
NK106(me)010:1178: tshul bzhin yid la byed pa ni /
NK106(me)010:1179: mi dge ba'i chos spang ba'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)010:1183: yang dag par 'jog pa ni yang dag par spang ba dang po'o //
NK106(me)010:1184: gang yang mi dge ba'i chos rnams zhes bya ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1188: rgyu gang las byung zhes pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1189: tshul bzhin yid la byed pa ni mi gtsang bas 'dod chags dang /
NK106(me)010:1191: rten 'brel gyis gti mug zhi bar byed do //
NK106(me)010:1192: gang nyon mongs pa de dag tha dad du rtogs pas spong zhes bya yis /
NK106(me)010:1193: gang spong ba de ni rnyed par mi 'gyur bas yang dag par spong ba gnyis pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1194: gang dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams bskyed pa'i phyir 'dun pa bskyed /
NK106(me)010:1197: sems yang dag par 'jog ces bya ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1198: bsgrub par bya ba'i chos dge ba tshad med pa la 'dun pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1199: sems rab tu 'dzin pas nyams su len par byed pa ni /
NK106(me)010:1200: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad kyi rtsa ba ste /
NK106(me)010:1201: yang dag par spong ba gsum pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1202: dge ba'i chos skyes pa rnams gnas pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1204: chud mi za bar bya ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba byang chub tu bsngo ba'o //
NK106(me)010:1206: gang yang dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad khams gsum
NK106(me)010:1207: la mi gnas par thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du
NK106(me)010:1208: bsngosa pas / de la zad par 'gyur ba gang
NK106(me)010:1209: yang med pas yang dag par spong ba bzhi pa'o
NK106(me)010:1210: bsngosa pas / // blo gros rab brtan gyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)010:1211: bcom ldan 'das rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ji ltar blta bar bgyi /
NK106(me)010:1212: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba /
NK106(me)010:1214: byang chub sems dpa'i lam ni bzhi ste /
NK106(me)010:1216: 'dun pa'i ting nge 'dzin spang ba'i 'du byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1217: brtson 'grus kyi ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i 'du byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1218: sems kyi ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i 'du byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1219: spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i 'du byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1221: de la chos thams cad ma grub pa sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK106(me)010:1222: gang du'ang mi dmigs shing 'dzin pa dang bral ba'i
NK106(me)010:1223: chos thams cad la mi sngangs dngangs par mi 'gyur
NK106(me)010:1224: dga' ba dang spro ba dang 'dun par byed pa
NK106(me)010:1225: de ni 'dun pa'i ting nge 'dzin to //
NK106(me)010:1227: gang dad pa rtse gcig pa'i 'dun pa dang ldan
NK106(me)010:1228: pa des 'jig rten gyi chos thams cad kyi brtson
NK106(me)010:1229: pa 'dor zhing le lor gyur pa thams cad kyis
NK106(me)010:1230: mi tshugs par brtson 'grus rtsom pa de ni brtson
NK106(me)010:1233: gang rtsol ba'i rtsom pa rgyun mi 'chad pa dang ldan pa des sems gang du'ang mi dmigs /
NK106(me)010:1234: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba de la rtse gcig pa ni sems kyi ting nge 'dzin to //
NK106(me)010:1236: gang rtse gcig tu gyur pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa des 'gro ba dang 'chag pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1238: nyal ba'i dus thams cad du'ang ting nge 'dzin de
NK106(me)010:1239: las mi 'da' bas spyod pa ni spyod pa'i ting
NK106(me)010:1240: nge 'dzin to // blo gros rab brtan /
NK106(me)010:1241: de la ci'i phyir rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa zhes bya zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1242: ting nge 'dzin des log par 'gyur ba'i chos thams cad spong bar byed /
NK106(me)010:1243: spangs pas dge bar byed de /
NK106(me)010:1244: yang dag pa'i gnas su phyin par byed /
NK106(me)010:1246: ting nge 'dzin gyi rang bzhin rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1247: blo gros rab brtan gyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)010:1248: bcom ldan 'das dbang po lnga gang lags /
NK106(me)010:1249: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba /
NK106(me)010:1250: blo gros rab brtan byang chub sems dpa'i lam la lnga ste /
NK106(me)010:1255: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang po dang /
NK106(me)010:1257: de la dad pa'i dbang po gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1258: 'khor ba na spyod pa 'jig rten pa'i yang dag pa'i lta ba la mngon par dad pa ste /
NK106(me)010:1259: las kyi rnam par smin pa la 'jigs pas srog gi phyir yang sdig pa mi byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1260: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la zhugs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1264: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa sangs rgyas
NK106(me)010:1265: kyi chos thos na the tshom med par dga' zhing
NK106(me)010:1266: dad pa ni dad pa'i dbang po'o //
NK106(me)010:1267: brtson 'grus kyi dbang po gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1268: chos gang la brtson 'grus kyi dbang po skyed par byed de /
NK106(me)010:1269: de ni brtson 'grus kyi dbang po'o //
NK106(me)010:1270: dran pa'i dbang po gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1271: chos gang la brtson 'grus kyis bsdus pa de dag
NK106(me)010:1272: dran pa'i dbang pos chud mi za bar byed pa
NK106(me)010:1273: de ni dran pa'i dbang po'o //
NK106(me)010:1274: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang po gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1275: chos gang dran pa'i dbang pos chud mi za bar
NK106(me)010:1276: byas pa de dag ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang pos
NK106(me)010:1277: rtse gcig tu ma yengs par byed pa de ni
NK106(me)010:1279: shes rab kyi dbang po gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1280: chos gang ting nge 'dzin gyis rtse gcig tu byed
NK106(me)010:1281: pa de dag shes rab kyi dbang pos brtags pas
NK106(me)010:1282: / chos thams cad sgyu ma ltar yongs su ma
NK106(me)010:1283: grub par shes pa de ni shes rab kyi dbang
NK106(me)010:1284: / po'o // blo gros rab brtan gyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)010:1285: bcom ldan 'das stobs lnga gang lags /
NK106(me)010:1288: byang chub sems dpa'i lam lnga ste /
NK106(me)010:1294: dad pa'i stobs gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1295: gang la dad cing mos pa de la gang gis kyang mi bardzi ba ste /
NK106(me)010:1296: de'i drung du bdud kyis sangs rgyas su bsgyur nas 'ong ste /
NK106(me)010:1297: khyod kyi de ni chos ma yin no zhes sgyur bar byed /
NK106(me)010:1298: log par byed kyang 'bral bar mi byed do //
NK106(me)010:1300: de yang 'byung ba chen po rnams gzhan du 'gyur yang srid kyi /
NK106(me)010:1301: dad pa'i stobs la mos pa de ni stobs de
NK106(me)010:1302: las 'bral bar mi nus pas na dad pa'i stobs
NK106(me)010:1303: so // brtson 'grus kyi stobs gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1304: gang brtson 'grus rtsom zhing dge ba'i chos gang dang gang la bstan pa'i stobs kyang /
NK106(me)010:1305: gnas der ma phyin gyi bar du brtson pa'i stobs
NK106(me)010:1306: de sus kyang bzlog par mi nus pas brtson 'grus
NK106(me)010:1307: kyi stobs so // dran pa'i stobs gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1308: chos gang dang gang la dran pa nye bar gzhag pas sems mi g.yeng ste /
NK106(me)010:1309: de la nyon mongs pa gang gis kyang bardzi bar mi nus shing /
NK106(me)010:1310: dran pa'i stobs des nyon mongs pa 'joms pas dran pa'i stobs zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1311: ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1312: dran pa dang bag chags yod pas nyon mongs pas
NK106(me)010:1313: mi bardzi ba de nyid gang du gnas kyang 'du
NK106(me)010:1315: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul thams cad la 'dzin pa'i 'du shes ma zhugs shing /
NK106(me)010:1316: chos gang la'ang rnam par mi rtog ste /
NK106(me)010:1317: 'du 'dzi las dben pa'i stobs thob pas na ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1318: shes rab kyi stobs gang zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1319: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK106(me)010:1320: cad shes rab kyi stobs des yongs su shes nas
NK106(me)010:1321: / 'jig rten pa rnams 'khor ba las sgrol ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1322: shes rab dang ye shes kyi stobs las byung bas na shes rab kyi stobs zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1323: de la ci'i phyir stobs lnga zhes bya zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1324: dbang po lnga bstan zhing de'i stobs rgyas pas na stobs lnga zhes bya'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1325: blo gros 'byung gnas kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1326: byang chub sems dpa' blo gros 'byung gnas kyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)010:1327: bcom ldan 'das byang chub kyi lam yan lag bdun pa ji ltar blta bar bgyi /
NK106(me)010:1329: blo gros 'byung gnas gang dran pa med cing yid
NK106(me)010:1330: la bya ba med pa'i phyir chos thams cad rang
NK106(me)010:1331: gi mtshan nyid kyis stong ste /
NK106(me)010:1332: gang de la chos thams cad ngo bo ma grub
NK106(me)010:1333: par mthong ba de ni dran pa yang dag byang
NK106(me)010:1335: blo gros 'byung gnas gang gi dge ba dang mi dge ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1336: lung du ma bstan pa yang ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:1337: chos su rtogs pa thams cad gang du'ang mi dmigs te /
NK106(me)010:1338: sgyu ma lta bu ni chos rnam par 'byed pa byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK106(me)010:1340: gang gi chos thams cad 'du shes shin tu bshig
NK106(me)010:1341: pa'i phyir khams gsum mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK106(me)010:1342: thams cad mi len mi 'dor bas lam gyi mngon
NK106(me)010:1343: par rtogs pa 'dzin pa dang bral ba la /
NK106(me)010:1344: spro ba dang mi rtog pa'i mos pas brtson pa mi 'dor ba 'di ni /
NK106(me)010:1345: brtson 'grus yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK106(me)010:1346: gang dga' ba dang mi dga' ba thams cad bshig pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:1347: 'du byed kyi chos thams cad la dga' ba mi
NK106(me)010:1348: bskyed par kun nas nyon mongs pa sel ba ni
NK106(me)010:1349: dga' ba yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go
NK106(me)010:1351: gang gi dmigs par 'gyur ba'i chos thams cad rdul
NK106(me)010:1352: tsam yang mi dmigs pa'i phyir chos thams cad la
NK106(me)010:1353: lus shin tu sbyong ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1354: sems shin tu sbyangs pas sgrib pa med pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1355: dmigs pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la sems gnas pa ni /
NK106(me)010:1356: shin tu sbyangs pa yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK106(me)010:1358: gang gi chos thams cad kyi 'dzin pa rnam par bshig pa'i phyir ram /
NK106(me)010:1359: rtogs pa'i phyir sems ni gang la yang mi dmigs te /
NK106(me)010:1360: gang sems mnyam par gzhag cing chos thams cad rtogs par 'gyur gyi /
NK106(me)010:1361: sems mnyam par gzhag pa ma yin dang /
NK106(me)010:1362: sems mnyam par gzhag pas 'tshang rgya yis /
NK106(me)010:1363: mnyam par ma bzhag pas ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:1364: de ltar 'dzin pa dang bral bar mnyam par 'jog pa de ni /
NK106(me)010:1365: ting nge 'dzin yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK106(me)010:1367: gang gis chos thams cad gang la yang gnas par mi byed /
NK106(me)010:1371: gang la yang yid mi bde zhing sdug bsngal mang
NK106(me)010:1372: ba la sogs pa'i chos thams cad la sems mi
NK106(me)010:1373: 'dzin te / 'jig rten gyis sems mi 'phrogs shing /
NK106(me)010:1374: des chos thams cad yang dag par rjes su mthong
NK106(me)010:1375: ba'i btang snyoms can du gyur nas dga' ba thob
NK106(me)010:1376: pa 'di ni / btang snyoms yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag go //
NK106(me)010:1378: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun la de ltar blta bar bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1379: blo gros 'byung gnas kyis gsol ba /
NK106(me)010:1380: bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa'i lam yan lag brgyad ji ltar blta bar bgyi /
NK106(me)010:1381: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba /
NK106(me)010:1382: blo gros 'byung gnas de la chos thams cad mnyam pa 'di ni yang dag pa'i lta ba ste /
NK106(me)010:1383: de la bdag tu lta ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1387: stong pa nyid du blta ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1388: lta ba yang dag pa mi byed do //
NK106(me)010:1389: de la lta ba'i dmigs pa chung ngu nas mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar dang /
NK106(me)010:1390: gang yang rab 'bring tha ma'i lta bar gyur pa
NK106(me)010:1391: thams cad dang bral ba ni yang dag pa'i lta
NK106(me)010:1393: de la rtog pa gang gis rtogs pa spangs par
NK106(me)010:1394: 'gyur ba de yang zhi gnas kyis bsdus pa'i lhag
NK106(me)010:1396: de la chos bzang ngan du rtog pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1398: rnam par rtog pa thams cad spang ba ste /
NK106(me)010:1399: cir yang mi rtog rnam par mi rtog /
NK106(me)010:1400: yongs su mi rtog pa 'di ni yang dag pa'i rtog pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1402: de la tshig gis bdag gzhan thams cad la mi gnod de /
NK106(me)010:1403: de la bdag kyang nyon mongs par mi byed /
NK106(me)010:1404: gzhan yang nyon mongs par mi byed /
NK106(me)010:1405: tshig gang gis chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du
NK106(me)010:1406: nges par ston par byed pa 'di ni yang dag
NK106(me)010:1407: pa'i ngag go // blo gros 'byung gnas /
NK106(me)010:1408: de la las gang zad cing ma grub pa ni las kyi matha'o //
NK106(me)010:1409: de las nyon mongs pa zhi bar 'gyur gyi /
NK106(me)010:1410: nyon mongs pa 'bar ba'i phyir ma yin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1411: las gang nyon mongs pa dang 'bral bar 'gyur gyi /
NK106(me)010:1412: nyon mongs pa bskyed pa'i phyir ma yin pa ste /
NK106(me)010:1415: 'dres pa'i las kyi mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing
NK106(me)010:1416: ma grub pa ni yang dag pa'i las kyi matha'o
NK106(me)010:1418: de la nyon mongs pas mi gos pa ni yang dag pa'i 'tsho ba ste /
NK106(me)010:1419: de la 'tsho ba gang bdag la mi gnod /
NK106(me)010:1420: gzhan la yang mi gnod par chos kyi don rdzogs
NK106(me)010:1421: par 'gyur ba 'di ni yang dag pa'i 'tsho ba'o
NK106(me)010:1423: de la zab cing spros pa dang bral ba 'dus
NK106(me)010:1424: ma byas pa'i chos bsgrub pa ni yang dag pa'i
NK106(me)010:1425: rtsol ba ste / de phyir sems rab tu 'dzin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1429: yang dag pa'i don mngon du byed pa ni yang dag pa'i rtsol ba'o //
NK106(me)010:1431: de la dran pa gang gis nyon mongs pa thams cad kyis go skabs mi rnyed pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1432: de la byang chub kyi yan lag sems dang tshad med pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1433: pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi dran pa ste /
NK106(me)010:1434: dran pa gang gis bdud kyis skabs mi rnyed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1435: dran pa gang gis lam log par mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1436: dran pa sgo ba lta bu'i sems dang sems byung
NK106(me)010:1437: gi mos pa mi dge ba thams cad kyis skabs
NK106(me)010:1438: mi rnyed pa 'di ni yang dag pa'i dran pa'o
NK106(me)010:1439: // blo gros 'byung gnas bdag mnyam pa nyid pas chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK106(me)010:1440: bdag rnam par dag pas chos thams cad rnam par dag pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1441: bdag stong pa nyid pas chos thams cad stong pa nyid du yang dag par snyoms par 'jug la /
NK106(me)010:1442: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gang gi sems skad
NK106(me)010:1443: cig dang ldan pa'i ye shes kyis thams cad mkhyen
NK106(me)010:1444: pa dang / thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis
NK106(me)010:1445: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa 'di ni yang
