NK106(me)010:1448: byang chub sems dpa'i lam yan lag brgyad de de ltar blta bar bya'o zhes gsungs pas so //
NK106(me)010:1449: de ltar lam gyi chos thams cad kyang snang la rang bzhin med pa sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:1451: lha'i bu dag dran pa nye bar gzhag pa rnams ni rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:1452: de bzhin du yang dag par spong ba rnams dang /
NK106(me)010:1453: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa rnams dang /
NK106(me)010:1456: byang chub kyi yan lag rnams dang /
NK106(me)010:1457: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa rnams kyang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:1458: de bzhin du mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang /
NK106(me)010:1459: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang /
NK106(me)010:1462: sangs rgyas kyis ma 'dres pa bco brgyad kyang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:1463: de la lam gyi ngo bo ni zhi lhag zung
NK106(me)010:1464: 'brel gyi thabs dang rtogs pa khyad par can yin
NK106(me)010:1465: te / sgrib pa'i gnyen po dam pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:1467: zhi gnas rab tu ldan pa'i lhag mthong gis //
NK106(me)010:1468: nyon mongs rnam par 'joms pa shes bya ste //
NK106(me)010:1471: bsam gtan med pa la yang shes rab med //
NK106(me)010:1472: shes rab med pa la yang bsam gtan med //
NK106(me)010:1473: gang la gnyis po yod pa srid pa yi //
NK106(me)010:1474: rgya mtsho gnag rjes lta bur 'tshal bar bgyi //
NK106(me)010:1476: de yang tshogs sbyor na mos pas sbyor ba'i sa de /
NK106(me)010:1477: don dam pa'i bden pa rnam kun mchog ldan gyis stong nyid mos pa 'jal zhing /
NK106(me)010:1478: dbang po'i sgo bsdam pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1479: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gtso ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1480: nam gyi cha stod dang cha smad la mi nyal bar brtson pas /
NK106(me)010:1481: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong gi don bsgom zhing /
NK106(me)010:1482: thabs shes rab zung 'brel khyad par can la slob pas /
NK106(me)010:1483: dang po tshogs lam gsum rdzogs pa'i rjes la /
NK106(me)010:1484: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes skye ba'i snga
NK106(me)010:1485: ltas su de dang mthun pa'i ting nge 'dzin rgyud
NK106(me)010:1486: la skyes te / drod ces brjod pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1489: chos kyi mchog rnams rdzogs pa las /
NK106(me)010:1490: nyon mongs par rags pa mgo non zhing 'phags pa'i
NK106(me)010:1491: ye shes dang po skye ba la dngos su phyogs
NK106(me)010:1492: pa'o // de nas mthong lam rnam par mi rtog
NK106(me)010:1493: pa'i ye shes bden pa bzhi'i chos nyid mngon sum
NK106(me)010:1494: mthong ste khams kyi phyogs gcig spang bya kun brtags
NK106(me)010:1495: glo bur ba dag pa'i dus so //
NK106(me)010:1497: lam 'gog pa'i bden pa re re bzhin chos shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1498: chos shes pa la bzod pa rjes su shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1499: rjes su shes pa la bzod pa ste /
NK106(me)010:1500: bzhi bzhi bsdoms pas bcu drug go //
NK106(me)010:1501: chos shes pa ni bden bzhi so so'i chos can gyi rang mtshan mthong ba'o //
NK106(me)010:1502: chos shes pa la bzod pa ni rang mtshan mthong bas mi skrag pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1503: rjes su shes pa ni bden bzhi so so'i chos nyid kyi rang mtshan stong nyid du mthong ba'o //
NK106(me)010:1504: rjes su shes pa'i bzod pa nam mkha' mthong ba la mi skrag pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1505: de dag blo rdzas gcig gis bden bzhi rang bzhin
NK106(me)010:1506: snang stong sgyu ma lta bur bya rdzogs kyi skad
NK106(me)010:1507: cig la mthong tshul bzhi bzhir 'char te /
NK106(me)010:1508: bden bzhi don la chos shes bzhi //
NK106(me)010:1511: rjes bzod bzhi'i rim pa so sor 'char ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:1512: de dag la mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK106(me)010:1513: sdug bsngal la sogs bden pa la //
NK106(me)010:1514: chos shes rjes su shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1515: bzod shes skad cig bdag nyid 'di //
NK106(me)010:1517: de'i dus su mthong spang brgya dang bcu gnyis spang tshul ni /
NK106(me)010:1518: kun brtags kyi nyon mongs pa drug la /
NK106(me)010:1529: tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs la mchog 'dzin /
NK106(me)010:1530: lta ba la mchog tu 'dzin pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1531: de la ma rig pa la sogs pa lta ba
NK106(me)010:1532: ma yin pa lnga po de dang bsdoms pas bcu
NK106(me)010:1533: / de ltar rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa bcu po
NK106(me)010:1534: de 'dod khams na bden bzhi re re la bcu
NK106(me)010:1536: gzugs dang gzugs med gnyis na khong khro ma gtogs
NK106(me)010:1537: pa dgu dgu bden bzhi re re ma byung bas
NK106(me)010:1538: / sum cu rtsa drug pa gnyis te bsdoms pas
NK106(me)010:1539: mthong spangs brgya dang bcu gnyis po spang tshul ni
NK106(me)010:1540: / / mthong lam gyis ye shes skye 'gyur lam gyis rags pa brgyud nas spangs /
NK106(me)010:1541: skye bzhin pas phra ba dngos su spangs /
NK106(me)010:1542: skyes dus nas mthong spangs kyi sa bon ma lus pa 'gag pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK106(me)010:1543: de'i 'og tu sgom lam sa dgu'i dri ma bzhi
NK106(me)010:1544: brgya dang bcu bzhi yang rang rang gi sa'i sbyor
NK106(me)010:1545: ba dang / dngos dang rjes la spang ste /
NK106(me)010:1546: sgom spang gi nyon mongs pa bag la nyal ba'i lhan skyes las phye na drug ste /
NK106(me)010:1553: 'dod khams na nyon mongs pa drug po rnams re re la'ang /
NK106(me)010:1557: de la'ang chen po'i chen po /
NK106(me)010:1563: dgu dgur phye bas drug tshan dgu ste lnga bcu rtsa bzhi /
NK106(me)010:1564: gzugs khams na bsam gtan dang po /
NK106(me)010:1567: bzhi pa rnams su khong khro bor nas nyon mongs
NK106(me)010:1568: pa lnga po rnams la che 'bring dgu dgu ste
NK106(me)010:1569: / 'dod chags la sogs pa bzhi bcu zhe lnga pa lnga bsdoms pas brgya brgyad cu /
NK106(me)010:1574: srid rtse bzhi la brgya brgyad cu ste /
NK106(me)010:1575: khams gong ma'i brgya brgyad cu tshan gnyis la sum brgya drug cu /
NK106(me)010:1576: de'i steng du 'dod pa'i lnga bcu rtsa bzhi bsnan pas sgom spang bzhi brgya dang bcu bzhi'o //
NK106(me)010:1578: sbyor ba dang bar chad med lam gnyis kyi nye rgyu dang por spong /
NK106(me)010:1579: khyad par lam gyis dngos su spong /
NK106(me)010:1580: rnam grol gyis thag bsring dang phra ba 'gag 'gyur gyi tshul gyis spong ngo //
NK106(me)010:1581: de yang sa rab tu dga' ba la sogs pa
NK106(me)010:1582: bcu la sbyin pa la sogs pa'i pha rol tu
NK106(me)010:1583: phyin pa bcu gtso bo la lhag ma dgu 'khor
NK106(me)010:1584: du yod de / dbus mtha' las /
NK106(me)010:1585: khyad par can dang khyad med ni //
NK106(me)010:1586: sa bcu dag tu shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:1589: khye'u rab snang gi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1590: rigs kyi bu de la byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang po la gnas pa'i ltas ni /
NK106(me)010:1591: 'dod na skad cig yud tsam thang cig la ting
NK106(me)010:1592: nge 'dzin brgya rab tu thob cing snyoms par 'jug
NK106(me)010:1593: pa dang / sangs rgyas brgya mthong ba de dag gis byin gyis brlabs par yang shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1594: 'jig rten gyi khams brgya bskyod pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1595: sangs rgyas kyi zhing brgyar 'gro ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1596: 'jig rten gyi khams brgyar snang bar byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1597: sems can brgya yongs su smin par byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1598: bskal pa brgyar gnas par byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1599: sngon gyi matha'i bskal pa brgya dang /
NK106(me)010:1600: phyi ma'i matha'i bskal pa brgya la 'jug pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1601: chos kyi sgo brgya rnam par 'byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1602: lus brgya yongs su ston pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1603: lus re re la'ang byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor brgya
NK106(me)010:1604: brgya yang dag pa'i brtson 'grus rtsom zhing yon tan
NK106(me)010:1606: rigs kyi bu sa gnyis pa la gnas pa ni
NK106(me)010:1607: skad cig yud tsam thang cig la ting nge 'dzin
NK106(me)010:1608: stong thob cing snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1609: sangs rgyas stong mthong ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1610: de dag gis byin gyis brlabs pa yang dag par rab tu shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1611: 'jig rten khams stong bskyod pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1612: sangs rgyas kyi zhing stong du 'gro ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1613: 'jig rten gyi zhing stong snang bar bya ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1614: sems can stong yongs su smin par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1615: bskal pa stong du gnas par bya ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1616: sngon gyi matha'i bskal pa stong dang /
NK106(me)010:1617: phyi ma'i matha'i bskal pa stong la 'jug pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1618: chos kyi sgo stong rab tu 'byed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1619: lus stong yongs su ston pa dang /

NK106(me)010:1731: rigs kyi bu sa bcu pa la gnas par 'dod na skad cig yud tsam thang cig la /

NK106(me)010:1734: chos kyi sprin tshad med pa'i bzod pa thob bo //
NK106(me)010:1739: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos kyi sku las ye shes
NK106(me)010:1740: chos kyi sprin bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan
NK106(me)010:1741: pas chos kyi sprin zhes bya'o zhes gsungs so //
NK106(me)010:1742: de la kha cig sa lam gyi yon tan 'di
NK106(me)010:1743: dag rmi lam spel bsgyur tsam la zer gyi nyin
NK106(me)010:1744: dus med de / tshangs pa kun dag'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1745: sa dang lam gyi yon tan rnams //
NK106(me)010:1746: rmi lam skabs las rtogs par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1748: mdo de ni sa lam gang du bgrod pa'i rmi
NK106(me)010:1749: lam khyad par can de gsungs pa dpe des sa
NK106(me)010:1751: nyin dus yon tan med par bstan pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:1752: yon tan 'di dag nyin mtshan rtag par yod pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:1753: 'di dag gi tshul rgyas par ni shing rta chen por bstan pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:1754: thabs lam sgyu ma bstan zin to //
NK106(me)010:1755: da ni thabs des grub pa'i /
NK106(me)010:1756: ye shes sgyu ma mthar phyin mi slob lam //
NK106(me)010:1757: rgyal ba'i sku gsum phrin las lhun grub ste //
NK106(me)010:1758: dag pa gnyis ldan mngon du gyur pa yin //
NK106(me)010:1759: sa bcu rgyun gyi mtha' mar rdo rje lta bu'i
NK106(me)010:1760: ting nge 'dzin gyi gnas ngan len gyi dri ma
NK106(me)010:1761: mtha' dag bcom pa'i rjes la /
NK106(me)010:1763: spangs rtogs kyi yon tan mthar phyin nas //
NK106(me)010:1764: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i chos sku
NK106(me)010:1765: dag pa nyis ldan gyi ngang las gzugs sku gnyis
NK106(me)010:1766: lhun grub tu snang bas 'khor ba ji srid par
NK106(me)010:1767: don mdzad de / ye shes bla na med pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:1768: 'dus ma byas pa'i dbyings nyid dang //
NK106(me)010:1769: ye shes gnyis su med pa ste //
NK106(me)010:1770: nyon mongs shes bya yang dag pa'i //
NK106(me)010:1771: chos sku dag pa nyis ldan te //
NK106(me)010:1772: mi 'gyur ma skyes mtshan med pa'i //
NK106(me)010:1773: sangs rgyas rnams ni chos kyi sku //
NK106(me)010:1774: de la bzhengs bzhugs mi mnga' yang //
NK106(me)010:1775: sngon gyi sems bskyed bsod nams chos //
NK106(me)010:1776: smon lam bskyed rim rgyu rkyen las //
NK106(me)010:1777: gzugs sku gnyis ni rang shar 'byung //
NK106(me)010:1779: 'dir thub pa mchog dang sbyar nas theg pa chung
NK106(me)010:1780: ngu bas so so skye bo rang rgyud pa gcig
NK106(me)010:1781: gi sku tshe de la lam lnga mngon du byas
NK106(me)010:1782: nas rdo rje gdan du sangs rgyas par 'dod de
NK106(me)010:1784: 'phags pa min yang pha ma dang //
NK106(me)010:1785: nad pa dang ni chos smra dang //
NK106(me)010:1786: skye matha'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK106(me)010:1787: yon ni gzhal du med par gsungs //
NK106(me)010:1791: sngon bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i dus su sangs rgyas zin cing /
NK106(me)010:1792: 'dir sems can gyi don du sangs rgya bar ston pa 'dod de /
NK106(me)010:1793: mdo sde pad+ma dkar po las /
NK106(me)010:1794: rigs kyi bu nga ni bskal pa bye ba khrag
NK106(me)010:1795: khrig mang po 'das pa'i sngon rol du sangs rgyas
NK106(me)010:1798: nga 'das pa'i dus bskal pa grangs med pa'i yang dpag tu med pa 'das pa'i dus na /
NK106(me)010:1799: sangs rgyas dbang po'i tog ces bya bar sangs rgyas so zhes so //
NK106(me)010:1800: gsang sngags rnal 'byor gyi lugs kyi rgyal bu don grub 'og min du byon pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1801: til gyi gong bu kha bye ba lta bu'i sangs
NK106(me)010:1802: rgyas rnams kyis byin gyis brlabs te mngon byang lngas
NK106(me)010:1804: rnal 'byor bla med rgyud las ni /
NK106(me)010:1805: 'og min du rnam snang rdo rje 'chang chen po
NK106(me)010:1806: la dbang zhus nas der sangs rgyas pa'i sprul pa
NK106(me)010:1807: 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir sangs rgya bar 'dod do //
NK106(me)010:1809: gtsang ma'i rigs dag spangs pa yis //
NK106(me)010:1810: 'og min stug po nyams dga' bar //
NK106(me)010:1811: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)010:1812: sprul pa po zhig 'dir sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)010:1814: 'dus pa don yod pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:1815: gsang ba'i gnas mchog 'og min dam par ni //
NK106(me)010:1816: byang chub sems dpa'i mtsho chen dbang phyug des //
NK106(me)010:1817: chos kyi pho brang der ni dbang bskur bas //
NK106(me)010:1818: kun du bzang po rdo rje dbyings kyi skur //
NK106(me)010:1819: byang chub sems kyi rdo rjer byin gyis brlabs //
NK106(me)010:1820: de nyid du ni mngon par byang chub pas //
NK106(me)010:1821: bla med snying po'i rdo rje 'chang du gyur //
NK106(me)010:1822: rang byung bde ba chen por mngon sangs rgyas //
NK106(me)010:1825: khrag chen gyi sangs rgyas bcu gcig de 'og min
NK106(me)010:1826: gyi gnas rdo rje btsun mo'i gzhal yas dbus su
NK106(me)010:1827: dbang bzhi rdzogs zhus nas bud med mchog la brten
NK106(me)010:1828: nas bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob bo
NK106(me)010:1829: // rab tu mi gnas pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:1830: bcu gcig sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang //
NK106(me)010:1831: bud med phyag rgya brten byas nas //
NK106(me)010:1834: de dag kyang theg pa phyogs re'i cha tsam ste /
NK106(me)010:1835: 'dir dpal gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sgyu 'phrul dra ba chen po'i lugs kyis /
NK106(me)010:1836: slob lam rdzogs pa'i rjes la /
NK106(me)010:1837: khams kyi sgrib pa sprin dang 'dra ba mtha' dag spangs nas /
NK106(me)010:1838: khams de dang byang chub ces yon tan ci yin pa sangs rgyas te /
NK106(me)010:1839: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pas don gnyis rdzogs par 'dod de /
NK106(me)010:1841: dri med dag pa'i byang chub ni //
NK106(me)010:1842: 'gyur ba med las dri bral ba //
NK106(me)010:1843: yon tan rdzogs pa'i rang gzugs te //
NK106(me)010:1844: sku lnga ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)010:1847: de tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK106(me)010:1849: gang du'ang sangs rgyas pa'i 'og min de gang na yod ce na /
NK106(me)010:1850: kha cig de gtsang ma ris kyi 'og min du 'dod pa yang mi 'thad de /
NK106(me)010:1851: gtsang ma'i gnas dag spangs pas gnod do //
NK106(me)010:1852: kha cig gtsang ma'i 'og min las grong las dgon pa'i tshod tsam zhes pa'ang mi 'thad de /
NK106(me)010:1853: phyogs dang rgya khyon tshad med pa'i //
NK106(me)010:1855: 'dir ni thog ma sangs rgyas pa'i rang snang dag
NK106(me)010:1856: pa de rig pa'i 'og min yin pas sku dang
NK106(me)010:1857: ye shes dbyings gcig tu brnyes pa der bshad do
NK106(me)010:1858: // ye shes bla na med pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:1859: sems nyid bde chen lhan cig skyes //
NK106(me)010:1860: 'og min gtsang ma'i gnas mchog go //
NK106(me)010:1862: chos kyi dbyings su bstod pa las //
NK106(me)010:1863: 'og min de nyid rnam mdzes pa //
NK106(me)010:1864: shes pa gsum pa gcig nyid du //
NK106(me)010:1867: de'i ngang la gzugs sku rigs lnga sems dpa' la snang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1868: rnam snang gang chen mtsho chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK106(me)010:1869: 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho bsten zhing /
NK106(me)010:1870: 'khor sa bcu pas bskor ba'i gnas ni rgyan stug po bkod pa ste /
NK106(me)010:1871: 'jig med rgyun gyi 'khor lor snang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:1872: 'phags pa sar gnas kyi snang ba dag pa'i phyir 'pho 'gyur gyi 'khrul snang med la /
NK106(me)010:1873: de nang du tshud pa'i zhing khams chung ngu 'jig
NK106(me)010:1874: rten gyi khams rgya mtsho rnams ni chags 'jig tu
NK106(me)010:1875: snang ste / sems can gyi rang snang skye 'jig tu snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:1877: zhing de mi 'jig na de yang mi 'jig par rig ste /
NK106(me)010:1878: 'di yang de'i zhing du bshad pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1879: gnyis ka 'jig rten du bshad pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK106(me)010:1880: lan ni khyed kyis rten dang brten pa'i khyad par ma phyed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1881: snang ba so so ma phyed pa re mtshar /
NK106(me)010:1882: rten gzhi mi 'jig par brjod kyi /
NK106(me)010:1883: brten pa 'jig ces bya ba la /
NK106(me)010:1884: snang ba so so la 'jig mi 'jig tu 'thad pas /
NK106(me)010:1885: de'i 'jig rten 'jig mi 'jig tu bshad de /
NK106(me)010:1886: sems can skye 'jig la zhen pa'i snang ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1887: 'phags pa skye 'jig med pa'i mthong ba'i khyad kyis phye ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:1888: gnyis ka 'jig rten du rdzogs pa'ang /
NK106(me)010:1889: rten dang brten pa'i cha las /
NK106(me)010:1890: rten gzhi mi 'jig kyang brten pa 'jig pa'i phyogs
NK106(me)010:1891: nas de skad rtogs pa tsam las 'og min stug
NK106(me)010:1892: po bkod pa'i zhing khams zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten
NK106(me)010:1895: 'og min stug po nyams dga' zhing //
NK106(me)010:1896: stug pa'i zhing khams 'jig med pa //
NK106(me)010:1897: de nas sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos //
NK106(me)010:1900: de ltar longs spyod rdzogs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:1901: chos dang sprul pa'i sku gsum ngo bo dbyer med cing /
NK106(me)010:1902: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa bsam gyis
NK106(me)010:1903: mi khyab pa'i yon tan mnga' ba de ni ye
NK106(me)010:1904: shes sgyu ma zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:1906: bde gshegs rnams kyi sku de ni //
NK106(me)010:1907: ye shes sgyu mar mi g.yo gsal //
NK106(me)010:1909: bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsten pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1910: nam mkha' sa gzhi gang yin pa //
NK106(me)010:1911: skra rtses gzhal bar nus srid kyi //
NK106(me)010:1912: rgyal ba'i yon tan rgya mtsho ni //
NK106(me)010:1913: bskal pa grangs med brjod mi nus //
NK106(me)010:1914: dpag cing brjod pa'i yul las 'das //
NK106(me)010:1915: de phyir bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK106(me)010:1917: de ltar sgyu ma bzhi nye bar mtshon pa /
NK106(me)010:1918: dpe yi sgyu ma rten 'brel sgyu ma ste /
NK106(me)010:1919: rdzas sngags dag las snang ba'i gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK106(me)010:1920: bden med nyid du chos kun gtan la 'bebs //
NK106(me)010:1921: 'di dag sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i tshul las ni //
NK106(me)010:1922: de la chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa ni /
NK106(me)010:1923: dpe rig sngags dang sbyar ba'i shing bu rde'u rta
NK106(me)010:1924: glang du snang ba ltar rgyu rkyen nang mthun gyi
NK106(me)010:1925: rten 'brel tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:1926: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1927: 'jam dpal sgyu ma ni snang la yod pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:1928: de bzhin du chos thams cad snang la yod pa ma yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)010:1929: tshul 'di dag dpal gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sgyu
NK106(me)010:1930: 'phrul dra ba chen po stong phrag brgya pa las
NK106(me)010:1931: / chos rnams thams cad sgyu ma ste //
NK106(me)010:1932: rang bzhin thabs dang ye shes dang //
NK106(me)010:1933: ma dag sgyu ma rnam pa bzhi //
NK106(me)010:1934: rang byung ye shes dbyings nas gsal //
NK106(me)010:1936: de thams cad sgyu ma mtha' bral du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:1937: ji ltar rdzas dang rigs sngags 'dus pa las /
NK106(me)010:1938: gzhan du snang ba 'khrul bar shes pa ltar //
NK106(me)010:1939: 'gro ba'i 'khrul snang don la med pa ste //
NK106(me)010:1940: bag chags 'khrul pa'i rten 'brel snang ba tsam //
NK106(me)010:1941: snang dus nyid nas stong la ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)010:1942: yod med mtha' las 'das par shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:1943: rigs sngags bzlas pas shing bu rde'u rta glang du snang dus /
NK106(me)010:1944: shing bu rde'u mi snang bar rta glang snang ba de 'dzin na 'khrul par 'dzin pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:1945: 'khor ba'i snang ba thams cad de dang 'dra ste /
NK106(me)010:1946: rang snang 'di yang rdul phran cha med las yod
NK106(me)010:1947: yod ltar snang bas don la med pa gsal snang
NK106(me)010:1948: ste cha med ni snang mi srid /
NK106(me)010:1949: cha med las ma gtogs pa'i rags pa rtsom byed med pa'i phyir 'khrul pa kho na'o //
NK106(me)010:1951: rdo dang sa dang chu la sogs pa khang pa ma yin pa du ma 'dus pa las /
NK106(me)010:1952: khang par snang ba yang rdul phran la ngo bo
NK106(me)010:1953: la ltos nas snang mi rung ba lta bu snang
NK106(me)010:1955: de bzhin du gnyen dang dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1956: dgra dang mi dga' ba dang /
NK106(me)010:1959: byed spyod thams cad la brtags na med la /
NK106(me)010:1960: ma brtags na snang ba'i phyir 'khrul snang med pa gsal ba tsam ste /
NK106(me)010:1961: de yang dpyad na nam mkha' bzhin du dngos po med pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:1962: sgyu ma mtha' bral stong pa'i gzugs brnyan tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:1963: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:1964: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:1965: rang bzhin gyis ni ma skyes pa //
NK106(me)010:1966: stong dang dngos po mtshan ma med //
NK106(me)010:1967: bsam med brjod pa kun las 'das //
NK106(me)010:1969: thams cad sgyu ma'i rol par bstan pa ni //
NK106(me)010:1970: sgyu ma'i yul dang sgyu ma'i grong khyer dang //
NK106(me)010:1971: sgyu ma'i skye bo sgyu ma'i longs spyod dang //
NK106(me)010:1972: sgyu ma'i bde sdug sgyu ma'i skye 'jig dang //
NK106(me)010:1973: sgyu ma'i bden rdzun ji ltar snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)010:1974: 'gro drug snang ba de ltar shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:1975: sgyu ma mkhan gyi sprul pa'i yul dang /
NK106(me)010:1976: skye bo dang bde sdug dang skye 'jig dang /
NK106(me)010:1977: 'gro 'ong dang 'gro drug so so'i gnas dang /
NK106(me)010:1978: longs spyod dang snang ba dang dgra gnyen thams cad de ltar shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:1980: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK106(me)010:1981: ji ltar snang ba thams cad kun //
NK106(me)010:1982: gsal bar snang la rang bzhin med //
NK106(me)010:1983: sgyu ma rmi lam ji bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:1985: thams cad sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du chos mtshungs pa yang /
NK106(me)010:1986: gdod nas dag pas sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK106(me)010:1987: med bzhin snang bas sgyu ma nyid dang mtshungs //
NK106(me)010:1988: rkyen las skyes phyir sgyu ma dang 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)010:1989: bslu zhing 'jig pa sgyu ma lta bu zhes //
NK106(me)010:1990: 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang sgyu mar gtan la phab //
NK106(me)010:1991: 'di ltar snod bcud du snang ba'i sa chu me rlung dang /
NK106(me)010:1992: sems kyi snang ba thams cad gdod ma nas dag pas kyang sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:1993: sgyu ma'i rta glang de yang shing bu rde'u tsam las rta glang gis stong pa bzhin /
NK106(me)010:1994: 'khrul snang yang gzhi med rig pa rang snang tsam las don la ma grub pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:1995: sgyu ma'i rang dus nas rta glang med kyang yod pa ltar snang ba bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:1996: sna tshogs kyi chos su snang dus nas grub ma myong bas kyang sgyu ma dang  'dra'o //
NK106(me)010:1997: rig sngags kyi rkyen dang shing bu rde'u'i rgyu tsam 'tshogs pas rta glang du snang ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:1998: las tha dad kyi rkyen gzung 'dzin dbang gis rgyu
NK106(me)010:1999: ma rig pa la sogs pas 'gro drug tha dad
NK106(me)010:2000: du 'khor zhing snang tshul du ma la spyod pas
NK106(me)010:2003: shing bu rde'u rta glang du snang bas sems 'khrul bar byed pa bzhin du /
NK106(me)010:2004: gzugs sgra dri ro reg la sogs par snang bas
NK106(me)010:2005: sems bslu ba'i phyir 'khrul snang sgyu ma'i rnam pa
NK106(me)010:2007: de ltar chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bu yin
NK106(me)010:2008: yang ma rtogs pa la snying rje bskyed par gdams
NK106(me)010:2009: pa ni / 'di ltar 'gro drug sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du //
NK106(me)010:2010: don la gnas kyang de ltar ma rtogs pas //
NK106(me)010:2011: mtha' med 'khor ba'i grong 'dir rgyun du 'khyams //
NK106(me)010:2012: bde sdug las kyis mnar bas snying re rje //
NK106(me)010:2013: 'khrul snang sgyu mar soms shig skye bo dag /
NK106(me)010:2014: sna tshogs kyi 'khor ba sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du ye nas gnas kyang /
NK106(me)010:2015: ma rig pa bdag tu 'dzin pa'i lta bas med
NK106(me)010:2016: pa gsal snang rdzun pa'i ngo bor ma rtogs shing
NK106(me)010:2018: 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa'i grong khyer mtha' yas par 'khyams te /
NK106(me)010:2019: so so'i las kyis 'khrul snang sna tshogs la spyod pa rnams /
NK106(me)010:2020: snying rje'i yul du 'phags pa rnams kyis gzigs pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2021: 'khor ba sgyu ma dang 'dra ba'i rang bzhin la kun rdzob rgyu'i snying rje sbyang bar bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2023: rab 'bar dgra yi dbang du song //
NK106(me)010:2024: 'ching ba che dang yang dag ldan //
NK106(me)010:2025: zas chen dug dang 'dres pa zhen //
NK106(me)010:2026: lam gol rab zhugs stobs chung ba'i //
NK106(me)010:2027: sems can rnams la snying bartse'o //
NK106(me)010:2029: nyon mongs pa me ltar 'bar ba dang /
NK106(me)010:2030: bdud kyis bar du gcod pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2031: nyon mongs pa dang lta ba'i 'ching ba mi bzad
NK106(me)010:2032: pas 'chings pa mu stegs byed la sogs pa dang
NK106(me)010:2033: / bsam gtan gyi ro la chags pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2034: nyan rang dang byang chub sems dpa' las dang po pa ste /
NK106(me)010:2035: snying rje'i gnas su 'phags pa rnams kyis gzigs pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2036: rtogs pa rnams kyis rtsal sbyangs pa'i gzhir gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2037: gang nas ma byung gang du ma song zhing /
NK106(me)010:2038: gar yang mi gnas chos kun chos nyid dang //
NK106(me)010:2039: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i sgyu ma ru //
NK106(me)010:2040: skal bzang rnams kyis lta bas thag chod cig /
NK106(me)010:2041: chos thams cad gdod ma nas ngo bo nyid med
NK106(me)010:2042: pas ji ltar snang bzhin pa'i dus nyid nas rang
NK106(me)010:2043: bzhin med pa stong pa nyid kyi rol par mkhas
NK106(me)010:2044: pa rnams kyis shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2046: dbang po ngo bo nyid med pa'i //
NK106(me)010:2047: sgyu ma de yang stong pa nyid //
NK106(me)010:2049: thams cad sgyu ma rang snang du bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2050: sems can rang bzhin sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK106(me)010:2051: byang chub rang bzhin sgyu ma'i ngang nyid de //
NK106(me)010:2052: 'khor 'das gnyis med sgyu ma'i rol pa ru //
NK106(me)010:2053: skal bzang rnams kyis de ring shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2054: sems can du snang ba yang sgyu ma lta bu la /
NK106(me)010:2055: sangs rgyas su snang ba yang sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:2056: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba thams cad rig don snang
NK106(me)010:2057: yang gshis rig pa'i rang ngo la ma grub pa
NK106(me)010:2058: sgyu ma'i rol par rang snang ba tsam du shes
NK106(me)010:2059: par bya ste / khri brgyad stong pa las /
NK106(me)010:2060: lha'i bu dag 'khor ba yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK106(me)010:2061: mya ngan las 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2062: sgyu ma gnyis med du thag bcad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2063: rgyal bas chos kun sgyu ma nyid las gzhan //
NK106(me)010:2064: rdul tsam dmigs su med ces gsungs pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2065: gang yang bden med sgyu ma'i chos nyid du //
NK106(me)010:2066: thar pa 'dod pa dag gis shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2067: chos thams cad sgyu ma'i rang bzhin las gzhan du grub pa ci yang med de /
NK106(me)010:2069: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:2070: gang chos su snang ba thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2071: rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu zhes bya'i /
NK106(me)010:2073: rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu yang gzhan no zhes par mi bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2074: chos thams cad sgyu ma'i rang bzhin nyid las gzhan ma yin pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2075: sgyu ma'i rnam grangs bsdu ba las /
NK106(me)010:2077: sgyu ma'i tshul yang 'di ltar rig par bya //
NK106(me)010:2078: byang chub sgyu ma lhun grub 'pho 'gyur med //
NK106(me)010:2079: mi bsdu khyab bdag rtag tu nam mkha' dang //
NK106(me)010:2080: nyi bzhin nor bu lta bur re ba skong //
NK106(me)010:2081: mtha' yas yon tan phrin las rdzogs par rol //
NK106(me)010:2082: dag gsal spros dang bral ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:2083: dbyings ngo bo nyid kyis dag pa la glo bur gyi dri ma thams cad dag pa na /
NK106(me)010:2084: dag pa gnyis dang ldan pa'i sangs rgyas chos kyi sku dang /
NK106(me)010:2085: de'i ngang las gzugs skur rang shar ba ni /
NK106(me)010:2086: byang chub sgyu ma zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2087: sgyu ma lta bu'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2088: byang chub sgyu ma'i rang bzhin te //
NK106(me)010:2089: ye shes kyang ni sgyu ma bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2090: dngos dang dngos po med zhi ba //
NK106(me)010:2091: rdul bral dpe las 'das pa yin //
NK106(me)010:2094: 'khor ba'i sgyu ma mi bden bslu ba ste //
NK106(me)010:2095: mtshan nyid chad la med snang sgyu ma bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2096: 'khrul rtog dag tshe 'khrul snang dbyings su nub //
NK106(me)010:2097: rig sngags bshig las rta glang mi snang bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2098: ma dag 'khrul snang gzung 'dzin gdod mar grol //
NK106(me)010:2099: dag pas stong la ngo bo med pa yin //
NK106(me)010:2100: sgyu ma'i rta glang rig sngags bshig pa las rang log pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:2101: 'khrul snang sgyu ma yang ma rig pa dang gzung 'dzin du zhen pa'i rtog pa dag pa'i tshe /
NK106(me)010:2102: snang yul 'khrul pa dang bcas pa thams cad rang
NK106(me)010:2103: log pa la dbyings su nub pa zhes bya ste
NK106(me)010:2104: / rta glang du snang ba nub pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:2105: de'i phyir 'khrul snang rang gi mtshan nyid chad pa
NK106(me)010:2106: sgyu ma'i snang ba ltar ngo bo nyid med pa
NK106(me)010:2107: yin no // 'khor 'das kyi dbyings sgyu ma ni /
NK106(me)010:2108: gshis kyi sgyu ma chos nyid 'pho 'gyur med //
NK106(me)010:2109: dag dang ma dag kun gyi chos nyid de //
NK106(me)010:2110: rdza snod gser snod nang gi mkha' dbyings bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2111: snod dang snod chag rkyen gyis 'phel 'grib med //
NK106(me)010:2112: de bzhin 'khrul dang grol ba'i rang dus kyis //
NK106(me)010:2113: chos nyid 'phel 'grib bzang ngan med par gnas //
NK106(me)010:2114: 'di ni gnas lugs don gyi dgongs pa ste //
NK106(me)010:2115: de ltar shes na skye bo mkhas pa yin //
NK106(me)010:2116: chos nyid gshis kyi sgyu ma ni //
NK106(me)010:2117: rig pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK106(me)010:2118: dag pa sangs rgyas kyi dus dang /
NK106(me)010:2119: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i dus kyi 'khrul snang dang
NK106(me)010:2120: 'khrul rtog thams cad ma rig pas ma khyab pa
NK106(me)010:2121: med pa ni / bzang por rtog kyang rig pa /
NK106(me)010:2122: ngan par rtog kyang rig pa /
NK106(me)010:2123: sna tshogs su snang yang rig pa la snang ba las gzhan med pas /
NK106(me)010:2124: rig pa thams cad chos nyid du khyab pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2125: dper na rdza snod na'ang nam mkha'/
NK106(me)010:2127: snod bzang ngan du snang yang de'i nang gi nam mkha' bzang ngan med pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:2129: snang ba rig pa la bzang ngan med par shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2131: snod kyi dbye bas nam mkha' rjes song ltar //
NK106(me)010:2132: de bzhin chos nyid rjes su song bar 'dod //
NK106(me)010:2134: 'di ltar rtogs na thams cad kyi dngos gzhir rig
NK106(me)010:2135: pa byang chub kyi sems lhun gyis grub pa mthong
NK106(me)010:2136: bas / spong len dang dgag sgrub med pa'i chos
NK106(me)010:2137: nyid rang bzhin gyis 'byong ba'i phyir mkhas pa chen
NK106(me)010:2138: bas / po zhes bya'o // de'ang snod ma chag pas nam mkha' 'phel ba med la /
NK106(me)010:2139: chag pas 'grib pa med pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:2140: rig pa yang 'khrul pa dang grol ba'i rang dus
NK106(me)010:2141: nyid nas bzang ngan 'phel 'grib med pa'i chos nyid
NK106(me)010:2142: du gnas pa'o // de dag gis gzhi sgyu ma lta bu'i lta ba gtan la phab zin to //
NK106(me)010:2143: da ni lam nyams su blang ba'i rim pa bshad par bya ba ni /
NK106(me)010:2144: gang tshe sgyu ma'i lta ba rtogs rjes su //
NK106(me)010:2145: sgyu ma'i bsgom pa bden med chen po ni //
NK106(me)010:2146: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin sgyu mar gsol ba gdab //
NK106(me)010:2147: sgyu mar chos rnams rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas de'i
NK106(me)010:2148: don bsgom pa'i phyir skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems
NK106(me)010:2149: bskyed pa dang / sgyu mar snyam pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2150: rang nyid lhar bskyed pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2151: spyi bor bla ma bskyed nas yan lag bdun pa bya ba rnams sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK106(me)010:2152: sgyu ma 'byongs par mdzad du gsol //
NK106(me)010:2153: zhes pa'i gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2154: 'di'i dus su mos gus tshad med pa kho na gal che ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:2157: lta sgom bya ba gzhan rnams kyi rang ngo des
NK106(me)010:2158: mi grol bar so so'i las sbyor dang bogs 'byin
NK106(me)010:2159: la sogs pa'i gzhan la ltos pa yin la /
NK106(me)010:2160: bla ma'i mos gus gcig pus sa dang lam gyi
NK106(me)010:2161: rim pa rnams bde blag tu bgrod pa yin te
NK106(me)010:2162: / bla ma'i snang ba ma bral na //
NK106(me)010:2163: sangs rgyas rnams dang 'bral med gnas //
NK106(me)010:2165: g.yo med mos gus zla drug gis //
NK106(me)010:2168: de la bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgom dus su /
NK106(me)010:2169: kha cig na re bla ma rnam pa mir bsgoms te dman pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2170: yi dam gyi lha dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo la sogs par bsgoms te /
NK106(me)010:2171: rdo rje phreng ba dang gur las /
NK106(me)010:2172: rigs lnga 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor du bshad pa'i phyir
NK106(me)010:2173: ro zhes zer ba ni shin tu mi 'thad do
NK106(me)010:2174: // lha sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du 'dus par bshad pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2175: gur las rigs lnga 'dus pa'i ngo bor bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2176: bla ma de sangs rgyas kyi ngo bor ston pa yin gyi /
NK106(me)010:2177: rnam pa bsgyur bar bshad pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:2178: des na bla ma'i rnal 'byor yi dam du bsgoms na /
NK106(me)010:2179: yi dam sgom yin gyi bla ma'i rnal 'byor ma yin pas /
NK106(me)010:2180: bla ma la dmigs pa'i gus pa mi skye ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2181: nyes pa shin tu che bas bla ma'i rnam pa gang bzhugs der bsgoms te /
NK106(me)010:2182: yi dam ji ltar bzang yang mos gus byas pas sangs rgya bar bshad pa med de /
NK106(me)010:2183: bsnyen sgrub las la sbyor dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:2184: bla ma la mos pa mchog tshe 'dir 'grub ste /
NK106(me)010:2185: rgyud sde lnga bcu pa las /
NK106(me)010:2186: g.yo med mos gus zla drug gis //
NK106(me)010:2189: yang kha cig dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba btab pas chog mod /
NK106(me)010:2190: bla mas ci bya snyam na /
NK106(me)010:2191: bla ma ni dkon mchog gsum gyi ngo bo ste /
NK106(me)010:2193: bla ma sangs rgyas bla ma chos //
NK106(me)010:2194: de bzhin bla ma dge 'dun te //
NK106(me)010:2195: kun gyi byed po bla ma yin //
NK106(me)010:2196: 'dir ni bla ma bla med pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2198: de'i phyir rnam pa bla ma'i snang ba kho nar bsgoms te /
NK106(me)010:2199: bla ma'i snang ba ma bral na //
NK106(me)010:2200: sangs rgyas rnams dang 'bral med gnas //
NK106(me)010:2202: mos gus log pa'i 'du shes byung na /
NK106(me)010:2204: bla ma de 'dod chags can du mthong na /
NK106(me)010:2205: 'dod chags 'di khong la rdul tsam yang med pa
NK106(me)010:2206: lta bu'i 'dod chags can 'dul ba'i phyir bstan pa
NK106(me)010:2207: ste / rgyud nas 'dod chags rdo rje zhes gsungs pa /
NK106(me)010:2208: de bla ma 'di yin nges ngo mtshar che snyam du slar dad par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2209: de bzhin du zhe sdang dang gti mug dang nga rgyal dang /
NK106(me)010:2211: ser sna can du mthong dus 'di khong la med /
NK106(me)010:2212: nga rang la yod pa 'dul ba'i gnyen por bstan pa yin /
NK106(me)010:2213: rgyud nas zhe sdang rdo rje dang /
NK106(me)010:2217: ser sna rdo rje zhes gsungs pa de dus 'dir byon pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:2218: ngo mtshar che snyam du slar mos pa cher byed
NK106(me)010:2219: cing nyes pa bshags pas dngos grub thob par nges
NK106(me)010:2221: dngos gzhi phyi nang sna tshogs chos 'di rnams //
NK106(me)010:2222: rgyu rkyen dbang gis sgyu mar snang ba ste /
NK106(me)010:2223: don la mi bden 'al 'ol zang thal du //
NK106(me)010:2224: skad cig skad cig nyin mtshan rtag par bsgom //
NK106(me)010:2225: phyogs dngas shing mtho ba'i sar 'dug ste /
NK106(me)010:2226: gang mthong ba dang thos pa dang dran rtog thams
NK106(me)010:2227: cad sgyu ma rang snang du bsgom pa ni mi
NK106(me)010:2228: rtog go // de las langs pa'i rjes thob tu //
NK106(me)010:2229: chags sdang nyon mongs dgag sgrub ci shar yang //
NK106(me)010:2230: sgyu ma nyid ces bden med stong par sbyong //
NK106(me)010:2231: phyi rol dngos kun sgyu ma nyid dang ni //
NK106(me)010:2232: nang gi kun rtog sgyu ma lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:2233: rkyen las skyes phyir mi bden bslu ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:2234: snang tsam nyid phyir sgyu ma'i dpes bsgom mo //
NK106(me)010:2235: chags sdang dang dgra gnyen dang bde sdug gi snang ba phyi yul snang /
NK106(me)010:2236: nang sems snang thams cad la rkyen las skyes pas kyang sgyu ma /
NK106(me)010:2237: mi bden la bslu bas kyang sgyu ma /
NK106(me)010:2238: med bzhin snang bas kyang sgyu ma'o snyam nas sgyu
NK106(me)010:2239: ma stong pa'i rang gdangs su shes par bya ste
NK106(me)010:2241: ye nas stong pa'i dngos 'di la //
NK106(me)010:2242: mi dgar ci yod dgar ci yod //
NK106(me)010:2243: thob pa ci yod shor ci yod //
NK106(me)010:2244: thams cad nam mkha' 'dra bar ni //
NK106(me)010:2245: bdag 'dras yongs su gsung bar bgyi //
NK106(me)010:2247: de nas mtshan mo'i cha la /
NK106(me)010:2248: nyal tshe'ang sngar bzhin khyad par sgyu ma'i ngang //
NK106(me)010:2249: bden med spros dang bral ba lhod kyis glod //
NK106(me)010:2250: de nas 'phrul ba'i rmi lam ci shar yang //
NK106(me)010:2251: sgyu mar shes pas bden zhen 'jigs dngangs grol //
NK106(me)010:2252: sgyu mar sbyong dang spel bsgyur dag pa'i zhing //
NK106(me)010:2253: sgyu ma lta bu'i bgrod tshul sngar bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:2254: seng ge'i nyal lugs kyis chos thams cad sgyu ma'i ngang la spros bral stong par glod nas /
NK106(me)010:2255: rtsa dbu ma yar sna tshangs bug /
NK106(me)010:2256: mar sna gsang gnas su sleb pa /
NK106(me)010:2257: dkar la srab pa phru ma phus btab pa tsam gyi nang na /
NK106(me)010:2258: mar me 'bar ba cig la dar cig gtad nas
NK106(me)010:2259: rdzas la 'od de je phra las bltar med pa'i
NK106(me)010:2261: dang po rmi lam sgyu mar zin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2263: spel ba dang bsgyur ma dang zhing khams blta ba la sogs sngar bzhin bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2264: rmi lam nying 'khrul la sgyu mar spel sbyong sum 'khrul gyis ci bya snyam na /
NK106(me)010:2266: gzhan yang phan yon tshad med de //
NK106(me)010:2267: rmi lam nub cig zin gyur na //
NK106(me)010:2268: rnal 'byor zla phyed bar du bde //
NK106(me)010:2269: lha klu dri zas mchod cing bstod //
NK106(me)010:2271: ngan song mtsho las sgrol ba'i gru //
NK106(me)010:2274: des ni 'khor ba'i zhen 'dzin rang grol te //
NK106(me)010:2275: sgyu mar grol nas mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
NK106(me)010:2276: sgyu ma lta bur don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)010:2277: de phyir sgyu ma lta bu'i don sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:2278: de'ang gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu ni nyin mtshan du
NK106(me)010:2279: sgyu ma'i lha sku rab tu mi gnas pa gsum
NK106(me)010:2280: la bsgoms pas / slob lam gyi sa pa'i yon tan thob la /
NK106(me)010:2281: mthar thug bar dor longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob nas mya ngan las 'da' ba ste /
NK106(me)010:2282: ye shes gsang ba'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK106(me)010:2283: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams gang yin pa //
NK106(me)010:2284: rmi lam lus kyi bkod pas sbyong //
NK106(me)010:2285: dang po sa yi yon tan rnams //
NK106(me)010:2286: de las 'byung gi gzhan du min //
NK106(me)010:2287: nyin par dang ni rmi lam gyi //
NK106(me)010:2288: 'khrul pa'i bag chags ma dag pa //
NK106(me)010:2289: sa brgyad la yang mi gnas na //
NK106(me)010:2290: pad+ma can la smos ci dgos //
NK106(me)010:2293: nyin par snang stong sgyu ma dang //
NK106(me)010:2294: mtshan mo rmi lam lha yi sku //
NK106(me)010:2295: rang shar de las ma g.yos tshe //
NK106(me)010:2296: de ni rgyal ba longs spyod rdzogs //
NK106(me)010:2297: skad cig bar dor mya ngan 'da' //
NK106(me)010:2298: rgyun la gnas na smos ci dgos //
NK106(me)010:2299: sgyu ma 'od gsal de bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:2300: 'di ni gzhan du brjod mi bya //
NK106(me)010:2302: ye shes mngon par 'byung ba'i rgyud brgyad pa las /
NK106(me)010:2303: sgyu ma chos dbyings kun gzhi ste //
NK106(me)010:2304: sgyu ma lta bu'i chos rnams la //
NK106(me)010:2305: sgyu ma lta bur bsgoms byas na //
NK106(me)010:2306: sgyu ma lta bur mngon sangs rgya //
NK106(me)010:2307: lam lnga pa ni bcu gnyis te //
NK106(me)010:2308: 'di ni gzhan gyis rtogs pa min //
NK106(me)010:2309: gzhan dang rang bzhin 'bras bu'i don //
NK106(me)010:2310: zab dang rgya che dbyer med pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2312: gang tshe chos rnams ngo bo zab pa dang //
NK106(me)010:2313: rang bzhin rgya che sgyu ma'i rol pa gang //
NK106(me)010:2314: gnyis su med pa'i rdo rjer rab rtogs nas //
NK106(me)010:2315: 'gro kun byang chub sgyu ma thob par shog /
NK106(me)010:2316: mkha' dbyings rnam dag byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK106(me)010:2317: sgyu ma'i 'od gsal nyi zla'i snang ba can //
NK106(me)010:2318: ting 'dzin rnam 'dres mkhyen brtse'i 'od stong gis //
NK106(me)010:2319: 'gro ba'i ma rig mun pa sel bar shog /
NK106(me)010:2320: cha shas gang ba ston zla'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK106(me)010:2321: chu nang rnyog dang bral bar snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)010:2322: chos nyid dag pa rdo rje snying po'i mkhar //
NK106(me)010:2323: che ba'i yon tan ma las rdzogs par shog /
NK106(me)010:2324: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:2325: sgyu ma lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas gnyis pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:2326: de ltar sgyu ma'i rang bzhin 'gag pa med par
NK106(me)010:2327: bstan pa'i rjes la chos thams cad 'ong ba med
NK106(me)010:2328: pa mig yor lta bu'i rang bzhin du rtogs par
NK106(me)010:2330: yang 'dir rgyal bas mig yor lta bu zhes //
NK106(me)010:2331: gsungs pa gang de legs par bshad kyis nyon //
NK106(me)010:2332: gang gi tshe chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin
NK106(me)010:2333: med pa nyid 'ong ba med pa mig yor lta
NK106(me)010:2334: bu ste / yum bar ma las /
NK106(me)010:2335: rab 'byor chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis 'ong ba
NK106(me)010:2336: med pa mig yor lta bu'o zhes pa'i don man
NK106(me)010:2338: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i rang bzhin gsum du nges pa las /
NK106(me)010:2339: dang po gzhi 'ong ba med pa mig yor lta bu'i lta bas gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2340: ji ltar gzugs las mig yor snang ba bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2341: sems nyid ngang las bag chags 'khrul ba'i mthus //
NK106(me)010:2342: 'khor ba'i mig yor med snang 'khrul ba grub //
NK106(me)010:2343: gang ltar snang ba de ltar mig yor bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2344: ji ltar rags pa'i gzugs kyi gzhi las grib ma byung ba yang //
NK106(me)010:2345: gzugs de dang rjes su mtshungs par skyes la rnam pa mi 'dra ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:2346: dbyings gdod ma'i rig pa stong gsal lhun grub chen
NK106(me)010:2347: po'i rang gdangs gzugs lta bu de rang ngo ma
NK106(me)010:2348: shes pas gzung 'dzin du 'khrul pa yang /
NK106(me)010:2349: rig pa rang gdangs dang rjes su mtshungs par phung po lnga dang /
NK106(me)010:2353: dbang po gzugs can dang lnga la sogs par snang ste /
NK106(me)010:2354: rnam pa mi 'dra ba kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2355: thogs pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2356: rnam par ma dag pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2357: las dang nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa'i 'khrul snang sna tshogs su shar bas /
NK106(me)010:2358: khams gsum rigs drug so sor rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa las 'khor te /
NK106(me)010:2360: grib ma gzugs kyi dpe bzhin sna tshogs 'khrul ba'i yul //
NK106(me)010:2363: rkyen rnams tshogs na las kyi 'khrul 'khor rab tu 'byung //
NK106(me)010:2365: 'khrul snang las nying 'khrul du 'khor ba yang 'di ltar /
NK106(me)010:2366: mi mkhas bden par zhen pas byis pa bslus //
NK106(me)010:2367: yul lnga'i mig yor gzeb tu bcings pas na //
NK106(me)010:2368: don med bdag tu bzung bas 'khrul la ltos //
NK106(me)010:2369: 'khor ba mig yor gyi ngo bo nyid du ma
NK106(me)010:2370: rtogs pa'i byis pa rtag tu zhen pa'i blo can
NK106(me)010:2371: rnams ni / snang la ngo bo med pa'i gzugs dang /
NK106(me)010:2375: reg bya'i snang yul 'khrul ba rnams la /
NK106(me)010:2376: yid kyi rnam par shes pa zhen cing chags pas /
NK106(me)010:2377: yul la sred cing bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin pas brgyud mar 'khor bar ni /
NK106(me)010:2378: byis pa rang gi rtse mo'i gzugs la don rang mtshan du zhen pa bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:2379: de la 'jig rten gyi snang ba rang bzhin med par ma shes na /
NK106(me)010:2380: snang ba de bslu ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2381: lam lazhugasa pa dag kyang byis pa dang mtshungs pa mang ste /
NK106(me)010:2383: bye ma'i khang bu rdib pa na //
NK106(me)010:2384: byis pa rnams ni ga chad pa //
NK106(me)010:2385: de bzhin bstod dang grags nyams na //
NK106(me)010:2386: bdag gi sems ni byis pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2388: de ltar mig yor lta bu'i snang ba la byis pa chags pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:2389: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis rang bzhin shes pas ngo
NK106(me)010:2390: bo nyid med par rtogs par bya'o zhes gdams pa
NK106(me)010:2391: ni / snang srid snod bcud bde sdug mtho dman rnams //
NK106(me)010:2392: med bzhin snang ba mar me'i grib ma dang //
NK106(me)010:2393: mig btsir ba las gzugs brnyan gnyis pa dang //
NK106(me)010:2394: nyon mongs tshogs mang mtshan mo'i mun pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2395: ma brtags snang la brtags na ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)010:2396: shin tu brtags na rang bzhin mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)010:2397: mkha' 'dra ma skyes gdod ma'i chos nyid du //
NK106(me)010:2398: de ring nyid nas nges par rtogs par gyis //
NK106(me)010:2399: de la snang srid snod bcud kyi bde sdug dang mtho dman thams cad mig yor dang 'dra la /
NK106(me)010:2400: mig yor gyi don ni gzugs kyi rnam pa las /
NK106(me)010:2401: de dag dang grub sde gcig pa'i rnam pa gzhan med snang ba shar ba ste /
NK106(me)010:2402: grib ma dang zla ba gnyis snang dang mun pa la sogs pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2403: mdor na gzugs dngos las gzhan /
NK106(me)010:2404: de'i dper bris pa dang shar ba dang /
NK106(me)010:2405: de'i gzugs brnyan du gyur pa'ang gzugs de la ltos nas mig yor gyi khong du gtogs pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2406: gzugs dngos kyis don byed mi nus pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:2407: chos thams cad brtags na mig yor ltar snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK106(me)010:2408: ma brtags nyams dga' ba'i rang bzhin /
NK106(me)010:2409: shin tu dpyad na rags snang thams cad rdul phran cha med pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2410: phra ba shes pa dang bcas pa ngo bo ngos gzung med pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2411: gang du'ang ma grub nam mkha' lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:2413: chos thams cad mig yor gyi ngo bo nyid du rang bzhin med pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2414: gdod ma nas ngo bo nyid kyis stong pa'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2415: de yang ji ltar zhe na /
NK106(me)010:2417: 'khrul snang gzhi med mig yor lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:2418: rtsa ba bral zhing mtshan nyid kun du chad //
NK106(me)010:2419: brtags pas stong la med bzhin snang ba ste //
NK106(me)010:2420: rang bzhin ma skyes gdod mar rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:2421: de ltar 'khor ba mig yor ltar snang la rang gi mtshan nyid chad pa ste /
NK106(me)010:2422: brtags na stong pa rang snang tsam las gzhan ma yin pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2423: chos nyid gdod ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:2424: de la gdod ma ni chos rnams kyi rang bzhin stong pa nyid de /
NK106(me)010:2425: so so rang gi rig ngor snang yang gshis ngor ma grub pa de la bya'i /
NK106(me)010:2426: dus snga mo zhig tu brtags pa ni ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:2427: de'i phyir gang snang yang rang snang mig yor lta
NK106(me)010:2428: bu gshis rig ngor ma grub pa'i rang gdangs su
NK106(me)010:2430: ye shes snang brgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2431: 'jam dpal mig yor ni snang la rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2432: de bzhin du chos thams cad kyang snang la rang bzhin med pa'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2433: rtsa ba med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK106(me)010:2434: ma rig pa phra ba'i cha tsam des /
NK106(me)010:2435: 'khrul snang ches cher bkra bkra ltar snang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:2436: ji ltar thag ring mya ngam thang dkyil na //
NK106(me)010:2437: chung ngu'ang chen por snang ba nyid bzhin du //
NK106(me)010:2438: bdag med bdag tu 'dzin pa chung ngu las //
NK106(me)010:2439: 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang chen po 'di dag snang //
NK106(me)010:2440: chung ngu chen por snang bas cir yang 'khrul ba ste /
NK106(me)010:2441: dper na mya ngam gyi thang shin tu chen po rgyang ma na /
NK106(me)010:2443: g.yag ri tsam du snang ste /
NK106(me)010:2444: thang ka skam zhing tsha ba'i gdung bas gdung zhing /
NK106(me)010:2445: yid mi bde bas gdung zhing bar thang ring bas rkyen byas nas snang ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:2446: bdag tu 'dzin pa rtsa ba'i ma rig pa chung ngu las /
NK106(me)010:2447: kun brtags pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2449: las tha dad pas rkyen byas te /
NK106(me)010:2450: sna tshogs snang ba'i snod bcud kyis 'khrul pa nam mkha'i mtha' klas khyab pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2451: rtsa ba phra mo las byung ba /
NK106(me)010:2452: de yang dpyad na rtsa ba med pa'i rang bzhin sems nyid rnam par dag pa la thug ste /
NK106(me)010:2454: rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK106(me)010:2455: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK106(me)010:2457: gzhi dang rtsa ba phra zhing bstan du med pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2458: chu'i rnyog ltar bzhag pas dngas par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2459: 'khrul bar snang 'di rtogs na dngos med de //
NK106(me)010:2460: mkha' bzhin byed pa med par mngon pa na //
NK106(me)010:2461: med snang mig yor lta bu'i srid pa las //
NK106(me)010:2462: don med bdag tu ma 'dzin ji bzhin zhog /
NK106(me)010:2463: mig yor ni sus kyang spong bar mi byed de /
NK106(me)010:2464: gzugs log pas rang log pa ltar 'khor ba'i 'khrul
NK106(me)010:2465: snang 'di yang spong du med de dngos po med
NK106(me)010:2466: pa'i phyir / 'dzin pa log pas rang bzhin gyis rtog la /
NK106(me)010:2467: 'dzin pa ni ji bzhin du bzhag na rtogs pa yin te /
NK106(me)010:2469: gang 'du shes thams cad bshig pa de la ni /
NK106(me)010:2470: gzung ba'am 'dzin pa yod pa lta ga la 'gyur zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2471: gang snang bsam brjod dmigs su med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2472: ngang yin ye yin gdod nas dag pa yin //
NK106(me)010:2473: gar yang ma 'dzin cir yang ma rtog cig /
NK106(me)010:2474: ngo bo ngos gzung med pa'i snang ba la //
NK106(me)010:2475: phyogs ris zhen pa'i gzeb kyis ci byar yod //
NK106(me)010:2476: de bas ched du dmigs pa kun btang ste //
NK106(me)010:2477: gang snang bden pas stong par shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2478: snang srid kyi chos thams cad ngo bo nyid med pa snang ba mig yor dang 'dra ba la /
NK106(me)010:2479: 'jig rten gyi snang ba ltar dgag sgrub bden zhen chags sdang la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2480: grub matha'i snang ba ltar rgyu 'bras snang stong /
NK106(me)010:2482: phung po khams dang skye mched du 'byed pa'i phyogs ris thams cad spangs la /
NK106(me)010:2483: rig ngor snang yang snang thog tu 'dzin pa ma
NK106(me)010:2484: zhugs par rang gsal zang ka rjen par thal le
NK106(me)010:2485: shes par bya ba ni gnas lugs kyi don te
NK106(me)010:2486: / skye med rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK106(me)010:2487: gar yang ma rtog cir yang ma bsams shig /
NK106(me)010:2488: bcas bcos ma byed rang bzhin lhug par zhog /
NK106(me)010:2489: ma bcos pa de skye med rin chen mdzod //
NK106(me)010:2490: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi gshegs shul lags //
NK106(me)010:2492: gzhi gtan la phab zin to //
NK106(me)010:2493: lam nyams su blang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:2494: de ltar chos kun mig yor ltar rtogs nas /
NK106(me)010:2495: sems nyid don la ji bzhin blo gzhag bya //
NK106(me)010:2496: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin mig yor gsol ba gdab //
NK106(me)010:2497: chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par rtogs
NK106(me)010:2498: bzhin mnyam par gzhag pa de yang sngar bstan pa
NK106(me)010:2499: bzhin bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgoms nas /
NK106(me)010:2500: mig yor lta bu'i rang bzhin 'byongs par mdzad du
NK106(me)010:2501: gsol zhes gsol ba gdab pa sngon du 'gro bar
NK106(me)010:2503: dngos gzhi chos kun mig yor ltar bsgoms te /
NK106(me)010:2504: gzugs ni bden pas stong ste mig yor 'dra //
NK106(me)010:2505: sgra ni grag pas stong ste mig yor bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2506: dri ro reg kyang mig yor dang 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)010:2507: yid dang chos kyang mig yor lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:2508: gang yang bden pa med pa'i ngang nyid du //
NK106(me)010:2509: blo yang 'dzin zhen med par glod la gzhag /
NK106(me)010:2510: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul drug dang /
NK106(me)010:2511: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po drug dang /
NK106(me)010:2512: mig gi rnam par shes pa la sogs pa tshogs drug dang /
NK106(me)010:2513: snang brtags kyi chos thams cad mig yor ltar bden
NK106(me)010:2514: pa med pa'i ngang la dran rtog med par mnyam
NK106(me)010:2516: gang yid la byed pa thams cad ni mi dge ba'o //
NK106(me)010:2517: gang yid la mi byed pa de ni dge ba'o //
NK106(me)010:2518: gang dran pa med cing yid la byed pa med
NK106(me)010:2519: pa ni sangs rgyas rjes su dran pa'i zhes pa'i
NK106(me)010:2520: don to // mtshan mo rnal 'byor du bya ba'i chos ni /
NK106(me)010:2521: nyin bzhin mnal tshe'ang snying gar sems bzung la /
NK106(me)010:2522: chos kun mig yor 'dra ba'i ngang der nyal //
NK106(me)010:2523: rmi lam zin sogs sngar bzhin nges par 'char //
NK106(me)010:2524: snying gar 'od lnga'i gong bu las mthar gtad med ngang las nyal bas /
NK106(me)010:2525: rmi lam du mig yor lta bu'i chos su rtogs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2526: sprul pa dang bsgyur ba la sogs sngar dang 'dra bar 'char ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:2528: nyams rtogs snang ba'ang mig yor lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:2529: gang la'ang bden med rtogs pa shugs las 'byung //
NK106(me)010:2530: 'dzin med zang ka dgag sgrub 'khrul pa 'jig /
NK106(me)010:2531: spyan dang mngon shes ting 'dzin yon tan 'grub //
NK106(me)010:2532: rgyal ba'i chos mdzod 'gro kun 'dren pa yin //
NK106(me)010:2533: de phyir mig yor lta bu'i don sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:2534: de la gnas skabs su mig yor du rtogs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2535: de'i nyams la 'khrul par zhen pa'i blo zhig ste /
NK106(me)010:2536: 'khor ba las nges par 'byin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2537: ting nge 'dzin grub pas spyan dang mngon par shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2540: bsam gtan gyis ni 'dod pa'i yon tan smad pa 'dor //
NK106(me)010:2541: rig dang mngon par shes dang ting 'dzin mngon par 'grub //
NK106(me)010:2543: de la nyams ni du ba 'dra ba la //
NK106(me)010:2544: rtogs pa ni me lta bu ste /
NK106(me)010:2545: rig pa'i rang ngo gzhi med zang kar rtogs pa ni rtogs pa /
NK106(me)010:2546: rtogs pa'i ngang las ma yengs pas /
NK106(me)010:2547: bde gsal mi rtog pa la sogs pa'i nyams su 'char ro //
NK106(me)010:2548: gang dang gang gi yin lugs rtogs pas rtogs pa /
NK106(me)010:2549: de nyid goms pa las lus sems kyi drod rnyed pas nyams zhes bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2550: mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni chos thams cad kyi
NK106(me)010:2551: rang bzhin mig yor ltar gzhi med stong pa'i gnas
NK106(me)010:2552: lugs rtogs pas / 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ste /
NK106(me)010:2553: mya ngan las 'das pa thob pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2555: shes rab kyis ni chos ni rang bzhin yongs shes nas //
NK106(me)010:2556: khams gsum ma lus pa las yang dag 'da' bar 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:2558: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i chos 'di dag /
NK106(me)010:2559: med snang stong pa'i gzugs su thag chod de //
NK106(me)010:2560: ma skyes spros dang bral ba'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK106(me)010:2561: ma lus 'gro kun nyer zhi'i gnas thob shog /
NK106(me)010:2562: gzung 'dzin mig yor 'dra ba 'jig la khad //
NK106(me)010:2563: 'khrul snang ma rig mun pa sangs sangs 'dra //
NK106(me)010:2564: rang byung 'od gsal nyi ma khong nas shar //
NK106(me)010:2565: bdag bzhin gzhan yang gnas lugs bden mthong shog /
NK106(me)010:2566: yod par snang bas chos rnams sna tshogs kyang //
NK106(me)010:2567: med par snang bas gnyis 'dzin 'khrul ba zhig /
NK106(me)010:2568: gnyis med mnyam pas zang thal chig rdzogs su //
NK106(me)010:2569: ma lus 'gro kun phyam gcig grol bar shog /
NK106(me)010:2570: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:2571: mig yor lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas gsum pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:2572: de ltar 'ong ba med pa las /
NK106(me)010:2573: 'gro ba med pa'i ngo bo nyid du chos thams cad smig rgyu ltar bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2574: yang 'dir rgyal bas smig rgyu lta bu zhes //
NK106(me)010:2575: gsungs pa de yang ji bzhin bshad kyis nyon //
NK106(me)010:2576: 'di ltar snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK106(me)010:2577: snang la rang bzhin med pa smig rgyu lta bu
NK106(me)010:2579: rab 'byor chos thams cad gdod ma nas 'gro ba
NK106(me)010:2580: med pa'i phyir smig rgyu lta bu'o zhes gsungs pa'i
NK106(me)010:2581: don gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu gsum gyis bstan
NK106(me)010:2582: pa las / dang po gzhi 'gro ba med pa'i
NK106(me)010:2583: smig rgyu lta bu lta bas thag bcad pa ni
NK106(me)010:2584: pa las / / ji ltar sos ka'i nyi ma phyed dus na //
NK106(me)010:2585: thang rnams smig rgyu chu yi phung po bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2586: sems la bdag 'dzin shin tu goms pa'i mthus //
NK106(me)010:2587: srid pa'i 'khrul snang smig rgyu lta bur snang //
NK106(me)010:2588: sos ka'i tshe thang ka ring po'i steng thams cad na nyi ma'i 'od zer shar ba dang /
NK106(me)010:2589: rang gi mig tsha bas gdung ste bad kan 'phur byed kyi rlangs 'gyur ba gnyis bsdongs pa las /
NK106(me)010:2590: chu'i 'bab srol ltar snang yang chu ni med do //
NK106(me)010:2591: de bzhin du rig pa'i ngo bo gdod ma nas dag pa'i rang bzhin yang //
NK106(me)010:2592: rkyen bdag tu rtog pa'i cha phra mo dang /
NK106(me)010:2593: rang gdangs yul du snang ba'i thang ka 'jam po stong pa las /
NK106(me)010:2594: 'khrul snang smig rgyu'i chu ltar rang shar nas /
NK106(me)010:2595: khams gsum rigs drug tu 'khor ba yang /
NK106(me)010:2596: rang bzhin med pa'i gzugs brnyan med pa gsal bar snang ba tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2597: 'phags pa ting 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2598: ji ltar sos ka'i nyi ma phyed dus na /
NK106(me)010:2599: skyes bu skom pas gdung zhing 'gro ba dag /
NK106(me)010:2600: smig rgyu la ni chu yi phung por mthong //
NK106(me)010:2601: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:2603: ji ltar snang bzhin pa'i dus nas ngo bo nyid med do zhes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2604: 'di la ngo bo ngos gzung 'ga' med de //
NK106(me)010:2605: rang bzhin gnyis med stong pa zhi ba'i chos //
NK106(me)010:2606: ma skyes nam mkha' 'dra zhing bdag med la //
NK106(me)010:2607: skye med bsam yul 'das pa shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2608: snang bzhin pa'i ngo bo nyid la rdul phran dang /
NK106(me)010:2611: dbyibs la sogs pa rtogs pa na /
NK106(me)010:2612: phyi dang nang gi chos thams cad nam mkha' dang 'dra bar mthong ste /
NK106(me)010:2613: 'phags pa dkon mchog sgron ma'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2614: chos rnams thams cad bde bar gshegs dang 'dra //
NK106(me)010:2616: phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2617: ma rig nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NK106(me)010:2618: chos rnams thams cad mtshan nyid med //
NK106(me)010:2620: snang ba nyid nas stong pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:2621: rang bzhin med par bstan pa ni //
NK106(me)010:2622: ji ltar snang 'di snang ba'i dus nyid nas //
NK106(me)010:2623: skye bar snang yang ma skyes smig rgyu la //
NK106(me)010:2624: gnas par snang yang ma skyes smig rgyu 'dra //
NK106(me)010:2625: 'gag par snang yang mi 'gag smig rgyu bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2626: snang la rang bzhin med par shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2627: 'di ltar sna tshogs su snang ba'i dus nyid nas /
NK106(me)010:2628: de rang gi ngo bo ma grub ste /
NK106(me)010:2629: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten chags pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2630: me tog la sogs skye ba dang /
NK106(me)010:2631: nang bcud kyi sems can kun du rtogs pa thams
NK106(me)010:2632: cad skye bar snang dus nyid nas skye ba med
NK106(me)010:2633: de / skyes pa yul dang skyer snang rig pa'i ngo bor ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2634: de bzhin du yod yod sra sra ltar gnas par
NK106(me)010:2635: snang dus nyid nas gnas pa dang gnas mkhan ma
NK106(me)010:2637: 'jig rten zhig nas stong pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2638: sems can du rtog tshogs 'gro bar snang dus nyid nas 'gag pa dang 'gro ba med pas /
NK106(me)010:2639: smig rgyu'i chu ltar snang la rang bzhin med par shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2641: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)010:2642: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsang //
NK106(me)010:2643: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK106(me)010:2644: skyes tsam nyid nas skye ba med //
NK106(me)010:2645: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)010:2646: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)010:2647: gnas pa med la thams cad gnas //
NK106(me)010:2648: gnas tsam nyid nas gnas pa med //
NK106(me)010:2649: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK106(me)010:2650: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK106(me)010:2654: tshul de lta bu'i ngo bo nyid las spyod pa rnam sbyong gi chos su bstan pa yang /
NK106(me)010:2655: dga' dang mi dga' bde sdug bzang ngan kun //
NK106(me)010:2656: smig rgyu 'dra zhing stong la bdag med de //
NK106(me)010:2657: phyi nang snang srid chos kun smig rgyu 'dra //
NK106(me)010:2658: med bzhin snang la rang bzhin gdod nas dag /
NK106(me)010:2659: ye stong mtha' dbus med ces rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:2660: phyi nang gi chos rnams rang bzhin med pa yin
NK106(me)010:2661: pa'i phyir dgag sgrub dang dgra gnyen la sogs pa
NK106(me)010:2662: thams cad la rang grol smig rgyu 'dra bas lam
NK106(me)010:2663: du bya zhing / gdod ma nas stong pa'i rang gdangs shar ba tsam du rtogs par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2665: gnyis med gnyis su 'dzin pa'i smig rgyu bzhin //
NK106(me)010:2666: don med dgag sgrub zhen pas ma 'chings par //
NK106(me)010:2667: rang sems gnyis med smig rgyu lta bur ltos //
NK106(me)010:2668: 'di ni dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yin //
NK106(me)010:2669: bdag gzhan dgag sgrub tu zhen pa rang mtshan pa mi rig ste /
NK106(me)010:2670: chos thams cad smig rgyu ltar snang la rang bzhin ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:2671: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2672: 'jam dpal smig rgyu ni snang la rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2673: de bzhin du chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2674: lam nyams su blang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:2675: de nas ji ltar bsgom pa'i rim pa yang /
NK106(me)010:2676: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin smig rgyu'i gsol ba gdab //
NK106(me)010:2677: bla ma'i rnal 'byor sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK106(me)010:2678: chos thams cad smig rgyu lta bur 'byongs par mdzad du gsol zhes khyad par du bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2680: dngos gzhi chos kun smig rgyu lta bu'i ngang //
NK106(me)010:2681: sems kyi 'byung 'jug re dogs bral bar gzhag /
NK106(me)010:2682: mtshan mo'ang sngar bzhin brtags na smig rgyur 'char //
NK106(me)010:2683: nyin par gyi snang ba smig rgyu yin la /
NK106(me)010:2684: rang bzhin ci yang med do snyam nas sems phyir 'byung ba 'phro ba dang /
NK106(me)010:2685: nang du 'jug pa yid rtse gcig sdud pa med pa'i ngang la glod nas /
NK106(me)010:2686: rig pa'i rang gdangs ngos bzung la yang yang du skyong ngo //
NK106(me)010:2687: mtshan mo'i dus su sngar bzhin nyal ba las /
NK106(me)010:2688: rtsa dbu ma gcig tu gsal gdab pa'i ngang la
NK106(me)010:2689: gnyid log pas smig rgyu lta bu'i rmi lam zin
NK106(me)010:2690: nas sprul bsgyur nus pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2691: nye 'khor du mthong thos ma 'gags la gnyid ma sad pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2692: du ba dang smig rgyu dang me khyer la sogs pa'i snang ba dpag tu med pa 'char ro //
NK106(me)010:2694: gang la'ang ma zhen bdag 'dzin ngang gis grol //
NK106(me)010:2695: gzungs sprin mngon shes ting 'dzin khong nas 'char //
NK106(me)010:2696: rgyal ba'i go 'phang myur du 'grub pas na //
NK106(me)010:2697: rang bzhin smig rgyu lta bu'i don sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:2698: gnas skabs su chos thams cad smig rgyu ltar rtogs pas chags sdang las grol zhing /
NK106(me)010:2703: de la tshig don gyi chos 'dzin pa mi brjed par bstan pa'i phyir gzungs te /
NK106(me)010:2704: su si tu ka ra legs par grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:2705: gzungs ni gang phyir rnam gsum gzungs //
NK106(me)010:2706: tshig dang don dang gnyis ka dang //
NK106(me)010:2707: legs pa las ni nyams pa las //
NK106(me)010:2708: 'dzin pa'i phyir na gzungs zhes bya //
NK106(me)010:2710: ting nge 'dzin rig pa'i ngang dngas rtse gcig pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2711: don gang la mnyam gzhag gi ngang rtse gcig pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2713: gser gyi kha dog lta bu'i sku lus kyi //
NK106(me)010:2714: 'jig rten mgon po kun nas rab mdzes pa //
NK106(me)010:2715: dmigs pa 'di la gang gis sems 'jog pa //
NK106(me)010:2716: byang chub sems dpa' de mnyam gzhag ces bya //
NK106(me)010:2718: spyan ni sgrib pas chod pa'i pha rol thogs med du mthong ba la sogs pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2719: mngon shes ni tshe rabs shes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK106(me)010:2720: don ci yin pa mngon du shes pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2721: rnam grol yon tan mtsho chen las 'khrungs pa //
NK106(me)010:2722: dpag med zhing gi dam pa skye dgu'i gtso //
NK106(me)010:2723: ma lus bde 'byung bde gshegs dbang po dang //
NK106(me)010:2724: skal pa gcig pas bdud rtsi thob par shog /
NK106(me)010:2725: dag pa zhing khams rin chen sa gzhi la //
NK106(me)010:2726: gzhal med khang brtsegs yid 'ong nyams dga' bar //
NK106(me)010:2727: chos rnga sgrogs pas sems gtsang rnyog pa med //
NK106(me)010:2728: 'od dpag med pa'i gnas rab mthong bar shog /
NK106(me)010:2729: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin dag pa'i dngos //
NK106(me)010:2730: ma skyes stong pa'i tshul 'dir kun zhugs te //
NK106(me)010:2731: 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang phyam gcig stongs nas ni //
NK106(me)010:2732: zag med zhi ba mya ngan 'das thob shog /
NK106(me)010:2733: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:2734: smig rgyu lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas bzhi ba'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:2735: de ltar chos thams cad 'gro 'ong med par bstan pa'i rjes la /
NK106(me)010:2736: snang bzhin pa'i ngo bo khyad par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2737: chu'i zla ba ltar snang la rang bzhin med do zhes bshad pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2738: yang 'dir rgyal bas chu zla lta bu zhes //
NK106(me)010:2739: ji skad gsungs de nyams su blang phyir bshad //
NK106(me)010:2740: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK106(me)010:2741: cad snang yang rjes su ma chad pa chu'i zla
NK106(me)010:2744: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni snang yang rjes su
NK106(me)010:2745: ma chad pa'i phyir chu'i zla ba lta bu'o zhes
NK106(me)010:2746: pa'i don rnams nyams su blang ba la /
NK106(me)010:2747: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i dbye ba rnam pa gsum du gnas pa las /
NK106(me)010:2748: dang po la snang yang rang bzhin med pa'i gzhi bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2749: sems nyid zab cing dngas pa'i mtsho dbus su //
NK106(me)010:2750: lhun grub gzugs brnyan ye shar gnas mod kyang //
NK106(me)010:2751: gzung 'dzin rba rlabs rnyog pa'i dri ma yis //
NK106(me)010:2752: gsal bar ma gyur rtog pa'i rlung gis dkrugs //
NK106(me)010:2753: 'jig rten rmongs pa bdag 'dzin las byung bas //
NK106(me)010:2754: ye shes mi gsal mi shes nyon mongs te //
NK106(me)010:2755: thog mtha' dus med 'khor bar bying gyur te //
NK106(me)010:2756: sems nyid rang bzhin dag pa'i mtsho dbus lta bu na //
NK106(me)010:2757: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i rten //
NK106(me)010:2758: sangs rgyas kyi chos gang g+aa'i klung bye ma snyed
NK106(me)010:2759: lhun grub chen por ye ldan du yod pa las
NK106(me)010:2760: / lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas gzhi byas /
NK106(me)010:2761: kun du brtags pa'i ma rig pas gzung 'dzin du g.yos pa'i rlabs kyis /
NK106(me)010:2762: dbyings kyi yon tan gza' skar dngas pa'i gzugs brnyan mi gsal bar /
NK106(me)010:2763: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis sna tshogs kyi 'khrul snang gsal bar gyur nas /
NK106(me)010:2766: rgya che ba dang dngas pa dang //
NK106(me)010:2767: ye shes gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:2768: dbyings ni dag pa'i rgya mtsho 'dra //
NK106(me)010:2769: ma rig gzung 'dzin rlung dag gis //
NK106(me)010:2770: dkrugs pas rnyog pa can du byas //
NK106(me)010:2772: de ltar 'khrul nas sna tshogs su snang ba'i dus
NK106(me)010:2773: 'di'i snang ba'ang chu'i zla ba 'dra'o zhes bstan pa
NK106(me)010:2774: ni / ji ltar chu gtsang nang gi gza' skar gzugs //
NK106(me)010:2775: dngas la mi g.yo med bzhin snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)010:2776: 'khrul snang gzugs brnyan sems chur shar ba'i gzugs //
NK106(me)010:2777: med bzhin snang 'di 'gro kun nyam re thag /
NK106(me)010:2778: chu dngas pa'i rdzing bur gza' skar gyi gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:2779: gang gi sems dngas pa'i chu dbang po dngas pa'i
NK106(me)010:2780: sgor phyi dang nang gi chos gzugs la sogs pa
NK106(me)010:2781: drug gi snang ba gzugs brnyan dang 'dra ba shar
NK106(me)010:2782: ba la bden par zhen pas sems 'khrul te /
NK106(me)010:2783: de la chu dngas pa ltar dbang po dang sems la /
NK106(me)010:2784: gza' skar thog ma med pa'i bag chags dran pa'i
NK106(me)010:2785: yul snang sems dang gzhan du ma grub pa'i cha
NK106(me)010:2786: gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar snang yul de gzung 'dzin
NK106(me)010:2787: gyi nang gi shes pa la shar ba la chags
NK106(me)010:2788: sdang dgag sgrub tu zhen pas bcing bar byed do
NK106(me)010:2790: ji ltar nam mkha' dngas la zla shar ba //
NK106(me)010:2791: de yi gzugs brnyan dngas pa'i mtshor snang yang //
NK106(me)010:2792: zla ba chu yi nang du 'phos pa med //
NK106(me)010:2793: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:2795: 'di ni snang yul bag chags brtan pa'i rang gzugs /
NK106(me)010:2796: sgo lnga'i dbang po la gzugs brnyan gnyis par snang
NK106(me)010:2797: ba yid kyis ma bzung na rang bzhin gyis gos
NK106(me)010:2798: pa med par bstan pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:2799: snang srid chu zla'i tshul la rang gi rtogs pa'i
NK106(me)010:2800: nges pas ngo bo nyid med par bsgrags pa ni
NK106(me)010:2801: / 'di ci'i dngos po ma yin ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)010:2802: mtshan mar ma yin mtshan ma med ma yin //
NK106(me)010:2803: yod med ma yin bden rdzun mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)010:2804: gzugs brnyan nyid ces gsung de thog tu babs //
NK106(me)010:2805: chu'i zla ba'i dpes chos su snang ba 'di dag la bltas pa gang gi tshe /
NK106(me)010:2806: dngos snang 'di dag rdul phran ma yin pa'i stong gzugs su mthong ste /
NK106(me)010:2811: bden pa dang rdzun pa'i rang bzhin gang du yang ma grub par rtogs te /
NK106(me)010:2812: 'di ci sngon dang mi 'dra ba'i snang ba ngo mtshar snyam du dgod bro bas /
NK106(me)010:2813: snang la rang bzhin med pa'o zhes gzod rtogs par mthong ste /
NK106(me)010:2814: bcom ldan 'das la mchog tu gus pa skyes te /
NK106(me)010:2815: snying po mchog las chos thams cad ngo bo nyid
NK106(me)010:2816: kyis stong pa'i phyir chu'i zla ba lta bu'o zhes
NK106(me)010:2817: so // chos gang dag chu'i zla ba lta bu zhes bshad pa /
NK106(me)010:2818: gzugs sogs drug po chu zla lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:2819: med la snang phyir ngo bo ma grub phyir //
NK106(me)010:2820: rnam pa ma 'gags 'khrul ngor snang ba'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:2821: mig dang mig dbang mig shes la sogs drug /
NK106(me)010:2822: chu zla 'dra zhing stong la gsog dang gsob //
NK106(me)010:2823: ya ma barla 'dra chu shing snying po med //
NK106(me)010:2824: rnam kun bden pas stong zhes rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:2825: gzugs la sogs pa yul drug dang /
NK106(me)010:2826: mig la sogs pa'i sgo drug dang /
NK106(me)010:2827: mig gi dbang po la sogs drug dang /
NK106(me)010:2828: mig gi rnam par shes pa la sogs drug po rnams ni chu zla dang 'dra zhes bya la /
NK106(me)010:2829: ci'i phyir chu zla dang 'dra zhe na /
NK106(me)010:2830: de dag snang ba tsam dang /
NK106(me)010:2831: ngo bo ma grub pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2833: 'khrul snang du med la snang ba'i phyir te /
NK106(me)010:2834: de'i phyir med la snang bas gsog dang /
NK106(me)010:2835: gzugs brnyan tsam gyi phyir gsob dang /
NK106(me)010:2836: mi bden la snang bas ya ma barla dang /
NK106(me)010:2837: snying po med pas chu shing lta bu ste //
NK106(me)010:2838: stong gzugs kyi snang ba rol pa tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2840: chos 'di rnams ni rang bzhin med pa ste //
NK106(me)010:2841: gsog dang gsob dang ya ma barla 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)010:2842: chu shing lta bu'i snying po gang yang med //
NK106(me)010:2844: de ltar chos thams cad chu'i zla ba lta bur ma zad /
NK106(me)010:2845: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i
NK106(me)010:2846: rig pa byang chub kyi sems kyang snang la rang
NK106(me)010:2847: bzhin med pa so so rang gi ye shes su
NK106(me)010:2848: bshad de / mtha' yis ma gos dri ma med pa'i sems //
NK106(me)010:2849: chu zla'i tshul de snang stong spros dang bral //
NK106(me)010:2850: zab zhi mi rtog ye shes brjod las 'das //
NK106(me)010:2851: rang gsal dngas la mi g.yor shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2852: de la chu'i zla ba ni dngos po dang mtshan
NK106(me)010:2853: mar rang mtshan du med pas yod med kyi mtha'
NK106(me)010:2854: las 'das la / mig lam du snang ba ma 'gags pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:2855: sems nyid dag pa 'di yang dngos po dang mtshan
NK106(me)010:2856: ma med pas yod med spros pa'i mtha' las 'das
NK106(me)010:2857: kyang / bla ma'i byin rlabs las so so rang
NK106(me)010:2858: gi rig don stong gsal 'gag med chen por snang
NK106(me)010:2859: kyang / ba yin no // de yang rgya cher rol pa las /
NK106(me)010:2860: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK106(me)010:2861: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK106(me)010:2862: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur bas //
NK106(me)010:2863: mi smra gcig pur nags su gnas par bya //
NK106(me)010:2865: mtha' bral de bzhin nyid du gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2866: chu zlar snang dus zla bar ma grub ltar //
NK106(me)010:2867: sna tshogs snang dus sna tshogs grub bsal med //
NK106(me)010:2868: dus gsum tha snyad rtogs pa'i blo dang bral //
NK106(me)010:2869: mi rtog ji bzhin nyid du gnas de zhog /
NK106(me)010:2870: chu'i nang du zla gzugs snang dus de na zla ba med pa bzhin du /
NK106(me)010:2871: ji ltar snang bzhin pa'i dus nas de ltar ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:2872: gang snang rtog dpyod dang bral ba'i ngang der bzhag ste /
NK106(me)010:2874: kye sems ni ji bzhin pa yi ngo bo ste //
NK106(me)010:2875: ji bzhin rtsol bral bde ba chen po la //
NK106(me)010:2876: rnam pa kun ldan rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK106(me)010:2877: ma bcos ji bzhin pa ru sems pa zhog /
NK106(me)010:2879: blo ma bcos rnal du gzhag pa ni //
NK106(me)010:2880: ma lus 'gro 'ong med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK106(me)010:2881: phyi dang nang med bsam 'das ris ma 'dzin //
NK106(me)010:2882: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK106(me)010:2883: yangs dog mtho dman med kyi tshol khro zhog /
NK106(me)010:2884: nang rang byung ye shes kyi ngo bo ni 'gro
NK106(me)010:2885: 'ong phyi nang med pa'i rang bzhin yin pas blo
NK106(me)010:2886: yul las 'das pa de 'adi'o zhes 'dzin par mi
NK106(me)010:2887: bya zhing / rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas yangs
NK106(me)010:2888: dog mtho dman ma grub pa'i phyir na sgom blo'i
NK106(me)010:2889: gzeb tu 'ching bar mi bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2891: don dam blo yi dpyod yul min //
NK106(me)010:2892: blo ni kun rdzob yin par brjod //
NK106(me)010:2894: snang bzhin ngo bo med pas rtog dpyod don med du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2895: mi bsam gcig tu mi gnas gdod ma'i ngang //
NK106(me)010:2896: gang yin kun yin chu zla lta bu yin //
NK106(me)010:2897: bden min rdzun min 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid //
NK106(me)010:2898: ji bzhin chos nyid ngang du sems pa zhog /
NK106(me)010:2899: ji ltar snang yang mtha' yas 'das pas 'khor 'das mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:2900: ched du blos byas kyis stong pa'ang mi sgom ste /
NK106(me)010:2901: gnas 'di ni mdo ji lta ba bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:2902: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2903: 'jam dpal chu'i zla ba ni snang la rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK106(me)010:2904: de bzhin du chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:2905: mthar 'dzin blo yi zhen pa dgag pa ni //
NK106(me)010:2906: snang srid 'khor 'das chu zla dngas pa'i gzugs //
NK106(me)010:2907: ye stong babs stong rang bzhin gdod nas stong //
NK106(me)010:2908: de la yod med blos btags 'khrul bas na //
NK106(me)010:2909: tha dad phyogs ris grub mtha' ma zhen kye //
NK106(me)010:2910: chos thams cad gzhi med pas ye nas stong pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2911: ngo bo med pas babs kyis stong pa dang /
NK106(me)010:2912: mtshan nyid med pas rang bzhin gzod ma nas stong par mnyam pa la /
NK106(me)010:2913: yin min dang che chung dang nor ma nor dang /
NK106(me)010:2914: mtho dman la sogs par 'jal ba'i grub matha'i phyogs
NK106(me)010:2915: ris kyis dgos pa med pas mtha' bral nam mkha'
NK106(me)010:2916: 'dra bar khas len par shes par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2918: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK106(me)010:2919: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK106(me)010:2920: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK106(me)010:2923: rtogs ma rtogs kyi rim pa nges pa yang //
NK106(me)010:2924: ji srid ngar 'dzin zhen pa'i blo yod pa //
NK106(me)010:2925: de srid 'khor ba nyid nas thar dus med //
NK106(me)010:2926: 'dzin med rang babs so gnyug rnal ma'i sems //
NK106(me)010:2927: zang ka ye babs rang grol phyogs yan ni //
NK106(me)010:2928: rang bzhin nyid de de la bcos ci dgos //
NK106(me)010:2929: gang 'adi'o zhes zhen 'phrin phra mor yod kyang 'khor bar 'ching ba ste /
NK106(me)010:2931: til gyi shun pa tsam gyi zug rngus kyang /
NK106(me)010:2932: nam yang sdug bsngal 'ba' zhig bskyed par zad //
NK106(me)010:2934: 'dzin med rang babs kyi rig pa rang yan yangs
NK106(me)010:2935: pa chen por 'char ba ni sems nyid rnal ma'i
NK106(me)010:2937: ma bsgoms lhug pa ye mtha' med pa'i don //
NK106(me)010:2938: sems gnyug rnal ma rang bzhin gang shar ba //
NK106(me)010:2939: gnas lugs nyid de de la bcos ci dgos //
NK106(me)010:2941: de nyid rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por thag bcad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2942: yul rnams ngos stong chu zla lta bu la //
NK106(me)010:2943: blo yang zhen stong 'dzin med shar ba na //
NK106(me)010:2944: gzung 'dzin gnyis med yul sems 'brel med pas //
NK106(me)010:2945: ci bzhin rtsol bral rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang //
NK106(me)010:2946: nang sems thams cad 'dzin med du shar ba na /
NK106(me)010:2947: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:2949: ma bcos rang dag gnyis su med pa ni //
NK106(me)010:2950: rdzogs chen nyid de de la bcos ci dgos //
NK106(me)010:2952: dag mnyam phyam gcig rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas byed
NK106(me)010:2953: spyod thams cad chos sku'i rol par sa lam bcad
NK106(me)010:2954: pa yang / gang byung grogs su 'char ba'i rang bzhin la //
NK106(me)010:2955: phyogs med bde ba chen por lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)010:2956: de ltar shes te bgrod pa'i sa med par //
NK106(me)010:2957: gdod ma'i gzhi la mngon par byang chub 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:2958: sa dang lam thams cad rig par go gcig la /
NK106(me)010:2959: rig pa rang yan phyogs bral du rtogs pa na
NK106(me)010:2960: byed spyod tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i spyod par grub pa'i
NK106(me)010:2961: phyir / snang srid kyi chos thams cad dkyil 'khor gcig gi rol par shar ba ste /
NK106(me)010:2963: sa dang lam dang sangs rgyas thams cad go gcig pa //
NK106(me)010:2964: gnyug ma'i ye shes de ni yid kyis yid la kun du dris //
NK106(me)010:2967: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK106(me)010:2971: kye dkyil ni ma nor don gyi snying po la //
NK106(me)010:2972: 'khor ni 'khor 'das bde chen rdzogs par rol //
NK106(me)010:2973: gzhi rtsa gnyis med byang chub sems kyi klong //
NK106(me)010:2974: kun byed rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:2976: lam bsgom pa'i rim pa bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:2977: de ltar rtogs nas ngang der gnas pa ni //
NK106(me)010:2978: mi g.yo chu zla lta bu'i bsgom pa ste //
NK106(me)010:2979: cir snang bden med 'al 'ol phyam phyam du //
NK106(me)010:2980: skal bzang skye bos rab tu goms par bya //
NK106(me)010:2981: 'di ltar snang rung gi yul rnams ni med bzhin snang ba chu zla'i rang bzhin du shes nas /
NK106(me)010:2982: sems ni gcig dang du ma med pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag ste /
NK106(me)010:2983: 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK106(me)010:2984: ji ltar mtshan mo chu yi zla ba dag /
NK106(me)010:2985: rang bzhin rnyog pa med pa'i mtshor snang yang //
NK106(me)010:2986: chu zla stong pa gsog ste snying po med //
NK106(me)010:2987: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:2989: ji ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK106(me)010:2990: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin chu zlar gsol btab la //
