NK106(me)010:2991: dngos gzhi gang snang dngos de chu zla dang //
NK106(me)010:2992: 'dra ba nyid du bsams la mnyam par gzhag /
NK106(me)010:2993: bla ma'i rnal 'byor sngar bzhin bsgoms pa las //
NK106(me)010:2994: chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par chu
NK106(me)010:2995: zla 'dra ba 'byongs par mdzad du gsol zhes mos
NK106(me)010:2997: snang ba thams cad chu'i zla ba lta bu yin
NK106(me)010:2998: snyam pa'i ngang la sems gzhan du mi rtog par
NK106(me)010:3000: dngos po med snang stong pa tsam las /
NK106(me)010:3001: rjes la de yang med par yid la byed pa
NK106(me)010:3002: thams cad bral ba'i nyams su myong ba 'char te
NK106(me)010:3004: dmigs pa la ni brten nas su //
NK106(me)010:3005: mi dmigs pa ni rab tu bskyed //
NK106(me)010:3006: ci yang med ces rtogs pa yis //
NK106(me)010:3007: phyis nas de yang rab tu spong //
NK106(me)010:3009: de yang dmigs rten chu zla lta bu la sems rtse gcig tu ma yengs par byed dus /
NK106(me)010:3010: rtog pa gzhan du yengs na dran pas de ma
NK106(me)010:3011: thag tu bzung la chu zla nyid du bsgom pa
NK106(me)010:3013: dmigs pa gang yang rung cig la //
NK106(me)010:3014: yid ni ting nge 'dzin la gzhag /
NK106(me)010:3015: rnam g.yeng myur du rtogs byas nas //
NK106(me)010:3016: slar yang de la blan par bya //
NK106(me)010:3018: de'i tshe sems nang du gnas pa dang /
NK106(me)010:3020: las su rung bas nyon mongs pa med pa dang /
NK106(me)010:3022: yul snang ma 'gags la don rab tu 'byed pa'i
NK106(me)010:3023: shes rab dang ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'thob ste
NK106(me)010:3025: sems ni gang du gnas pa dang //
NK106(me)010:3026: bde ba skyed par byed pa dang //
NK106(me)010:3027: der gnas las su rung ba nyid //
NK106(me)010:3031: don rab tu 'byed pa gnyis mi 'gal te /
NK106(me)010:3032: rtog pa ni yul gyi phyir sems 'phro ba yin la /
NK106(me)010:3033: mi rtog pa'i shes rab ni don skad cig la
NK106(me)010:3034: nang du rig pas rang gsal ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK106(me)010:3036: kha phyir bltas nang bltas dang /
NK106(me)010:3037: ting nge 'dzin mi rtog pas ma zin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:3038: zin pa'i khyad par yod do //
NK106(me)010:3041: mtshan dus sngar bzhin khyad par chu zla'i nyams //
NK106(me)010:3042: gang la'ang 'dzin med phyam gcig ngang du gnas //
NK106(me)010:3043: dbu ma'i nang du 'od zer lnga'i snang bas gang bar bsgoms te nyal bas /
NK106(me)010:3044: rmi lam chu zla ltar zin nas sprul bsgyur la
NK106(me)010:3045: sogs sngar bzhin nus la snang ba thams cad zang
NK106(me)010:3046: thal du mthong ba'i nyams 'char ro //
NK106(me)010:3048: myur du sems nyid rgyal po'i gtan srid zin //
NK106(me)010:3049: gang snang bltas pas der snang 'dzin pa grol //
NK106(me)010:3050: dngas gsal chu zla lta bu'i 'od gsal 'char //
NK106(me)010:3051: 'di ni skal mchog ldan pas rab sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:3052: gnas skabs su snang ba la 'dzin pa zhig pas dgag sgrub rang sar grol ba dang /
NK106(me)010:3053: yul snang chu zla ltar snang ba dang /
NK106(me)010:3054: rjes su mthun pa'i ting nge 'dzin dngas gsal spros
NK106(me)010:3055: dang bral ba spyod lam kun du 'char bas mnyam
NK106(me)010:3057: lus kyi rdul phran mthong zhing spyan dang mngos shes 'grub pa dang /
NK106(me)010:3060: rang bzhin med la gang goms pa //
NK106(me)010:3061: myur du bla med byang chub thob //
NK106(me)010:3063: rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:3064: med snang chu zla 'dra bar rtogs pa dang //
NK106(me)010:3065: mnyam du gzung 'dzin zhen pa'i mtsho brgal bas //
NK106(me)010:3066: rnam grol rin chen gling du phyin par shog /
NK106(me)010:3067: rnam kun mchog ldan rtogs pa'i dpung bskyed de //
NK106(me)010:3068: ting 'dzin gzhu drag shes rab mda' 'phangs pas //
NK106(me)010:3069: ma rig nyon mongs rtsad nas bton pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3070: 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo ma lus 'pham byed shog /
NK106(me)010:3071: chos dkar yon tan ri bong 'dzin gzugs can //
NK106(me)010:3072: ma lus 'gro rgyud skye bo'i mthar khyab pas //
NK106(me)010:3073: srid pa'i mtshan mo gti mug mun brel te //
NK106(me)010:3074: chos nyid me tog kun+da rgyas par shog /
NK106(me)010:3075: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:3076: chu zla lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas lnga pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:3077: de ltar chad pa med pa'i ngo bo nyid du chos thams cad gtan la phab nas /
NK106(me)010:3078: da ni rtag pa med pa'i rang bzhin du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3079: yang 'dir rgyal bas brag ca lta bu zhes //
NK106(me)010:3080: gsungs pa de yang gsal bar bshad kyis nyon //
NK106(me)010:3081: chos thams cad ni brag ca ltar snang bzhin pa'i dus nas ngo bo med la /
NK106(me)010:3082: rtag pa ther zug pa'i cha las grol te brjod
NK106(me)010:3083: du med pas dngos po med pa'i phyir brag ca'i
NK106(me)010:3086: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis rtag
NK106(me)010:3087: pa med pa'i phyir brag ca lta bu'o zhes pa'i
NK106(me)010:3088: don yang gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i dbye ba
NK106(me)010:3089: gsum las / dang po gzhi gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3090: ji ltar brag ri'i drung 'dug mi dag gis //
NK106(me)010:3091: ji skad brjod bzhin brag ca'i dbyangs 'byung ba //
NK106(me)010:3092: de bzhin chos kun rkyen 'byung ngo bo med //
NK106(me)010:3093: bden pas stong zhes nges par rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:3094: brag ri'i drung du skyes bu'i sgra skad brjod pa na /
NK106(me)010:3095: sgra de ji lta bu'i dbyangs grags kyang /
NK106(me)010:3096: dbyangs de phyi nang gang na'ang med bzhin grags pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:3097: gdod ma'i gzhi stong gsal ngo bo med pa'i rang bzhin las /
NK106(me)010:3098: lhan cig skyes pa dang mtshungs ldan gyi ma rig pas rkyen byas te /
NK106(me)010:3099: gzhi snang gi rang gdangs las sna tshogs kyi 'khrul
NK106(me)010:3100: pa shar ba ni rig pa dang de las gzhan
NK106(me)010:3101: gang na'ang med bzhin du snang bas 'khor ba brag
NK106(me)010:3103: don la med pa gsal bar snang ba las gzhan ma yin te /
NK106(me)010:3105: ji ltar mi dag brag ri'i drung 'dug ste //
NK106(me)010:3106: glu len smra dang dgod dang ngu ba las //
NK106(me)010:3107: rkyen la brten te brag ca 'byung mod kyang /
NK106(me)010:3108: sgra las dbyangs de nam yang 'phos pa med //
NK106(me)010:3109: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:3111: de phyir snang la ngo bo med pas mtha' las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3112: brag ca grags dus phyi nang bar gsum du //
NK106(me)010:3113: brag ca'i dbyangs de btsal yang mi rnyed ltar //
NK106(me)010:3114: phyi nang chos kun blo yis dpyad byas na //
NK106(me)010:3115: sems dang sems las snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:3116: brag ca'i rnam tsam yang mi rnyed de //
NK106(me)010:3117: mkha' bzhin stong la dngos med rnam par dag /
NK106(me)010:3118: de ltar rtogs na gang la'ang zhen 'dzin med //
NK106(me)010:3119: brag ca'i dbyangs de brag dang mi dang de dag gi bar gang na'ang med la /
NK106(me)010:3120: rkyen gyis yod pa ltar snang ba bzhin /
NK106(me)010:3121: phyi yul gyi chos dang nang sems kyi dran rtog
NK106(me)010:3122: thams cad la rags pa rnams ni cha shas kyis
NK106(me)010:3123: dbye ba dang / phra ba rnams ni ngo bo
NK106(me)010:3124: ngos gzung dbyibs dang kha dog la sogs par dpyad
NK106(me)010:3125: na cung zad kyang mi rnyed pas /
NK106(me)010:3126: nam mkha' dang 'dra bar bsam brjod las 'das te /
NK106(me)010:3128: ji ltar snang ba'i dngos po 'di //
NK106(me)010:3129: rig pas brtags na 'ga' mi rnyed //
NK106(me)010:3130: ma rnyed pa nyid don dam ste //
NK106(me)010:3131: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK106(me)010:3133: gshis kyi stong pa blo las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3134: kun rdzob snang la don dam mi dmigs zhes //
NK106(me)010:3135: cha gnyis 'dzin pa'ang blo yi rnam dbye zhes //
NK106(me)010:3136: ji ltar snang dus nyid nas blo las 'das //
NK106(me)010:3137: blos bkod spros pa'i rtsa ba rang sems te //
NK106(me)010:3138: yul der 'phel 'grib gang du'ang mi byed pas //
NK106(me)010:3139: rtog pa'i d+r+wa bas ma 'dzin ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)010:3140: de ltar shes te spros pa'i pha rol 'gro //
NK106(me)010:3141: de la dngos po smra bas kun rdzob tu grub la /
NK106(me)010:3142: don dam dus grub ces cha 'dzin pa de yang
NK106(me)010:3143: chos rnams kyi rang dus na ma grub pas 'thad
NK106(me)010:3145: cha gnyis su blos rtog pa tsam las snang ba'i
NK106(me)010:3146: steng na med par mngon sum du gsal ba'i phyir
NK106(me)010:3147: dang / gang yang ma grub par rtogs pa'i dus
NK106(me)010:3148: nas dngos po chung ngu ma song ba'i phyir na
NK106(me)010:3149: dang / / sems kyis de ltar dpyad pa yin la /
NK106(me)010:3150: sems kyis stong par dpyad kyang rang gi kun rtog pa'i cha las /
NK106(me)010:3151: stong pa rnal mar med pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3152: dbu ma thal 'gyur ba'i lung 'di yin te /
NK106(me)010:3153: snang ba'i dus na khas len thams cad bral ba
NK106(me)010:3154: dbu ma de kho na nyid du shes par bya'o
NK106(me)010:3156: ji ltar snang bzhin ngo bo'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:3159: brag ca dang 'dra ba'i 'khor ba rkyen rten cing
NK106(me)010:3160: 'brel bar 'byung ba las snang brnyan tsam du grub
NK106(me)010:3161: pa'i tshul ni / gdod ma'i sems nyid nam mkha' yid bzhin dang //
NK106(me)010:3162: yon tan lhun grub rgyal chos dri med las //
NK106(me)010:3163: kun rtog ma rig skyes bu srid pa'i chos //
NK106(me)010:3164: med snang brag ca lta bu 'dir 'khyams te //
NK106(me)010:3165: 'gro drug rang snang bag chags dbang gis snang //
NK106(me)010:3166: rnyog pa'i rang sems rab 'jug dbang gis 'jug /
NK106(me)010:3167: sems nyid gdod ma'i ngo bo nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK106(me)010:3168: dbyings na yon tan nor bu ltar lhun gyis grub
NK106(me)010:3171: kun rtog pa'i ma rig pa rkyen tsam du shar bas gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i bag chags bsags nas /
NK106(me)010:3172: 'khor ba brag ca dang 'dra ba 'dir 'khyams te
NK106(me)010:3173: 'gro drug so so'i snang ba bag chags tha dad
NK106(me)010:3175: srid pa gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa ni sems
NK106(me)010:3176: kyi rnyog pa bsod nams cha mthun gyis mtho ris
NK106(me)010:3177: dang / mi dge ba so sos ngan song du 'jug ste /
NK106(me)010:3179: gang bsod nams dang bsod nams ma yin pa'i las
NK106(me)010:3180: kyis gcig nas gcig tu 'khor te nyon mongs par
NK106(me)010:3182: 'phags pa gnas brtan pa'i gzhung las kyang /
NK106(me)010:3183: 'jig rten sna tshogs las las skyes //
NK106(me)010:3184: las ni sems dpa' dag las skyes //
NK106(me)010:3186: 'khrul par snang dus nyid nas stong par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3188: gzhi med rtsa ba bral ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:3189: e ma med bzhin snang 'di dgod re bro //
NK106(me)010:3190: don med ngang la don du bzung ba yis //
NK106(me)010:3191: don du snang ba brag ca'i dbyangs 'dra ba //
NK106(me)010:3192: 'di la bden zhen 'dzin pa ci zhig bya //
NK106(me)010:3193: gang yin gtad med phyam gcig ngang der zhog /'phral byung snang ba bden med chen por grol //
NK106(me)010:3194: yangs dog mtho dman med pas nyams re dga' //
NK106(me)010:3195: ji ltar snang ba nyid nas gzhi dang rtsa ba
NK106(me)010:3196: med pa'i rang bzhin du rtogs pas gtad med yangs
NK106(me)010:3197: pa chen po'i rol par shar te /
NK106(me)010:3198: yangs dog mtho dman med pa chos nyid kyi ra
NK106(me)010:3199: bar dal khod snyoms pa'i phyir blo bde ba yin
NK106(me)010:3200: no // ji ltar snyoms she na /
NK106(me)010:3201: gang byung ched 'dzin zhig pa'i snang ba la //
NK106(me)010:3202: dgag sgrub brag ca 'dra ba'i snang ba shar //
NK106(me)010:3203: ci yin gzab gtad med par grol bas na //
NK106(me)010:3204: de yin phyogs cha bral bar phyam gcig go //
NK106(me)010:3205: blo re dogs zad pa'i snang ba yul snang brag ca 'dra ba'i snang ba shar te /
NK106(me)010:3206: ci yin ngos gzung med par grol ba'i phyir bden
NK106(me)010:3207: med phyal ba ye dag tu dal khod snyoms pa'o
NK106(me)010:3208: // de'i tshe nyams snang gzigs mor che ba 'di ltar shar ba /
NK106(me)010:3209: ha ha ltos dang 'khrul snang dgod re bro //
NK106(me)010:3210: ngo bo ngos gzung med la khral ma khrol //
NK106(me)010:3211: zab zob 'al 'ol yal yol ban ma bun //
NK106(me)010:3212: phyad phyod bden zhen med la sna tshogs snang //
NK106(me)010:3213: nang sems kyi rtsa ba chod pa na /
NK106(me)010:3214: phyi yul gyi 'dzin pa rang bzhin gyis grol te /
NK106(me)010:3215: dus ma 'gyur bar snang ba ni rnal 'byor pa'i gzigs mo ste /
NK106(me)010:3216: yul snang thams cad ngos gzung med pas khral ma khrol /
NK106(me)010:3217: snying po med pas zab ma zob /
NK106(me)010:3219: gtad 'dzin yal bas ban ma bun /
NK106(me)010:3220: gza' gtad med pas phyad ma phyod mar snang ste /
NK106(me)010:3222: chos nyid bden pa mthong bas rgyal ba'i sras //
NK106(me)010:3223: rtogs pa khong du chud pas nam yang bde //
NK106(me)010:3225: de'i tshe sna tshogs kyi chos la snang zhen gyi rim pa tha dad pa la yang 'di ltar /
NK106(me)010:3226: mi mkhas bden par zhen pas bden bden 'dra //
NK106(me)010:3227: bden med rnal 'byor pa la phyam phyam gcig /
NK106(me)010:3228: mi rtag rtag par 'dzin la rtag rtag 'dra //
NK106(me)010:3229: rtag 'dzin ngang gis grol la stong gzugs gcig /
NK106(me)010:3230: yangs dog rgya chad med pas nyams daga'o //
NK106(me)010:3231: 'khor ba la bden bden ltar snang ba'i yul rnams /
NK106(me)010:3232: rnal 'byor pa la bden med phyam phyam zhig shar la /
NK106(me)010:3233: rtag par zhen pa rnams la dus rtag tu yod yod rtag rtag ltar snang ba rnams /
NK106(me)010:3234: rnal 'byor pa la med snang stong pa'i rang gdangs shig shar te /
NK106(me)010:3235: rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med par chos nyid phyal ba bar med blo bde ba yin te /
NK106(me)010:3237: rang bzhin snang ba'i chos rnams la //
NK106(me)010:3238: sgra tshig dngos po rang dag pas //
NK106(me)010:3239: yul med rten bral dgongs pa zhes //
NK106(me)010:3240: kun du bzang po nga yis bstan //
NK106(me)010:3242: lam nyams su blang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3243: rtogs pa'i don la goms 'dris bya ba ni //
NK106(me)010:3244: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin sgra brnyan gsol ba gdab //
NK106(me)010:3245: dngos gzhi chos kun sgra brnyan brag ca 'dra //
NK106(me)010:3246: grags dus nyid nas ngos gzung med pa dang //
NK106(me)010:3247: cir snang thams cad de bzhin bsgom par bya //
NK106(me)010:3248: bla ma'i rnal 'byo sngar bzhin bsgoms nas /
NK106(me)010:3249: chos thams cad brag ca ltar bden med 'byongs par mdzad du gsol ces snying nas byas la /
NK106(me)010:3250: dngos gzhi ni snang grags kyi chos thams cad brag
NK106(me)010:3251: ca ltar snang la ngo bo med par bsgom zhing
NK106(me)010:3252: / khyad par bstod smad snyan dang mi snyan kun //
NK106(me)010:3253: grags pas stong la ngo bo ngos gzung med //
NK106(me)010:3254: de la sems kyi dgag sgrub don med kyi //
NK106(me)010:3255: sgra rnams brag ca 'dra bar rtogs par gyis //
NK106(me)010:3256: brag ca ltar gzhan gyis bdag la bstod pa dang
NK106(me)010:3257: smad pa kun mnyam par shes pa la slob par
NK106(me)010:3260: rab 'byor 'di la byang chub sems dpa' gang 'di
NK106(me)010:3261: ltar shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la
NK106(me)010:3262: spyod pa'i tshe / gzhan dag kha zer ram skur pa 'debs sam /
NK106(me)010:3263: smra'am 'thing glod par byed pas kyang rung ste /
NK106(me)010:3264: gang ci yang rung ba'i sgra de dag thams cad
NK106(me)010:3265: brag ca ltar ngo bo nyid med par bsgom par
NK106(me)010:3266: bya'o zhes so // de la khro ba'i sgo ni
NK106(me)010:3267: ngag gi brjod pa mi snyan pa las 'byung bas
NK106(me)010:3268: de ngo bo med par rig pas kyang rtogs par
NK106(me)010:3269: bya'o zhes so // bya ste / khro sogs sems de yul dang phyogs na med //
NK106(me)010:3270: med la snang dus btsal yang rnyed pa med //
NK106(me)010:3271: rkyen byung stong pa brag ca'i dbyangs 'dra zhing //
NK106(me)010:3272: pha rol tshig kyang rkyen byung brag ca 'dra //
NK106(me)010:3273: dpyad na med la snang ba'i gzugs brnyan tsam //
NK106(me)010:3274: shin tu dpyad na mkha' bzhin dngos med cing //
NK106(me)010:3275: legs nyen shor god ci yang mi dmigs pas //
NK106(me)010:3276: sgra la don du ma 'dzin bden pas stong //
NK106(me)010:3277: rnam kun brag ca 'dra bar rtogs par gyis //
NK106(me)010:3278: de yang pha rol pos ngan du smra ba'i tshe /
NK106(me)010:3279: tshig 'bru de ni phyi nang gang na'ang med pas mi dga' ba bya mi dgos la /
NK106(me)010:3280: ngan sems de ni kha dog dang dngos po med
NK106(me)010:3281: pas gnod byed du ma grub pa'i phyir mi dga'
NK106(me)010:3283: rang gis nga la de skad zer ba snyam du bzung bas lan pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3284: rang la rang gi gnod pa byas pa da gdod shes te /
NK106(me)010:3285: ngos gzung med pa stong pa'i rang sgra la shor
NK106(me)010:3286: god rdul tsam yang mi 'dug pas grag stong rang
NK106(me)010:3287: yal rjes med du lam du khyer bar bya ste
NK106(me)010:3289: ye nas stong pa'i dngos 'di la //
NK106(me)010:3290: thob pa ci yod shor ci yod //
NK106(me)010:3291: mi dgar ci yod dgar ci yod //
NK106(me)010:3292: thams cad nam mkhar 'dra ba ni //
NK106(me)010:3293: bdag 'dras yongs su gzung bar bgyi //
NK106(me)010:3294: zhes gsungs pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:3296: de yis thog ma'i 'khor ba'i bag chags dang //
NK106(me)010:3297: khyad par khong khro zhe sdang me 'jil zhing //
NK106(me)010:3298: 'phags pa'i bzod thob ngan song yang mi ltung //
NK106(me)010:3299: rim gyis rgyal ba'i 'byor pa nye bar skye //
NK106(me)010:3300: mtshan mo sngar bzhin khyad par brag ca'i nyams //
NK106(me)010:3301: grags pa sgras stong chos la bzod pa thob //
NK106(me)010:3302: de phyir brag ca lta bu'i don sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:3303: nyin par shin tu goms pa nyid kyis rmi lam du'ang brag ca ltar rtogs te /
NK106(me)010:3304: sprul pa dang bsgyur ba la sogs sngar bzhin thob pa'i tshe /
NK106(me)010:3305: gnas skabs su sgra'i rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pas khong khro thams cad zhi ste /
NK106(me)010:3307: 'od srungs de la byang chub sems dpa' gang gis
NK106(me)010:3308: chos thams cad brag ca dang 'dra bar rtogs pa
NK106(me)010:3309: des ni sgra'i rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pa thob
NK106(me)010:3310: ste / gang bdag gis dgra la dga' bar mi byed /
NK106(me)010:3311: gzhan gyi sgra la khro bar mi byed /
NK106(me)010:3312: stong pa nyid sgra'i chos thos kyang skrag par mi byed de /
NK106(me)010:3313: 'di ni sgra'i rjes su mthun pa'i bzod pa dang po'o zhes gsungs so //
NK106(me)010:3314: zhi ba rdul phran mi 'khrugs 'dus ma byas //
NK106(me)010:3315: yon tan mtsho chen bzod pa dam pa'i mtshor //
NK106(me)010:3316: ting 'dzin gru chen dam pa legs sbyar te //
NK106(me)010:3317: ma lus 'gro kun thar lam bgrod par shog /
NK106(me)010:3318: rnam dag mos pa yangs pa'i nam mkha' la //
NK106(me)010:3319: blo gros sprin chen 'dus pa'i glog 'gyu zhing //
NK106(me)010:3320: chos char zhi ba rgyun gyi tshogs bsil bas //
NK106(me)010:3321: skal ldan gdul bya'i lo thog rgyas par shog /
NK106(me)010:3322: snying rje'i sdong po phan bde'i yal 'dab can //
NK106(me)010:3323: ting 'dzin me tog shes rab 'bras bzang ba //
NK106(me)010:3324: bsdu bzhi'i grib bsil snyan pa'i dri bsung gis //
NK106(me)010:3325: 'gro blo'i bya tshogs rab tu dga' bar shog /
NK106(me)010:3326: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:3327: sgra brnyan lta bu'i le'u rdo rje'i gnas drug pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:3328: de ltar chos thams cad rtag pa med par bstan pa'i rjes la /
NK106(me)010:3329: snang la rang bzhin med pa nyid don tha dad pa'i ngo bo ma grub par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3330: yang 'dir rgyal bas dri za'i grong khyer zhes //
NK106(me)010:3331: gsungs pa de yang bsgom phyir bshad kyis nyon //
NK106(me)010:3332: chos thams cad ji ltar snang bzhin pa'i dus nas
NK106(me)010:3333: rten med pa dri za'i grong khyer lta bu ste
NK106(me)010:3335: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni gnas med pa rten
NK106(me)010:3336: med pa rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa'i phyir dri
NK106(me)010:3337: za'i grong khyer lta bu'o zhes gsungs pa dag gi
NK106(me)010:3338: don ni / gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu'i rang bzhin gsum du nges pa las /
NK106(me)010:3340: gdod ma'i 'od gsal mkha' la snang ba'i chos //
NK106(me)010:3341: lhun grub yon tan grong khyer brgyan pa zhig /
NK106(me)010:3342: thog ma tha ma dbus mtha' med 'dir gnas //
NK106(me)010:3343: gzhi gdod ma'i rig pa stong pa nam mkha' 'dra ba'i dbyings na /
NK106(me)010:3344: lhun grub yon tan gyi grong khyer rang chas su bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3345: dbyings la ye ldan gyi sku dang ye shes te /
NK106(me)010:3346: thog ma med pa nas tha ma med pa'i bar du gnas pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3347: ji ltar sngon bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3348: 'gyur ba med pa'i de bzhin nyid //
NK106(me)010:3351: rnam dbyer bcas pa'i mtshan nyid can //
NK106(me)010:3352: glo bur dag gis khams stong gis //
NK106(me)010:3353: rnam dbyer med pa'i mtshan nyid can //
NK106(me)010:3354: bla med chos kyis stong pa min //
NK106(me)010:3356: gzhi stong gsal lhun grub chen po /
NK106(me)010:3357: de nyid ngang las ma rig sems kyi mkhar //
NK106(me)010:3358: gzung 'dzin las byung 'gro drug dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3359: rten gzhi med la snang ste sna tshogs gzugs //
NK106(me)010:3360: bag chags 'khrul pa'i yid las skyes pa can //
NK106(me)010:3361: dbyings kyi rig pa nam mkha' 'dra ba la //
NK106(me)010:3362: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa mtshungs par ldan pas /
NK106(me)010:3364: gzhi snang las 'gro drug gi snang ba so sor
NK106(me)010:3365: 'khrul pa ni thog ma med pa'i bag chags kyi
NK106(me)010:3366: snang ba med bzhin snang ba dri za'i grong khyer
NK106(me)010:3367: lta bu ste / gsang snying las /
NK106(me)010:3368: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las //
NK106(me)010:3369: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK106(me)010:3371: ji ltar snang ba nyid ngo bo med par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3372: gang 'di rtogs na sems nyid gdong ma'i ngang //
NK106(me)010:3373: ma rtogs dus na da ltar 'khrul pa'i sems //
NK106(me)010:3374: ci 'dra ngos gzung med pas dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3375: nyid las gzhan pa'i dpe zhig gang yin kye //
NK106(me)010:3376: rig pa'i ngo na snang bdo ba'i dus nyid /
NK106(me)010:3377: ma rtogs na 'khrul snang bden pa 'dra yang /
NK106(me)010:3378: nam mkha'i ngang na dri za'i grong khyer snang ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:3379: rig pa'i ngang na med pa gsal snang tsam du
NK106(me)010:3380: rten dang ngo bo dang gzhi rtsa med par gnas
NK106(me)010:3381: pas / rtogs na ngo bo nyid med pa'i phyir stong gzugs snang ba tsam ste /
NK106(me)010:3383: 'du byed rnams ni dri za'i grong khyer lta bu'o zhes gsungs pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:3384: 'khor ba ye nas stong pas spong du med par la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3385: 'on kyang 'di kun rang bzhin med pa ste //
NK106(me)010:3386: nub kha'i thang la dri za'i grong khyer bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3387: rten dang brten pa gnyis ka 'khrul pa'i sems //
NK106(me)010:3388: bag chags nyid de rtogs na ngo bo med //
NK106(me)010:3389: rang bzhin bzhag na ji bzhin ngang gis grol //
NK106(me)010:3390: de bas snang yang 'jigs spong dka' ba med //
NK106(me)010:3391: srid 'gro ye stong dag pa'i tshul shes bya //
NK106(me)010:3392: nub kha'i thang la dri za'i grong khyer skye bos
NK106(me)010:3393: gang ba zhig mthong dus nas grong dang skye bo
NK106(me)010:3394: gnyis ka ma grub pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:3395: snod de la brten pa'i 'gro bar snang ba yang snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin med pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3396: sems kyi 'khrul snang las don du ma grub pas sems rang bzhin med pas grol ba na /
NK106(me)010:3397: 'khrul snang rang bzhin stong pa'i phyir ched du spong
NK106(me)010:3398: mi dgos pas ji bzhin rtsol bral mnyam pa chen
NK106(me)010:3399: por bzhag ste / ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:3400: 'jam dpal dri za'i grong khyer ni snang la yod pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:3401: de bzhin du chos thams cad ni snang la yod pa ma yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)010:3402: gzung 'dzin yul med chen por bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3403: yul snang thams cad bden stong dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3404: blo rnams thams cad babs stong dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3405: yul sems gnyis snang dri za'i grong 'dra bas //
NK106(me)010:3406: cung zad tsam du'ang zhen 'dzin rang sar zhog /
NK106(me)010:3407: phyi rol gyi yul snang thams cad gzhi med stong pa /
NK106(me)010:3408: nang gi 'dzin rtog thams cad rang sangs stong pa ste /
NK106(me)010:3409: yul sems thams cad stong pa'i rang 'gros la dgag
NK106(me)010:3410: sgrub dang 'dzin zhen byed pa 'khrul pa'i phyir te
NK106(me)010:3411: / rang bab rang 'gros phyal bar zang thal gyis bskyangs te /
NK106(me)010:3413: gang la zhen pa yod na de yang thong //
NK106(me)010:3414: rtogs par gyur na thams cad de yin te //
NK106(me)010:3416: 'dzin zhen 'khor ba'i gzeb tu bstan nas rang grol zang kas shes par bya ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3417: de ci med la snang ba'i chos rnams la //
NK106(me)010:3418: blo yis ma bzo ched kar gzung ba shol //
NK106(me)010:3419: thog med 'khrul pa'ang 'dzin zhen las byung bas //
NK106(me)010:3420: da ni 'dzin med rang bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:3421: snang la ngo bo med pas ched du yod par bzung bas 'khrul te /
NK106(me)010:3422: thog ma'i 'khrul pa'ang 'dzin zhen phyir mched pa las byung ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3423: da lta'ang 'dzin zhen ngang gis grol bar bya ba la bslab pa ni gnad gal po che'o //
NK106(me)010:3424: 'di ltar mi 'thad pa byung yang 'dzin zhen ma
NK106(me)010:3425: byas na de la brten pa'i rtsod pa dang sdug
NK106(me)010:3427: thams cad mdo mthun pas 'dzin med nam mkha' ltar gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3428: 'phags pa zag pa med dang chos rnams la /
NK106(me)010:3429: mya ngan 'das pa rab zhi dngos med pas //
NK106(me)010:3430: khyed kyis dngos dang dngos med chos rnams la //
NK106(me)010:3431: bden stong dri za'i grong dang mkha' dbyings bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3432: gdod nas rab zhi skye med mkhyen par mdzod //
NK106(me)010:3433: chos rnams kyi chos nyid zag pa med pa ste /
NK106(me)010:3434: mya ngan las 'das pa dang mtshungs pas dngos po
NK106(me)010:3435: sna tshogs yul snang gi chos rnams snang nas stong
NK106(me)010:3436: pa dri za'i grong khyer dang 'dra la /
NK106(me)010:3437: dngos med sems kyi rang bzhin nam mkha' ltar dag pa'i ngang la bzhag ste /
NK106(me)010:3438: chos rnams thams cad bde bar gshegs dang 'dra //
NK106(me)010:3441: gang tshe dngos dang dngos med dag /
NK106(me)010:3442: blo yi mdun na mi gnas pa //
NK106(me)010:3443: de tshe rnam pa gzhan med pas //
NK106(me)010:3444: dmigs pa med pa rab tu zhi //
NK106(me)010:3446: bzang ngan blang dor las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3447: 'dod chags mi dmigs de bzhin zhe sdang ste //
NK106(me)010:3448: gti mug nga rgyal phrag dog mi dmigs te //
NK106(me)010:3449: kun du rtog can dri za'i grong 'dra bar //
NK106(me)010:3450: mkhyen nas nyon mongs ngo bo med can dang //
NK106(me)010:3451: sems nyid byang chub gnyis su med pa'i chos //
NK106(me)010:3452: mkha' mnyam dri ma med par rtogs 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)010:3453: 'khor ba'i rgyu nyon mongs pa lnga kun rtog pa
NK106(me)010:3454: dang bcas pa med la snang bzhin dpyad na ngo
NK106(me)010:3456: sems nyid ngo bo nyid med de med pa dag
NK106(me)010:3457: rang bzhin med pa'i stong par gnyis su med pas
NK106(me)010:3458: / 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis su med pa zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3459: ma rig nam mkha' ji bzhin du //
NK106(me)010:3460: chos rnams thams cad mtshan nyid med //
NK106(me)010:3464: 'di gnyis kyis ni khyad par gang //
NK106(me)010:3465: shin tu phra ba'ang yod ma yin //
NK106(me)010:3468: srid dang zhi ba mnyam nyid dang //
NK106(me)010:3471: 'khor ba gang yin mya ngan 'das par nges //
NK106(me)010:3473: mnyam pa nyid du la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3474: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin gzod nas mya ngan 'das //
NK106(me)010:3475: 'khrul rtog rab zhi mkha' la sprin dengs bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3476: dang po'i 'byung sar zhi ba'i tshul mkhyen nas //
NK106(me)010:3477: ye shes rab zhi stong gsal ngang der skyongs //
NK106(me)010:3478: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di dang po nam mkha'i ngang las chags /
NK106(me)010:3479: da ltar der gnas tha ma'ang zhig dus dang po'i chags sa nam mkha' nyid du thim pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:3480: 'khor ba'ang dang po dbyings las shar /
NK106(me)010:3482: mthar yang dbyings su grol ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3483: gang blo'i spros pa thams cad nam mkha' la sprin
NK106(me)010:3484: dengs pa ltar rang yal stong gsal gyi ngang la
NK106(me)010:3486: gdod ma'i dbyings la phyin pa zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3488: nam zhig 'jig rten khams 'di byung ba dang //
NK106(me)010:3489: byung nas zhig ste nam mkhar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK106(me)010:3490: ji ltar sngon bzhin phyis kyang de bzhin te //
NK106(me)010:3491: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:3492: ji ltar bar snang cung zad sprin med la //
NK106(me)010:3493: skad cig tu ni sprin gyi dkyil 'khor snang //
NK106(me)010:3494: byung nas zhig ste sprin gyi dkyil 'khor med //
NK106(me)010:3495: thog ma gang las byung ba brtag par byos //
NK106(me)010:3496: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK106(me)010:3498: gnad 'gag dril bas 'gag bsdam pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3499: skye med ngang las bsam yul mi dmigs kyang //
NK106(me)010:3500: skye ba'i cho 'phrul dbyings su ma zhi bar //
NK106(me)010:3501: kun rtog 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba bcad par mdzod //
NK106(me)010:3502: bya dang mi bya blang dor gnyis med kyang //
NK106(me)010:3503: dngos po bdag tu 'dzin pa'i sems yod par //
NK106(me)010:3504: nyon mongs gnyen por zab mo'i chos bsten 'tshal //
NK106(me)010:3505: phyi nang gnyis med sems nyid ngang du grol //
NK106(me)010:3506: de ltar rtogs na mkhas pa'i skye bo yin //
NK106(me)010:3507: chos thams cad skye ba med kyang rang gi rnam
NK106(me)010:3508: rtog rang dngas ting nge 'dzin dang mi 'bral bar
NK106(me)010:3509: rgyud la med kyi bar du sems kyi 'khrul rtog
NK106(me)010:3510: la rtsa ba bcad cing rang kar ma shor ba
NK106(me)010:3511: gces te de la sogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:3513: gang kun du rtog pa las 'byung gi rnam par mi rtog pa las ma yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)010:3514: gshis la blang dor med kyang sems bdag tu 'dzin
NK106(me)010:3515: ring la dge sdig blang dor gyis las 'bras mi
NK106(me)010:3516: bslu bas / bsags sbyong chos la 'bad pa gces te /
NK106(me)010:3518: gang chos thams cad kyang nam mkha' lta bur rtogs la /
NK106(me)010:3519: las dang las kyi rnam par smin pa la 'jigs
NK106(me)010:3520: par lta ba ni yang dag pa'i chos so zhes
NK106(me)010:3521: pa dang / ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK106(me)010:3522: mi dag 'jig rten 'di yang shi nas ni //
NK106(me)010:3523: srid pa gzhan du 'jug pa de med na //
NK106(me)010:3524: las byas pa sogs pa rnams kyang med mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:3527: chos kun nam mkha' ltar mthong la //
NK106(me)010:3528: rnam par smin la yid ches pa //
NK106(me)010:3529: ngo mtshar las kyang 'di ngo mtshar //
NK106(me)010:3530: rmad byung las kyang 'di rmad byung //
NK106(me)010:3532: lam nyams su blang ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3533: da ni de nyid don la bsgom pa yang //
NK106(me)010:3534: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin dngos gzhi chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:3535: dri za'i grong du nges par 'tshal bar bya //
NK106(me)010:3536: bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK106(me)010:3537: khyad par du chos thams cad dri za'i grong khyer
NK106(me)010:3538: ltar 'byang bar mdzad du gsol zhes gsol ba btab
NK106(me)010:3539: nas sna tshogs su snang ba thams cad dri za'i
NK106(me)010:3542: gzugs ni snang bas stong ste dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3543: sgra dri ro reg chos drug dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3544: sems dang dgag sgrub kun rtog shar ro cog /
NK106(me)010:3545: dri za'i grong yin ngang der gsal bar bsgom //
NK106(me)010:3546: cir snang thams cad dri za'i grong khyer du //
NK106(me)010:3547: nyin mtshan dus kun sngar bzhin goms par bya //
NK106(me)010:3548: gzugs la sogs pa yul dang rang gi sems dang dran rtog thams cad /
NK106(me)010:3549: snang la stong pa dri za'i grong du nyin par gyi cha la goms shing /
NK106(me)010:3550: mtshan mo seng ge'i nyal lugs kyis dbu ma dkar
NK106(me)010:3551: po'i nang na sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams 'ja' tshon
NK106(me)010:3553: rmi lam du dri za'i grong dang 'dra bar zin pa dang /
NK106(me)010:3554: sngon med pa'i yul dang snang ba ya mtshan can mthong zhing /
NK106(me)010:3555: sprul bsgyur nus pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:3557: dri za'i grong dang 'dus byas 'drar mthong nas //
NK106(me)010:3558: bden med ngang der bzhag pas spros kun zhi //
NK106(me)010:3559: stong gsal rang byung 'od gsal khong nas 'char //
NK106(me)010:3560: rmi lam na yang dri za'i grong du mthong //
NK106(me)010:3561: sprul bsgyur la sogs sngar bzhin bsgoms pa ste //
NK106(me)010:3562: bden zhen grol bas gzung 'dzin 'ching ba chad //
NK106(me)010:3563: kun sbyor bag chags rab zhi grol ba thob //
NK106(me)010:3564: de phyir dri za'i grong khyer nyid sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:3565: nyin dang mtshan du goms pa las gnas skabs su
NK106(me)010:3566: bdag 'dzin grol zhing ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i
NK106(me)010:3568: mthar thug sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur te /
NK106(me)010:3570: srid gsum 'di dag dri za'i grong //
NK106(me)010:3571: smig rgyu chu yi phung po bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3572: nor bar shes phyir mi rtog go //
NK106(me)010:3574: gang gi rang bzhin chos dkar dbang po'i gzhu //
NK106(me)010:3575: sna tshogs rang bzhin mi gnyis spros dang bral //
NK106(me)010:3576: dag gsal dri med dngas pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK106(me)010:3577: ma lus 'gro kun lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK106(me)010:3578: pad spungs me tog 'dab bskyed ge sar gyi //
NK106(me)010:3579: rdul la reg pas bdud rtsi 'byung gnas gang //
NK106(me)010:3580: lha yi mtsho chu dal bzhin babs bsil bas //
NK106(me)010:3581: ches lhag mngon par dga' ba'i gnas mthong shog /
NK106(me)010:3582: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:3583: dri za'i grong khyer lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas bdun pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:3584: de ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin nam mkha'
NK106(me)010:3585: dang 'dra bas tha dad pa ma yin par bstan
NK106(me)010:3586: nas / da ni gcig tu'ang bsgrub par bshad de /
NK106(me)010:3587: rang bzhin med pa gang la gcig pa'ang mi 'thad pa'i phyir te /
NK106(me)010:3588: gcig tu ma grub pa nyid do zhes bshad pa /
NK106(me)010:3589: yang 'dir rgyal bas chos kun sprul pa zhes //
NK106(me)010:3590: gsungs pa de yang ji bzhin bshad kyi nyon //
NK106(me)010:3591: chos rnams thams cad snang la ma grub pa sprul pa'i skye bo ltar /
NK106(me)010:3592: ngo bo gcig pa med de tha snyad so sor snang la /
NK106(me)010:3593: dpyad na gcig pa ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3594: snang brnyan gyi rang bzhin can ni /
NK106(me)010:3596: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni gnyis su med de /
NK106(me)010:3597: gcig tu ma yin pa'i phyir sprul pa lta bu'o zhes gsungs pa'i don yang /
NK106(me)010:3600: 'bras bu'i dbye ba gsum du nges pa las /
NK106(me)010:3601: dang po gzhi bshad pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3602: rang bzhin gdod nas 'od gsal ngang nyid las //
NK106(me)010:3603: ma rig bdag tu 'dzin pa las sprul pa'i //
NK106(me)010:3604: 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang sna tshogs sprul pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3605: med bzhin snang la bde sdug so sor spyod //
NK106(me)010:3606: gdod ma'i 'od gsal nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang las /
NK106(me)010:3607: 'dzin byed kun du rtog pa'i bag la nyal sprin dang 'dra ba glo bur du langs pa las /
NK106(me)010:3608: 'khor ba'i snang ba sprul pa ltar med pa gsal snang du shar te /
NK106(me)010:3610: thog ma'i 'od gsal snying po las //
NK106(me)010:3611: mtshungs ldan ma rig snying po byung //
NK106(me)010:3613: zo chu bzhin te brgyud mar 'khor //
NK106(me)010:3615: sna tshogs 'khor bar chos su snang ba /
NK106(me)010:3616: 'di ni 'gro sems rang snang bag chags te //
NK106(me)010:3617: de nyid dag tshe khams la sku gsum dang //
NK106(me)010:3618: 'od gsal ye shes rang snang rang shar bas //
NK106(me)010:3619: sems dang ye shes rang snang rnam gnyis su //
NK106(me)010:3620: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i lung las gsung de bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3621: 'khor ba pa'i sems can la gang ci snang ba
NK106(me)010:3622: dang shar ba thams cad ni sems kyi rang snang
NK106(me)010:3623: / sangs rgyas la sku dang ye shes dang zhing
NK106(me)010:3624: dag pa gang ci shar ba thams cad ni ye
NK106(me)010:3625: shes kyi rang snang ba ste /
NK106(me)010:3627: sems can sangs rgyas chos so cog /
NK106(me)010:3628: sems dang ye shes rang snang nyid //
NK106(me)010:3630: sems la snang ba'i gzugs la sogs pa phyi rol
NK106(me)010:3631: gyi snang yul rnams ni thog ma med pa'i dus
NK106(me)010:3632: kyi bag chags brtas pa tsam las /
NK106(me)010:3633: sems dang gzhan du grub pa med de sprul pa lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:3635: rnam shes kyi tshogs gang yin /
NK106(me)010:3636: kun gzhi rnam shes yin na phyi rol du mi snang bar 'gyur /
NK106(me)010:3637: kha nang bltas kho na'i rang bzhin du gnas la /
NK106(me)010:3638: sems ni kun gzhi'i rnam par shes //
NK106(me)010:3639: ngar 'dzin pa ni yid bzhin no //
NK106(me)010:3641: mig shes la sogs lnga ni kha phyir bltas yin yang /
NK106(me)010:3642: yul 'dzin byed du dus der skyes pas blo rdzas
NK106(me)010:3643: gcig po'i ngang dus na gzung yul ma yin no
NK106(me)010:3644: // yid shes dang nyon yid ma yin te dbang
NK106(me)010:3645: po gzugs can dngas pa la snang ba'i phyir ro
NK106(me)010:3646: // // sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig po'i nang tshan kyang ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:3647: gzugs la sogs pa sgo lnga'i yul sems ma yin par shes so //
NK106(me)010:3649: gdod ma'i dbyings ni kun gyi 'byung gnas te //
NK106(me)010:3650: rig pas dri ma dag tshe ye shes dang //
NK106(me)010:3651: ma rig bdag 'dzin 'khrul pas sems snang du //
NK106(me)010:3652: 'gro drug bde sdug sprul pa lta bur snang //
NK106(me)010:3653: dbyings gcig las rang ngo shes pas ye shes rang snang ba dang /
NK106(me)010:3654: ma shes pas 'khrul pa'i rang snang 'khrul pa ltar shar ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:3655: sprul pa dang 'dra ba'i 'thad pa dgod pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3656: ji ltar sprul pa gzhi med las byung ba //
NK106(me)010:3657: de ltar 'khrul snang gzhi med dag par shes //
NK106(me)010:3658: ji ltar sprul pa sems la dbang bsgyur ltar //
NK106(me)010:3659: de bzhin sna tshogs 'gro sems goms par shes //
NK106(me)010:3660: ji ltar sprul pa gang 'dod der snang bas //
NK106(me)010:3661: de ltar chos kun rgyu rkyen dag las shes //
NK106(me)010:3662: ji ltar sprul pa med snang 'khrul pa ltar //
NK106(me)010:3663: de bzhin chos kun sems snang 'khrul pa'i blo //
NK106(me)010:3664: rang snang rang shar rang sems rab 'jug dbang //
NK106(me)010:3665: ji ltar goms pa de ltar snang ba yin //
NK106(me)010:3666: sprul pa ni shing bu rde'u la sogs pa'i dngos can gyi rdzas med kyang /
NK106(me)010:3667: gzhi med las snang ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:3668: 'khrul snang yang rkyen tsam las rang rgyu nyon mongs
NK106(me)010:3669: ma grub pa las shar ba'i phyir gzhi rtsa med
NK106(me)010:3670: pa'o // sprul pa ni sems la dbang bsgyur thob
NK106(me)010:3671: pa dag gis gang bsams su der snang ba ltar
NK106(me)010:3672: pa'o // / 'khrul snang 'di yang sems la bag
NK106(me)010:3673: chags goms pa'i dbang gis shar bas dngos po med
NK106(me)010:3674: pa'o // / pa'o // sprul pa ni rang dbang
NK106(me)010:3675: thob pa des gang 'dod pa de ston nus pa
NK106(me)010:3677: yang rgyu dang rkyen las de'i 'bras bu tha dad
NK106(me)010:3678: pa 'char bas bden pa med pa'o //
NK106(me)010:3680: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung /
NK106(me)010:3681: de rgyu de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs //
NK106(me)010:3683: sprul pa ni 'khrul snang du snang ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:3684: chos 'di dag kyang sems snang glo bur ba'i stong gzugs te /
NK106(me)010:3688: gzugs las kyang stong pa nyid gzhan ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:3689: stong pa nyid las kyang gzugs gzhan ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:3690: de bzhin du tshor ba dang /
NK106(me)010:3693: rnam par shes pa rnams kyang stong pa'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:3694: mdor na chos su snang ba thams cad rang snang du rang shar ba yin la /
NK106(me)010:3695: khyad par du 'khrul snang thams cad rang sems la
NK106(me)010:3696: bag chags tha dad du goms pa'i dbang gis snang
NK106(me)010:3697: ba las / phyi nang gang na'ang ma grub pa'i phyir med pa gsal bar snang ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:3698: da ni 'khrul snang rtogs tshul dang sbyar na /
NK106(me)010:3699: gang yang ma goms ji bzhin nyid bzhag na //
NK106(me)010:3700: gar yang mi 'khrul rang bzhin gzhi la gnas //
NK106(me)010:3701: sngon bzhin sems nyid dbyings su 'ub chub bo //
NK106(me)010:3702: 'khrul snang thams cad yid la byed pa ring du goms pa las byung bar shes nas /
NK106(me)010:3703: rnal 'byor pas gang yid la mi byed pa rang sangs zang ka rjen par gnas dus /
NK106(me)010:3704: gar yang mi 'khrul ba'i rig pa stong pa gzhi thog tu gnas pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3705: bum pa chag pa'i nam mkha' dbye ba med par 'dres pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:3706: dus gsum dus med gcig tu rtogs pas sngon thog gdod ma'i zad par thug ste /
NK106(me)010:3707: nang dbyings ka dag chen por 'ub chub pa'o //
NK106(me)010:3708: 'di la gnyis su med pa'i ye shes su brda
NK106(me)010:3709: rtogs te chos sku dag pa nyis ldan gyi ngo
NK106(me)010:3710: bor krong nger bzhugs pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:3711: spring yig bdud rtsi'i thigs pa las /
NK106(me)010:3712: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK106(me)010:3713: mar la mar ni rjes zhugs ltar //
NK106(me)010:3714: shes bya spros bral de nyid dang //
NK106(me)010:3715: dbyer med ye shes rnam 'dres pas //
NK106(me)010:3716: de nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK106(me)010:3717: rang bzhin chos sku zhes byar brjod //
NK106(me)010:3720: ji ltar lan tsh+wa chu la thim pa ltar //
NK106(me)010:3721: de bzhin sems ni rang bzhin la thim 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:3723: sems la gang shar rang babs khyab gdal du bzhag pa yang /
NK106(me)010:3724: dug gsum dug lnga kun rtog las byung ba //
NK106(me)010:3725: kun du dpyad na gang du'ang mi gnas pas //
NK106(me)010:3726: nyon mongs sprul 'dra ngo bo med pas na //
NK106(me)010:3727: ma skyes stong pa'i ngang la ji bzhin zhog /
NK106(me)010:3728: dug lnga'i kun du rtog pa de dag kyang //
NK106(me)010:3729: brtag cing dpyad na phyi nang gang du'ang mi rnyed la ngo bo ngos gzung ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3730: rang bzhin sprul pa lta bur bzhag pas rang tshugs
NK106(me)010:3731: mi thub par grol nas 'gro ba ni sems kyi
NK106(me)010:3733: de nyid ma shes nas spangs kyang je mang la 'gro zhing /
NK106(me)010:3734: spang gnyen gyi gzeb tu 'ching ba yin te /
NK106(me)010:3736: nyon mongs rnams ni gzugs sogs la med dbang sogs la med de dag par na'ang med //
NK106(me)010:3737: ces pa la sogs pa dang /
NK106(me)010:3738: sems kyi gsang 'di ma shes na //
NK106(me)010:3739: bde thob sdug bsngal gzhom 'dod kyang //
NK106(me)010:3740: de dag don med gyi nar 'khyam //
NK106(me)010:3742: snang srid snod bcud skye 'gro ji snyed kyi //
NK106(me)010:3743: lus dang longs spyod 'gro 'dug bde sdug kun //
NK106(me)010:3744: med snang sprul pa dang 'dra rang bzhin med //
NK106(me)010:3745: skye med 'gag med 'ong med 'gro ba med //
NK106(me)010:3746: 'pho med 'gyur med 'on kyang sna tshogs snang //
NK106(me)010:3747: de bas sprul pa dngos zhes rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:3748: sprul pa de yang bsam gtan bsgrub pa'i cho 'phrul las //
NK106(me)010:3749: ngo bo rig pa'i rang rtsal du ma 'gyur yang sna tshogs su 'gyur 'gyur 'dra ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:3750: rang snang rdul phran las ma 'gyur yang che chung
NK106(me)010:3751: la sogs pa du mar 'gyur 'gyur 'dra ba dang
NK106(me)010:3752: / shing gcig las ma 'gyur kyang bzo tha dad pas rnam par 'gyur 'gyur 'dra ba nas /
NK106(me)010:3754: yul snang gi dngos po thams cad sa chu me rlung gi rdzas las ma 'gyur kyang /
NK106(me)010:3755: bzo la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis 'gyur 'gyur 'dra yang /
NK106(me)010:3756: snang tshod la ltos nas kyang dang po'i rtsom gzhi
NK106(me)010:3757: rang rang gi rdul rdzas de las log par 'gyur
NK106(me)010:3758: ba med cing / dpyad na gang du'ang ma grub par /
NK106(me)010:3759: gshis 'gyur med chen por gnas te /
NK106(me)010:3760: 'di ltar chos thams cad rang rang gi rgyu dang rkyen gyis tha dad par sprul pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3761: sprul pa dngos su rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3763: lha'i bu chos thams cad ni 'ong ba dang 'gro
NK106(me)010:3764: ba med pa'i phyir sprul pa lta bu'o zhes so
NK106(me)010:3765: // de yang snang brnyan tsam du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3766: sems kyi 'khrul rtog zug rngu ci snyed pa //
NK106(me)010:3767: de kun sprul pa lta bu'i ngang can te //
NK106(me)010:3768: rang bzhin med la snang ba ma 'gags pa //
NK106(me)010:3769: bden stong gnyis su med ces rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:3770: sems la dgag sgrub tu shar ba de la'ang snang la ngo bo med pa ste /
NK106(me)010:3771: yul dang blo gnyis gang du'ang med pa de /
NK106(me)010:3772: gnyis nas 'char 'char 'dra yang 'char ba dang 'char mkhan gnyis su med pas /
NK106(me)010:3773: 'char gzhi'i rang mdangs ngos zin pa tsam du bya'o //
NK106(me)010:3775: 'byung lnga snod dang srid gsum bcud dang ni //
NK106(me)010:3776: dgag sgrub ma lus sems kyis sprul pa ste //
NK106(me)010:3777: sems kyang med snang sgyu ma'i sprul pa ru //
NK106(me)010:3778: rang bzhin gdod nas dag par rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:3779: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba lnga'i rang gzugs dang /
NK106(me)010:3780: nang bcud sems can gyi kun tu rtog pa dang bcas pa thams cad /
NK106(me)010:3781: sems kyi steng du bag chags bzhag pa las shar ba'i sprul pa ste /
NK106(me)010:3782: sems de yang dpyad na rig pa'i rang rtsal du snang ba'i 'char tshul tsam las /
NK106(me)010:3783: ngo bo ngos gzung gang du'ang ma grub pas /
NK106(me)010:3784: dbyings nam mkha' lta bur rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3786: 'od srungs sems 'di ni phyi rol na yang rjes su mi mthong /
NK106(me)010:3787: nang na yang rjes su mi mthong /
NK106(me)010:3788: de gnyis ka'i bar na yang rjes su mi mthong ste /
NK106(me)010:3789: kun tu btsal na med cing mi dmigs so zhes so //
NK106(me)010:3790: rtogs par snang ba ngo bo nyid kyis ma grub par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3791: mi shes byis pas rtog dang log par snang //
NK106(me)010:3792: blos bkod dngos snang mtshan ma'i chos rnams kun //
NK106(me)010:3793: bag chags nyid las don du grub pa med //
NK106(me)010:3794: de bas 'di zhes gzung 'dzin ma byed par //
NK106(me)010:3795: thams cad mtha' grol brjod 'das shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:3796: tshu rol mthong ba byis pa'i so so skye bo
NK106(me)010:3797: rnams la snang ba dang rtog pa thams cad 'khrul
NK106(me)010:3798: pa yin te / bdag tu 'dzin sems dang de
NK106(me)010:3799: la bag chags brtas pa'i snang ba yin pa'i phyir
NK106(me)010:3800: pa yin te / ro // lang kar gshegs pa las /
NK106(me)010:3801: don yod ma yin sems nyid de //
NK106(me)010:3802: bag chags kyis ni dkrugs pa'i sems //
NK106(me)010:3803: don du rab tu snang ba 'byung //
NK106(me)010:3805: de'i phyir blo thams cad kun rdzob la de'i yul du ji ltar bkod kyang /
NK106(me)010:3806: kun rdzob las logs su ma grub ste /
NK106(me)010:3807: rtsig logs dang ras la ji ltar bris kyang ras
NK106(me)010:3808: bris dang rtsis ris las gzhan du med pa bzhin
NK106(me)010:3810: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK106(me)010:3811: blo ni kun rdzob yin par brjod //
NK106(me)010:3813: byis pa rnams kyi kun rdzob ni de kho na nyid la sgrib pa'i dri ma yin te /
NK106(me)010:3815: gti mug rang bzhin sgrib phyir kun rdzob ste //
NK106(me)010:3816: des gang bcos ma bden par snang de ni //
NK106(me)010:3817: kun rdzob bden zhes thub pa des gsungs te /
NK106(me)010:3819: de'i phyir blos brtags pa thams cad rtog pa'i dra ba yin pas spangs la /
NK106(me)010:3820: yin min blo las 'das pa mtha' bral nam mkha' lta bur rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3822: chos thams cad ming tsam brda tsam rtog pa tsam /
NK106(me)010:3823: gang rtog pa de ni yang dag pa ma yin te /
NK106(me)010:3824: de bzhin nyid ni rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba lags so zhes so //
NK106(me)010:3825: brjod med bsam yul 'das par la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3826: chos kun 'di zhes brjod cing mtshon byas kyang //
NK106(me)010:3827: nam mkha'i ming dang ri bong rwa 'dra bar //
NK106(me)010:3828: dngos med gshis las ma grub rtag pa tsam //
NK106(me)010:3829: ye stong rtsa ba bral bar shes par bya //
NK106(me)010:3830: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin la dpyad na /
NK106(me)010:3831: gang du'ang ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3832: tshig gis mtshon yang don rang mtshan ma yin pa nyid kyis /
NK106(me)010:3833: ming tsam spu ris 'dzin pa las /
NK106(me)010:3834: don dngos su mi mjal te /
NK106(me)010:3835: nam mkha'i ming dang ri bong gi rwa zhes brjod pa lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:3837: nam mkha' yang ni ming tsam mo //
NK106(me)010:3839: de phyir chos so cog tu snang dus nas ye
NK106(me)010:3840: stong rtsa ba bral ba'i rang gzugs snang ba tsam
NK106(me)010:3842: snang brtags thams cad blo 'das chen por la bzla ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3843: rtog pas brtags na blo yin don la med //
NK106(me)010:3844: don du snang de bag chags med snang yin //
NK106(me)010:3845: yul med yul 'dzin med pas gzung 'dzin med //
NK106(me)010:3846: smra med bsam med brjod med mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)010:3847: de la 'di zhes sus kyang mtshon med pas //
NK106(me)010:3848: ye nas bdag med sprul pa lta bur shes //
NK106(me)010:3849: gang rtog pas brtags pa de rang gi blo yin la /
NK106(me)010:3850: blo'i yul du ci snang ba thams cad bag chags 'khrul pa'i snang ba yin la /
NK106(me)010:3851: de yang med snang stong pa yin pas mtha' bral sprul pa lta bur shes par bya /
NK106(me)010:3852: de ltar na sangs rgyas sprul sku yang 'khrul snang yin nam zhe na /
NK106(me)010:3853: rang ngo ni gang du'ang ma grub pas 'khrul par ma grub la /
NK106(me)010:3854: sems can la snang cha sems can de'i bzang rtog gi las kyis 'khrul snang bzang 'khrul tsam ste /
NK106(me)010:3856: ji ltar bee d+aur sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK106(me)010:3857: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK106(me)010:3858: de bzhin 'gro sems sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK106(me)010:3859: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK106(me)010:3860: 'gro bar 'char nub so sor snang ba ni //
NK106(me)010:3861: rnyog pa'i rang sems rab 'jug dbang gis 'jug /
NK106(me)010:3863: ji ltar lha yi rnga sgra de //
NK106(me)010:3864: lha rnams rang bzhin las las byung //
NK106(me)010:3865: de ltar thub pa zhi ba'i chos //
NK106(me)010:3866: gsungs pa rang gi las las byung //
NK106(me)010:3868: de ltar chos thams cad sprul pa ltar bstan pa yang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK106(me)010:3869: ji ltar sprul pa snang ba'i dus nas stong //
NK106(me)010:3870: de ltar chos kun gang snang bden pas stong //
NK106(me)010:3871: ji ltar sprul pa yod med mtha' las 'das //
NK106(me)010:3872: de ltar chos kun rang bzhin dmigs bsam 'das //
NK106(me)010:3873: sprul pa ni snang bzhin pa'i dus nas stong pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:3874: chos thams cad kyang stong pa'o //
NK106(me)010:3875: sprul pa ni dpyad na yod med kyi mtha' las 'das pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:3876: chos thams cad mtha' las 'das te /
NK106(me)010:3877: snang la rang bzhin med pa sprul pa ltar bstan te /
NK106(me)010:3878: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK106(me)010:3879: 'jam dpal sprul pa ni snang la yod pa ma yin no //
NK106(me)010:3880: de bzhin du chos thams cad snang la yod pa ma yin no zhes so //
NK106(me)010:3881: sprul pa lta bur snang ba las /
NK106(me)010:3882: sprul par yang grub pa med de 'di ltar /
NK106(me)010:3883: snang mod stong mod bden mod rdzun yin mod //
NK106(me)010:3884: gang ltar btags kyang bden pa 'ga' med pas //
NK106(me)010:3885: 'di zhes ma 'dzin phyogs yan chen por ltos //
NK106(me)010:3887: bden rdzun la sogs pa'i ming cir btags kyang /
NK106(me)010:3888: don la grub pa med pas phyogs zhen grub matha'i ra ba las brgal te /
NK106(me)010:3889: mtha' bral klong yangs chen por rtogs par bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3891: stong ngo zhes kyang brjod gyur la //
NK106(me)010:3892: mi stong zhes kyang brjod gyur kyang //
NK106(me)010:3893: stong dang mi stong la sogs zhi //
NK106(me)010:3894: zhi ba 'di la ga la yod //
NK106(me)010:3896: sangs rgyas rnams kyis bdag dang ni /
NK106(me)010:3897: bdag med 'gag med ces kyang bstan //
NK106(me)010:3899: mthar 'dzin med na kun yin gtad med chen por bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3900: 'dzin zhen med na gang yin yin du chug /
NK106(me)010:3901: tshig tsam mtshon la dgag sgrub ci byar yod //
NK106(me)010:3902: gang la'ang bden zhen gyi mthar 'dzin med na gang
NK106(me)010:3903: ltar rtogs kyang brda shes pa'i yan lag tsam las
NK106(me)010:3904: / don bden med stong par grub zin pa'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:3905: tshig gi phyogs la rtsod pa don med pas /
NK106(me)010:3908: rtogs par gyur na thams cad de yin te //
NK106(me)010:3909: de las gzhan zhig sus kyang shes mi 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:3911: zhen 'dzin yod na mthon por rtogs kyang rang thog tu mi phebs te /
NK106(me)010:3912: 'di zhes 'dzin na gang yang gnas lugs min //
NK106(me)010:3913: yid dpyod rtog pa'i dra bas ci zhig mtshon //
NK106(me)010:3914: sems kyis brtags pa rang gi rtog pa ste //
NK106(me)010:3915: de yis don dam stong nyid mtshon byas kyang //
NK106(me)010:3916: mthar 'dzin nyid las gnas lugs ga la yin //
NK106(me)010:3917: stong pa nyid do zhes pa la sogs pa'i 'dzin
NK106(me)010:3918: pa yod kyang rang gi rtog pas der rtog pa
NK106(me)010:3919: las / stong pa rnal ma ma yin te 'dzin pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:3921: rtog pa kha brgyud pa'i phyir 'gro ba so sor 'phen pa ste /
NK106(me)010:3922: de dang bral na mya ngan las 'das par yang /
NK106(me)010:3924: rnam par rtog pa ma gtogs pa //
NK106(me)010:3925: 'khor ba zhes bya ci yang med //
NK106(me)010:3926: rnam rtog de dang bral bas na //
NK106(me)010:3927: khyod ni rtag tu mya ngan 'das //
NK106(me)010:3929: stong pa'o snyam pa las stong pa mtshon pas skyon med ces pa'ang mi 'thad par bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:3930: 'on kyang mtshon te shes par byed ce yang //
NK106(me)010:3931: mtshan mtshon 'das la ci zhig mtshon du yod //
NK106(me)010:3932: de bas don med rtsod pa'i zhen 'dzin gyis //
NK106(me)010:3933: sems nyid mi rtogs yid dpyod pho tshod tsam //
NK106(me)010:3934: stong par blos gzhal ba'i stong pa des sems nyid
NK106(me)010:3935: kyi rang ngo'i stong pa gshis kyi don dam de
NK106(me)010:3936: ma rtogs te / gshis kyi ngo bo la mtshan mtshon thams cad las 'das pa /
NK106(me)010:3937: rtog pa med pa yin la /
NK106(me)010:3938: blos gzhal de yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i pho tshod spom
NK106(me)010:3939: yor po rgyus med pa'i yul yid la 'jal ba'o
NK106(me)010:3940: // long ba bshad bzang pos gzugs kyi dbye ba mjal ba dang 'dra ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:3941: 'o na gang gis rtogs she na /
NK106(me)010:3942: bla ma'i byin rlabs gang gi snying zhugs pa //
NK106(me)010:3943: sprin bral mkha' la nyi shar dag pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:3944: nam zhig nus ldan rten 'brel thabs kyis 'char //
NK106(me)010:3945: de tshe dam pa'i don de mngon du 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:3946: blos ma rtogs pho tshod dang bral ba'i stong pa gshis kyi gnas lugs ni /
NK106(me)010:3947: rig pa'i ngo bo bsam brjod dang bral ba yin la /
NK106(me)010:3948: de rang gi rgyud la 'char ba ni /
NK106(me)010:3951: dbang ngam ngo sprod la sogs pa'i skabs su brda
NK106(me)010:3952: dang rten 'brel bzang pos rig pa stong gsal zang
NK106(me)010:3953: kar yod pa rang shes te /
NK106(me)010:3955: bla ma'i dus thabs bsten pa dang //
NK106(me)010:3956: rang gi bsod nams las shes bya //
NK106(me)010:3959: bla mas smras pa gang gi snying zhugs pa //
NK106(me)010:3960: lag pa'i mthil na gnas pa'i gter mthong 'dra //
NK106(me)010:3962: de ji lta bu zhe na /
NK106(me)010:3963: thams cad phyam gcig yin min dpyad ra med //
NK106(me)010:3964: mkha' mnyam mtha' grol ngang stong zang ka ma //
NK106(me)010:3965: yangs la snang stong sprul pa'i rang bzhin du //
NK106(me)010:3966: chos rnams thams cad ngang gis rtogs par 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:3967: gshis rtogs pa'i tshe yul snang thams cad phyal pa bar med sprul pa ltar sang seng /
NK106(me)010:3968: rig pa rang sangs rjes med zang ka /
NK106(me)010:3969: phyi nang bar med dpyad ra zhig pa'i snang bar 'char te /
NK106(me)010:3972: yangs phyal phyal ba zhig tu 'char ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:3974: mdun dang rgyab dang phyogs bcu ru //
NK106(me)010:3975: gang gang mthong ba de de nyid //
NK106(me)010:3976: de ring mgon po nga ltar 'khrul pa chad //
NK106(me)010:3977: da ni su la yang 'dri bar mi bya'o //
NK106(me)010:3979: 'khor 'das rig par grol ba blo bde ngang gis shar ba yang /
NK106(me)010:3980: 'khor ba gang yin 'khrul rtog sems nyid 'di //
NK106(me)010:3981: rtogs par gyur na ye yin mya ngan 'das //
NK106(me)010:3982: 'dzin med rig pa'i ye shes yul la 'phyo //
NK106(me)010:3983: gang snang dgos med der 'dzin mi 'jug pa //
NK106(me)010:3984: snang sems sprul pa'i ngang der blo bde rnyed //
NK106(me)010:3985: 'khor ba kun du rtog pa'i rang bzhin 'di med
NK106(me)010:3986: snang ba stong pa'i rang 'gros su rtogs na mya
NK106(me)010:3987: ngan las 'das pa rang shar du snang bas /
NK106(me)010:3988: dran snang yul med stong par grol te /
NK106(me)010:3989: gnyis med ye snang ba 'phyo ba zhes bya ste /
NK106(me)010:3991: sems kyi mkha' la yid kyi dal 'phyo ba //
NK106(me)010:3992: sgyu ma'i 'gros te ye shes khyab gdal ba'o //
NK106(me)010:3995: 'di ltar rtogs na bden mthong ye shes pa //
NK106(me)010:3996: gzhan zhig mtshon du med de de rang nyid //
NK106(me)010:3997: rang shar rang sar grol ba'i chos nyid do //
NK106(me)010:3998: rig stong zang ka'i rtog pa de nyid dam dam dbyings kyi bden pa mthong ba ste /
NK106(me)010:3999: phyis nas goms pa'i nyams skye ba las /
NK106(me)010:4000: rtogs pa'i ngo bo de nas lhag tu rtogs byar
NK106(me)010:4001: med de zad pa'i dgongs pa mthong ba'i phyir ro
NK106(me)010:4003: gang gi chos mthong ba de ni 'phel ba'am 'grib pa med pas nam mkha' lta bu'o zhes so //
NK106(me)010:4004: byin gyis brlabs las rtogs pa de nyid gzhan skal
NK106(me)010:4005: pa med pa dag la mtshon yang go spyi las
NK106(me)010:4006: / rang gis rtogs pa 'dra ba mi 'char ro zhes bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:4007: thabs stong bla ma'i byin rlabs snying zhugs pa //
NK106(me)010:4008: gang la mngon du gyur yang gzhan du min //
NK106(me)010:4009: mig ldan gzugs snang sgron me 'bar gyur pa //
NK106(me)010:4010: dmus long dag la bstan pas mthong ngam ci //
NK106(me)010:4011: mig dang ldan pa la mar me 'bar ba de dmus long la bstan yang mi mthong ba ltar /
NK106(me)010:4012: skal ba dang ldan pa la rtogs pa shar ba
NK106(me)010:4013: de skal pa chung ba rnams la brda dang thabs
NK106(me)010:4014: ji lta bur mtshon kyang yid dpyod las rang gi
NK106(me)010:4015: rtogs pa ci 'dra ba mi mthong ngo //
NK106(me)010:4016: de yang bla ma'i mos gus mchog las skye ba yin te /
NK106(me)010:4018: rang byung rnams kyi don dam de //
NK106(me)010:4019: dad pa nyid kyis rtogs bya yin //
NK106(me)010:4021: mig med pas ni mi mthong ngo //
NK106(me)010:4023: thos pa dang mi ldan pa rnams dang /
NK106(me)010:4024: ldan yang kun du rtog pas 'chel ba rnams la /
NK106(me)010:4025: de kho na nyid rtogs pa da res kyi tshe 'dir med do zhes bshad pa /
NK106(me)010:4026: tshig kyang mi shes don kyang mi go ba //
NK106(me)010:4027: gang gis legs pa'i nyi ma mi mthong ba //
NK106(me)010:4028: de bas blun po'i skye bo gzhan dag ni //
NK106(me)010:4029: ne tso'i 'don pa 'dra zhing rlom pas khengs //
NK106(me)010:4030: rtog pa'i dra bas snying po'i don ma mjal //
NK106(me)010:4031: de nyid mi shes dmus long gzugs mjal 'dra //
NK106(me)010:4032: rtogs pa'i dus med yid dpyod bden par 'dzin //
NK106(me)010:4033: e ma gzu lums shin tu skal pa ngan //
NK106(me)010:4034: snying po'i don la nam yang ma re zhig /
NK106(me)010:4035: sngon yang legs par bshad pa'i nor gyis dben pa /
NK106(me)010:4036: 'dir yang mchog tu blun pa'i blo gros su gyur pa rnams dang /
NK106(me)010:4037: rtog pa'i dra ba la don du zhen pa'i ne tso dang 'dra ba dag gis /
NK106(me)010:4038: sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i don mthong ba'i skal ba med de /
NK106(me)010:4039: gcig ni blun sgom yid dpyod la /
NK106(me)010:4040: don du zhen pa'i phyir dang /
NK106(me)010:4041: cig shos ni yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i mthar lhung ba'i phyir te /
NK106(me)010:4042: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rje'i zhal snga nas /
NK106(me)010:4043: yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i lta ba nyon re mongs //
NK106(me)010:4044: de la brten pa'i bsgom pa yi re mug /
NK106(me)010:4045: de la 'bras bu re ba yang re 'khrul //
NK106(me)010:4047: rang gi phyogs la de kho na nyid rtogs pa 'thad pa dang bcas pas basngagasa pa ni /
NK106(me)010:4048: 'dir ni sems nyid dam pa'i ye shes ni //
NK106(me)010:4049: bla mas bstan pa rang rig ye shes dngos //
NK106(me)010:4050: rang sems bcos bslad med par bzhag na 'char //
NK106(me)010:4051: re dogs 'dzin zhen med na mngon pa ste //
NK106(me)010:4052: stong gsal mtha' dbus med na legs kyang mngon //
NK106(me)010:4053: de bas brgyud pa'i byin rlabs dang ldan pa //
NK106(me)010:4054: dam pa'i bla mas zin pa mchog tu gces //
NK106(me)010:4055: so so rang gi ye shes ni rtag par gnas kyang ngo ma shes pa de /
NK106(me)010:4056: bla mas bstan pa'i dus 'dir mngon du mthong bas nges par byas pa de yang /
NK106(me)010:4057: phyis nas sems kyi ngo bo ji bzhin du bzhag pa tsam gyis 'char te /
NK106(me)010:4058: de tshe yul dang sems su snang yang 'dzin zhen med pa'i ngo bo la mngon pa ste /
NK106(me)010:4059: rig pa stong gsal phyam gdal ba ngang gis shar ba'i tshe /
NK106(me)010:4060: sngon bas kyang gsal bar mngon pa ni bla ma dam pa'i drin las byung ba na /
NK106(me)010:4061: brgyud pa dang bla ma shin tu bzang ba zhig la thug pa kho na gal che ste /
NK106(me)010:4063: de phyir brgyud par ldan pa'i byin rlabs lngas byung ba //
NK106(me)010:4064: de yang rje btsun mthu yis nges par rtogs par bya //
NK106(me)010:4067: bdag dang gzhan du bral ba'i ston mkhan rin chen mdzod //
NK106(me)010:4068: sman pa'i rgyal po de ni g.yo med gus pas bsten //
NK106(me)010:4071: bla ma mkhas pa dag la rtag tu brten par bya //
NK106(me)010:4072: ci phyir zhe na mkhas pa'i yon tan de las 'byung //
NK106(me)010:4074: lam ji ltar bsgom pa ni /
NK106(me)010:4075: gnas lugs don la yeng med bsgom pa yang //
NK106(me)010:4076: sngon 'gro sngar bzhin bla ma'i rnal 'byor la //
NK106(me)010:4077: sprul pa 'byong bar gsol gdab dngos gzhi ni //
NK106(me)010:4078: sems ni sprul pa lta bu'i rang bzhin la //
NK106(me)010:4079: sems la snang 'adi'ang rang bzhin sprul pa 'dra //
NK106(me)010:4080: thams cad ma skyes sprul 'drar thag bcad nas //
NK106(me)010:4081: sems ni dran bsam tshol khro bral bar gzhag /
NK106(me)010:4082: bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgoms la chos thams cad sprul
NK106(me)010:4083: pa ltar 'byong bar mdzad du gsol zhes pa'i gsol
NK106(me)010:4084: ba btab nas / sems dang sems la snang ba'i
NK106(me)010:4085: chos thams cad sprul ba lta bur shes pa'i ngang
NK106(me)010:4086: la dran rtog yid la byed pa gang yang mi
NK106(me)010:4088: de tshe stong gsal spros dang bral ba yi //
NK106(me)010:4089: ngang la gnas pas g.yo byed gzung 'dzin bral //
NK106(me)010:4090: dngas gsal sprul pa lta bu'i 'od gsal 'char //
NK106(me)010:4091: snang yul ma 'gags der 'dzin bcos bslad med //
NK106(me)010:4092: sal le sing nge ma yengs ngang gis bde //
NK106(me)010:4093: gsal la mi rtog nam mkha' lta bu'i sems //
NK106(me)010:4094: rang bzhin spros dang bral ba'i ngo bo mthong //
NK106(me)010:4095: de tshe chos rnams sprul pa lta bu la //
NK106(me)010:4096: blo yi rnam pa'ang sprul pa lta bur grol //
NK106(me)010:4097: chags sdang re dogs bdag 'dzin sprul pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:4098: gzhi grol lam grol 'bras bu grol ba yin //
NK106(me)010:4099: sprul pa lta bu'i sems kyi 'phro 'du thams cad nub ste /
NK106(me)010:4100: sprul par 'dzin pa yang med pa'i ngang de ni
NK106(me)010:4101: g.yo byed gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i ye shes te
NK106(me)010:4102: / snang yul snang yang nger 'dzin gyi dpyad ra med pas /
NK106(me)010:4103: yul dang yul can der rtag pa'i gzung 'dzin thams cad dang bral zhing /
NK106(me)010:4104: rig pa dngas la snang ba thams cad gsal stong
NK106(me)010:4105: 'dzin med du rang snang bas sprul pa lta bu
NK106(me)010:4106: ste / sal le ba'i rig pa /
NK106(me)010:4107: rang gsal du ngo shes pa'i ngang la gnas pas /
NK106(me)010:4108: lus sems bde ba'i rang dus de nam mkha' 'dra ba'i 'od gsal te /
NK106(me)010:4109: spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'i ngo bo mthong ba'o //
NK106(me)010:4110: de tshe chos su snang ngo cog sprul pa lta bur shar bas /
NK106(me)010:4111: chos su 'dzin pa ngang gis grol te /
NK106(me)010:4112: dug lnga dang re dogs gang yang med pas /
NK106(me)010:4113: de dag gi gnyen po gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos
NK106(me)010:4114: su 'dzin pa'ang rang log pa'i phyir phyi gzung ba
NK106(me)010:4115: nang 'dzin pa ste gzung ba gang zag gis bdag
NK106(me)010:4116: la grol ba dang mnyam du /
NK106(me)010:4117: gnyen po lam du blang byar 'dzin pa med pas
NK106(me)010:4118: chos kyi bdag kyang shugs las med par rtogs te
NK106(me)010:4119: / bdag med gnyis rtogs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' zhes bya ba yin no //
NK106(me)010:4120: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa la 'ching zhen gyi gol sa gang yang med pas /
NK106(me)010:4121: phyogs yan du bstan pa ni /
NK106(me)010:4122: gang ltar bsgoms kyang de yis mi 'ching ste //
NK106(me)010:4123: yod par bsgoms kyang rtag pa'i mtha' las grol //
NK106(me)010:4124: med par bsgoms kyang chad pa'i dri ma bral //
NK106(me)010:4125: gnyis su bsgoms kyang gnyis med ngang der gnas //
NK106(me)010:4126: bdag tu bsgoms kyang bdag 'dzin 'ching ba med //
NK106(me)010:4127: gzhan du bsgoms kyang re dogs gnyis bcas med //
NK106(me)010:4128: bskyed par bsgoms kyang rdzogs par lhun grub cing //
NK106(me)010:4129: rdzogs rim bsgoms kyang sprul pa'i bskyed rim 'grub //
NK106(me)010:4130: rig pa zang ka bcos bslad med pa'i don mthong nas /
NK106(me)010:4131: las dang rnam par smin pa la sogs pa'i chos
NK106(me)010:4132: su yang nges snyam du bsgoms kyang rtag pa'i mthar
NK106(me)010:4133: mi ltung ste rig pa gzhi med du mthong ba'i
NK106(me)010:4134: phyir dang / snang srid kyi chos thams cad rtsa
NK106(me)010:4135: ba med par bsgoms kyang chad pa'i mthar mi ltung
NK106(me)010:4136: phyir dang / ste / rig par rang gsal du mthong ba'i phyir dang /
NK106(me)010:4137: snang ba dang shes pa lha dang gzhal yas khang
NK106(me)010:4138: la sogs pa gnyis bcas su bsgoms kyang gnyis 'dzin
NK106(me)010:4140: rang dus de nas rang rig gi ngo bo gnyis med du mthong ba'i phyir dang /
NK106(me)010:4141: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa bde bar gshegs
NK106(me)010:4142: pa'i snying po lhun grub 'dus ma byas ye nas
NK106(me)010:4143: grub pa'i bdag nyid dam pa'i 'od gsal bsgoms kyang
NK106(me)010:4144: mu stegs kyi bdag ltar ngar 'dzin du mi ltung
NK106(me)010:4145: ste / rang rig gi ngo bo stong gsal lhun grub chen por mthong ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:4146: 'khor ba'i 'khrul snang dag bya dri ma'i rnam pa
NK106(me)010:4147: can la sogs pa gzhan du bsgoms kyang re dogs
NK106(me)010:4148: gnyis bcas su mi ltung ste /
NK106(me)010:4149: rig pa'i ngo bo la dri ma ye nas yod ma myong bar mthong ba'i phyir te /
NK106(me)010:4151: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK106(me)010:4152: gzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK106(me)010:4153: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK106(me)010:4154: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK106(me)010:4156: bskyed rim lha sku zhal phyag dang bcas pa bsgoms kyang /
NK106(me)010:4157: bsgom dus de nyid las dmigs bcas su mi ltung ste /
NK106(me)010:4158: rig pa'i ngo bo stong gsal mtshan ma med pa mthong ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:4159: rdzogs rim snang bcas phra mo'i rnal 'byor dang snang
NK106(me)010:4160: med nam mkha' lta bur bsgoms kyang stong pa'i mthar
NK106(me)010:4161: mi ltung ste / rig pa'i ngo bo la rang
NK106(me)010:4162: gsal zang ka'i ngo bo ma spangs yongs rdzogs chen
NK106(me)010:4163: po'i snang ba lhun grub tu mthong ba'i phyir ro
NK106(me)010:4164: mi ltung ste / // 'di dag ni rnal 'byor pa la gces pa'i chings gal po che'o //
NK106(me)010:4165: de ltar rtogs pa'i tshe na /
NK106(me)010:4166: shar grol dus mnyam nyon mongs kun las grol //
NK106(me)010:4167: 'dzin rtog las 'das rnal ma'i ngang nyid der //
NK106(me)010:4168: dus gsum dus med chos nyid 'khor lo la //
NK106(me)010:4169: thun mtshams ris med sprul pa lta bur spyod //
NK106(me)010:4170: sprul pa'i skye bo ltar snang la rjes med stong par gnas pas /
NK106(me)010:4171: rnal 'byor pa de yang lus yod pa snyom yang
NK106(me)010:4172: stong pa zang ma tsam las gdos bcas su 'dzin
NK106(me)010:4174: shes pa zang thal rjen par bud nas /
NK106(me)010:4175: sems shar sa nas rang yal gtad med du phyam phyam grol te /
NK106(me)010:4176: snga phyi ris med kyi rig pa rang gsal zang kar rtag tu shar bas /
NK106(me)010:4177: thun mtshams res med du song ste dus gsum mnyam
NK106(me)010:4178: pa nyid du rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa zhes bya
NK106(me)010:4180: dus gsum dus med rtogs pa po //
NK106(me)010:4182: de tshe rnal 'byor pa de yang //
NK106(me)010:4183: gtad med smyon pa 'dzin med zang ka ma //
NK106(me)010:4184: shugs 'byung rang kar re dogs bcos bslad med //
NK106(me)010:4185: gang yin kun yin gtad med phyam gcig pa //
NK106(me)010:4186: nam mkha' rab 'byams dgongs pa lhun gyis grub //
NK106(me)010:4187: shes pa gtad 'dzin dang bral bas bya ba'i khrigs chags bud nas /
NK106(me)010:4188: shugs 'byung rang shar gyi snang ba la thad drang
NK106(me)010:4189: du spyod pa ni smyon pa khrog langs pa lta
NK106(me)010:4190: bu ste / dgongs pa ni phyogs yan nam mkha' ltar mngon du gyur pa'i dus so //
NK106(me)010:4191: 'bras bu ni gtad med kyi snang ba 'dzin med du shar ba /
NK106(me)010:4192: de tshe nyin mtshan sprul pa'i ngang gnas pas //
NK106(me)010:4193: bde chen 'khor lor bde klong gcig tu 'khyil //
NK106(me)010:4194: longs spyod 'khor lor rnam kun longs spyod rdzogs //
NK106(me)010:4195: chos kyi 'khor lo chos nyid rgyun chad med //
NK106(me)010:4196: sprul pa'i 'khor lor rnam sprul dpag tu med //
NK106(me)010:4197: bde skyong 'khor lor nyin mtshan bde bas skyong //
NK106(me)010:4198: ma sbyangs bzhin du rlung sems gnad du tshud //
NK106(me)010:4199: sbyang gzhi sbyang bya sbyong byed rtsa 'dab rlung //
NK106(me)010:4200: ye shes ro gcig sbyangs 'bras mngon du 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:4201: de la 'khrul pa'i lus sems khegs pa'i dus 'dir /
NK106(me)010:4202: de dag gi rten 'brel 'grigs pa las yon tan 'char ba yang /
NK106(me)010:4203: rtsol ba can bskyed rim gyi rnal 'byor la gtso
NK106(me)010:4204: bor byed pa dag rtsa rlung rags pa'i lam du
NK106(me)010:4205: byed la / rtsol bral rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK106(me)010:4206: kha cig phra mo'i rnal 'byor las mi rtog pa
NK106(me)010:4207: skyes pa nyid kyis sbyong rtsol shas chung ba lam
NK106(me)010:4208: byed la / du byed la / dbang po yang
NK106(me)010:4209: rab rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa dag ni
NK106(me)010:4210: rig pa'i ngo bo rtogs pa la dbang bsgyur bas
NK106(me)010:4211: byed la / du byed la / / bya rtsol
NK106(me)010:4212: med pa lam du byed pa las 'dir rig ngo
NK106(me)010:4213: bya rtsol med pa skyong bas rtsa rlung gnad du
NK106(me)010:4214: 'chings nas de dag gi yon tan zhor la 'char
NK106(me)010:4215: byed la / du byed la / / ba yin
NK106(me)010:4216: no // de la tshogs gnyis bsags pa las rtsa
NK106(me)010:4217: rlung las su rung nas yon tan 'char te byang
NK106(me)010:4218: chub sems dpa' lam lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:4219: sbyangs pas gnad du tshud de yon tan 'char ba thun mong ba lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:4220: bya rtsol med pas rtsa rlung gi yon tan 'char ba rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:4221: de yang rten rtsa dang rlung ni 'dug stangs la sogs pas sbyangs la /
NK106(me)010:4222: rlung ni sems kyi bzhon pa lta bu yin la /
NK106(me)010:4223: khams ni longs spyod ltar dga' ba ster ba las /
NK106(me)010:4224: rtsol bcas pa rnams rlung rta dang 'dra ba sbyangs pas /
NK106(me)010:4225: sems de la zhon pa'i mi dang 'dra ba rang
NK106(me)010:4226: dbang du byed do zhes mi rta yul khams gzhan
NK106(me)010:4227: du don gnyer ba la dpe byas te /
NK106(me)010:4228: rta'i kha lo sgyur ba ltar 'khor lo bzhi dang
NK106(me)010:4229: gtso mo gsum gyi gnas su rtsol bas dbang sgyur
NK106(me)010:4232: 'dir mi 'chun po che rang gi stan las ma g.yos par don rnams lhun gyis grub pa ltar /
NK106(me)010:4233: rig pa rang sa zin pa'i ngang las mi g.yo
NK106(me)010:4234: ba na rtsa rlung dang mi'i sems gnyis dang bral
NK106(me)010:4235: te rnam rtog 'phro 'du bde bar zhi nas /
NK106(me)010:4236: chos nyid rang sa'i ngang las ma g.yos par /
NK106(me)010:4237: rtsarlunga las su rung ba'i yon tan ma btsal lhun gyis grub rdzogs pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:4238: de phyir thun mong gi theg pa rnams blon 'bangs rtsol bas don bsgrubs pa dang 'dra la /
NK106(me)010:4239: thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa rang bzhin rdzogs
NK106(me)010:4240: pa chen po ba rnams rgyal po 'bad rtsol med
NK106(me)010:4241: par don kun lhun grub tu 'byung ba lta bu'o
NK106(me)010:4242: // de la rig pa rang sa zin pa las
NK106(me)010:4243: mi g.yo bas sems dang de'i rta rlung gnyis 'ching
NK106(me)010:4244: ste yon tan gyi 'char tshul yang /
NK106(me)010:4245: spyi bo bde chen gyi 'khor lo'i rlung sems las su rung bas sbyang gzhi rig pa'i steng du /
NK106(me)010:4246: sbyang bya 'dod chags kyi 'dzin rtog dag nas /
NK106(me)010:4247: sbyangs 'bras chos nyid kyi 'khor lo rang bzhin lhun
NK106(me)010:4248: grub kyi bsam gtan bde ba chen po'i ngang la
NK106(me)010:4250: yang mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo'i rlung sems las su rung bas sbyang gzhi rig pa la /
NK106(me)010:4251: sbyang bya zhe sdang gi rtog pa dag nas /
NK106(me)010:4252: sbyangs 'bras 'du ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyi longs spyod lhun grub tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4253: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rlung sems las su rung bas sbyang gzhi rig pa la /
NK106(me)010:4254: sbyang bya gti mug dag nas /
NK106(me)010:4255: sbyangs 'bras 'od gsal bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngo bo lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4256: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i rlung sems las su rung bas sbyang gzhi rig pa'i steng du /
NK106(me)010:4257: sbyangs bya nga rgyal phrag dog la sogs pa'i 'dzin rtog dag nas /
NK106(me)010:4258: sbyangs 'bras rdzu 'phrul dang sprul pa dang las bzhi'i phrin las 'grub pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4259: de dag thams cad kyi sbyang gzhi rig pa'i steng du /
NK106(me)010:4260: sbyong byed rang ngo shes la 'dzin pas ma bslad pa'i don goms pas /
NK106(me)010:4261: sbyang bya so so'i dri ma dag nas /
NK106(me)010:4262: sbyangs 'bras rig pa gtan srid zin nas gnas skabs
NK106(me)010:4263: dang mthar thug gi yon tan rdzogs par 'char ba
NK106(me)010:4264: yin no // de dag kyang yid bzhin bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK106(me)010:4265: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i mtha' //
NK106(me)010:4266: chos rnams rang sar bzhag pa ste //
NK106(me)010:4267: ye grol cog gzhag nyid la thug /
NK106(me)010:4268: dgongs pa blo las 'das pa dang //
NK106(me)010:4269: stong dang dngos po'i mtha' zad du //
NK106(me)010:4270: dgu zad rtog pa med pa dang //
NK106(me)010:4271: mtshan bcas rang sar grol ba'o //
NK106(me)010:4272: ma sbyangs lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK106(me)010:4273: yon tan rnams ni ngang gis rdzogs //
NK106(me)010:4275: de tshe rmi lam sprul bsgyur zhing khams mthong ba dang //
NK106(me)010:4276: phyis nas 'khrul pa'i rmi lam rgyun chad de //
NK106(me)010:4277: 'od gsal ba la nyin dang mtshan mo gnas //
NK106(me)010:4278: bde gsal mi rtog ting 'dzin ngang gnas shing //
NK106(me)010:4279: spyan dang mngon shes rdzu 'phrul yon tan 'grub //
NK106(me)010:4280: nyams rtogs tshad med rang gzhan don gnyis 'grub //
NK106(me)010:4281: de phyir chos kun sprul pa'i rang bzhin du //
NK106(me)010:4282: skal bzang rnams kyis rtag tu don sgoms shig /
NK106(me)010:4283: mtshan mo seng ge'i nyal lugs kyis dbu ma gsal
NK106(me)010:4284: ba'i 'khor lo bzhir brtan g.yo ba'i 'jig rten dang
NK106(me)010:4285: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi zhing khams chud pa las
NK106(me)010:4286: / khyad par du mgrin pa'i 'khor lo na 'khor
NK106(me)010:4287: 'das kyi chos thams cad sprul pa ltar bsams la
NK106(me)010:4288: / nyal bas / rmi lam zin nas sprul bsgyur la sogs pa 'grub cing /
NK106(me)010:4289: spyan dang mngon par shes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:4290: ting nge 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul 'grub cing 'od gsal gyi ngang la rtag tu gnas la /
NK106(me)010:4291: sa lam gyi rang bzhin bgrod nas /
NK106(me)010:4292: mthar thug kun tu bzang po byang chub mchog gi go 'phang thob par 'gyur te /
NK106(me)010:4294: de la rnal 'byor skal chen po //
NK106(me)010:4295: bsam med yid la mi byed pas //
NK106(me)010:4296: rang bzhin lhun gyis rdzogs pa yi //
NK106(me)010:4299: mi 'gyur mnyam pa chen po'i ngang nyid las //
NK106(me)010:4300: mi g.yo spros dang bral ba'i byang chub sems //
NK106(me)010:4301: mi rtog rang byung ye shes don mthong nas //
NK106(me)010:4302: mi gnas gdod ma'i gnas su phyin par shog /
NK106(me)010:4303: zhi ba rdul bral yon tan rdzogs pa'i gtso //
NK106(me)010:4304: 'od gsal mkha' dbyings nyi ma shar ba bzhin //
NK106(me)010:4305: rang gzhan gti mug mun pa kun bsal nas //
NK106(me)010:4306: 'gro kun mig gcig thar gling snang byed shog /
NK106(me)010:4307: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso las /
NK106(me)010:4308: sprul pa lta bu'i le'u ste rdo rje'i gnas brgyad pa'i 'grel pa'o ////
NK106(me)010:4309: da ni bstan bcos yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don bstan pa las /
NK106(me)010:4310: brjod bya'i don gang gis gtan la phab pa'i don ngos gzung ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4311: de ltar rgyal bas yongs su bstan pa'i chos /
NK106(me)010:4312: sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad nyid du rig bya'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:4313: rgyud lung man ngag snying po'i bcud bsdus te //
NK106(me)010:4314: dri med 'od zer shar bas snang bar byas //
NK106(me)010:4315: de la sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis mdo
NK106(me)010:4316: dang rgyud sde'i chos kyi phung po ji snyed cig
NK106(me)010:4317: gsungs kyang so so rang gi rig pa dang /
NK106(me)010:4318: de'i ngo bor snang ba sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad las chos lhag pa ma gsungs te /
NK106(me)010:4320: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:4321: mya ngan las 'das pa de yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu'o //
NK106(me)010:4322: mya ngan las 'das pa las chos lhag pa'i chos
NK106(me)010:4323: shig yod na de yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu
NK106(me)010:4324: ma lta bu'o zhes pa dang /
NK106(me)010:4325: rtsa ba shes rab las kyang /
NK106(me)010:4326: rmi lam ji bzhin sgyu ma bzhin //
NK106(me)010:4327: dri za'i grong khyer ji bzhin du //
NK106(me)010:4328: de bzhin skye dang de bzhin gnas //
NK106(me)010:4329: de bzhin du ni 'gags pa'ang gsungs //
NK106(me)010:4331: de dag gi don yang so so rang gi rig pa dang /
NK106(me)010:4332: de la snang ba'i chos rnams kun rdzob tu sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad du bstan pa yang /
NK106(me)010:4333: ji ltar snang bzhin pa'i dus nas don dam pa'i chos nyid skye 'gag dang bral bar bstan te /
NK106(me)010:4334: rig pa ni don dam pa'i bden pa nam mkha'
NK106(me)010:4335: dang 'dra ba'i ngang na 'khor 'das kyi chos sgyu
NK106(me)010:4336: ma'i dpe brgyad kyis bsdus pa rnams sprin dang 'ja'
NK106(me)010:4337: tshon ltar snang ba na kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK106(me)010:4338: ste / de dag kyang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung
NK106(me)010:4339: ba 'gag pa la sogs pa rnam pa brgyad kyi
NK106(me)010:4340: ngo bo dang 'brel ba 'grub pa'i don te /
NK106(me)010:4341: 'dzam bu'i gling na gdugs zla med pa'i slob dpon
NK106(me)010:4342: chen po 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa'i dbu
NK106(me)010:4343: ma rtsa ba'i shes rab las /
NK106(me)010:4345: 'gag pa med pa skye med pa //
NK106(me)010:4346: chad pa med pa rtag med pa //
NK106(me)010:4348: tha dad don min don gcig min //
NK106(me)010:4349: spros pa nyer zhi zhir bstan pa //
NK106(me)010:4350: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas smra rnams kyi //
NK106(me)010:4351: dam pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK106(me)010:4353: rig pa dang de'i ngo bo na snang ba'i chos
NK106(me)010:4354: bden pa gnyis kyi rang bzhin gtan la 'bebs pa'i
NK106(me)010:4355: tshul 'di ni dpag tu med pa'i bskal pa nas
NK106(me)010:4356: bla na med pa'i sgo'i chos kyi theg pa la
NK106(me)010:4357: sbyangs pas / 'dir yang tshul khrims kyi nam mkha'
NK106(me)010:4358: rdul dang bral ba las blo gros kyi nyi ma
NK106(me)010:4359: tshad med pa'i 'od zer stong mngon par 'phro bas
NK106(me)010:4360: sbyangs pas / / bskal pa mchog gis gdul bya rnams kyi ma rig mun pa sel zhing /
NK106(me)010:4361: dam chos kyi pad tshal rab tu rgyas par byed pa des snang bar byas pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:4362: dge ba byang chub tu bsngo ba las /
NK106(me)010:4363: skye dgu thams cad thar pa dam pa'i chos la spyod par bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4364: dge ba de yis ma lus 'gro ba kun //
NK106(me)010:4365: chos rnams ma skyes sgyu ma'i tshul mthong nas /
NK106(me)010:4366: gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i chos bsgrubs te /
