NK106(me)010:4367: rgyal ba'i sku gsum 'byor pas mdzes par shog /
NK106(me)010:4368: chos kyi sgo bla na med pa legs par phye
NK106(me)010:4369: ba'i dge ba phul du phyin pa de la brten
NK106(me)010:4370: nas / nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa'i sems can thams cad thar pa dam pa'i lam du zhugs te /
NK106(me)010:4371: chos thams cad sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad du snang bcas bsod nams kyi tshogs bsgrub cing /
NK106(me)010:4372: rig pa nam mkha' 'dra ba'i don la bsgom pa snang med ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs nas /
NK106(me)010:4373: sa dang lam gyi yon tan mthar phyin pa sangs
NK106(me)010:4374: rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par shog cig ces pa
NK106(me)010:4375: ste / rigs pa drug cu pa las /
NK106(me)010:4376: dge ba 'di yis skye bo kun //
NK106(me)010:4377: bsod nams ye shes tshogs bsags te //
NK106(me)010:4378: bsod nams ye shes las byung ba'i //
NK106(me)010:4379: dam pa gnyis ni thob par shog /
NK106(me)010:4381: lam gyi gegs med par bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4382: rmi lam sgyu ma smig rgyu gzugs brnyan dang //
NK106(me)010:4383: brag ca sprul pa lta bu'i chos rnams la //
NK106(me)010:4384: bden par zhen pa'i blo ni rab spangs te //
NK106(me)010:4385: ye shes yon tan gdod ma'i sar phyin shog /
NK106(me)010:4386: lam gyi gegs ni gshis kyis ngo ma shes pas /
NK106(me)010:4387: thun mong gi snang ba ngan pa rnams dang /
NK106(me)010:4388: lam gyi nyams phra mo rnams la bden par zhen pa las /
NK106(me)010:4389: bdud kyi las dang gegs 'jug pas /
NK106(me)010:4390: bden med du rtogs nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK106(me)010:4391: sku dang ye shes thob par shog cig ces pa
NK106(me)010:4393: gang tshe blta bar 'dod pa dang //
NK106(me)010:4395: mgon po 'jam dbyangs de nyid ni //
NK106(me)010:4396: gegs med par yang mthong bar shog /
NK106(me)010:4398: blta ba ni ting nge 'dzin la mnyam gzhag gi cha'o //
NK106(me)010:4399: 'dri ba ni shes rab lhag mthong gi don no //
NK106(me)010:4400: zhi lhag gi lam des 'jam dpal mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas te /
NK106(me)010:4401: de thob pa la gegs med pa la smon pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4403: byang chub sems dpa' la ni bdud yod par 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)010:4404: byang chub sems dpa' la la ni bdud med par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs pa'i don yang /
NK106(me)010:4406: gang shes rab dang brtson pa mchog dang ldan pa rnams la ni /
NK106(me)010:4407: bdud med bdud kyis glags rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK106(me)010:4409: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa nam mkha' ltar mthong ba'i phyir /
NK106(me)010:4410: bdud du bya ba gang yang mi dmigs so //
NK106(me)010:4411: gang shes rab chung la brtson 'grus dang ldan pa
NK106(me)010:4412: rnams la ni bdud kyis bar du gcod par 'gyur
NK106(me)010:4413: te / gang chos thams cad la bdag tu mngon par zhen nas brtson pa'i phyir ro //
NK106(me)010:4414: gang mi brtson pa la ni bdud 'jug par mi 'gyur te /
NK106(me)010:4415: de nyid bdud kyi las yin pa'i phyir ro zhes so //
NK106(me)010:4416: rnam g.yeng dang 'du 'dzi zhi bar bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4417: byis pa 'du 'dzi'i grong dang nyon mongs kyis //
NK106(me)010:4418: yongs gang srid pa'i nags khrod thibs po las //
NK106(me)010:4419: rgyang ring 'phags pa'i dga' tshal der song ste //
NK106(me)010:4420: dpag med lha brgya'i gtsug na mdzes gyur cig /
NK106(me)010:4422: grong khyer dang mtshungs pa'i dgon pa dag na 'dul bar dka' ba'i byis pa dang /
NK106(me)010:4423: rtsod pa'i gzhi nor rdzas dang /
NK106(me)010:4424: rkyen nyon mongs pa mang bas thar pa 'dod pa dag gis /
NK106(me)010:4425: 'phags pa dga' ba'i nags tshal rab tu dben par song ste /
NK106(me)010:4426: bsam gtan gyi don la bsgoms nas sa dang lam gyi yon tan 'grub pa na /
NK106(me)010:4427: dus dus su lha'i tshogs 'du ba dag la legs
NK106(me)010:4428: par 'doms pa de dag gis gtsug gi nor bu
NK106(me)010:4429: byed par gyur cig ces pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4431: byis dang skal pa mnyam spyod na //
NK106(me)010:4433: skal mi mnyam par 'khrid byed na //
NK106(me)010:4434: byis pa bsten pas ci zhig bya //
NK106(me)010:4435: skad cig gis ni mdzar 'gyur la //
NK106(me)010:4436: yud tsam cig gis dgrar yang 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:4437: dga' ba'i gnas la khro byed pa'i //
NK106(me)010:4438: so so skye bo mgu bar dka' //
NK106(me)010:4439: phan par smras na khro bar byed //
NK106(me)010:4440: bdag kyang phan las zlog par byed //
NK106(me)010:4441: de dag ngag ni mi nyan na //
NK106(me)010:4443: mtho la phrag dog mnyam la 'gran //
NK106(me)010:4444: dma' la nga rgyal bstod na dregs //
NK106(me)010:4445: mi snyan brjod na khong khro ste //
NK106(me)010:4446: nam zhig byis la phan par 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:4448: gcig pu mngon par gnas pa'i don du bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4449: bdag gi sems 'di rnam g.yeng la skyo bas //
NK106(me)010:4450: zhi ba'i nags nang dben zhing nyams dga' bar //
NK106(me)010:4451: gcig pu zab mo'i de nyid rnam bsgom zhing //
NK106(me)010:4452: 'phags pa'i blo mig dag pa thob par shog /
NK106(me)010:4453: spyir 'khrul snang sgyu ma dang 'dra ba la zhen pa rnams 'khrul la /
NK106(me)010:4454: khyad par 'jig rten gyi chos brgyad bslu ba'i sgyu
NK106(me)010:4455: mas kho bo thar pa bsgrub pa la dgos pa
NK106(me)010:4456: med pa'i phyir / gdul daka'i 'khor dang dus ngan gyi snang ba thams cad spangs la /
NK106(me)010:4457: gcig pu dben par gnas pas 'phags pa'i ye shes thob par gyur cig ces pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4459: bdag ni grol ba don gnyer la //
NK106(me)010:4460: rnyed dang bkur stis 'ching mi dgos //
NK106(me)010:4462: nags kyi yon tan la spro bas bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4463: nags rnams me tog lo ma 'bras mang zhing //
NK106(me)010:4464: chu gtsang dka' thub dpal gyis brgyan pa der //
NK106(me)010:4465: dal 'byor snying nor ldan pa'i lus 'di yis //
NK106(me)010:4466: don chen chos mdzod thar lam bgrod par shog /
NK106(me)010:4467: nags kyi nang rab tu dben pa /
NK106(me)010:4468: me tog dang 'bab chus brgyan pa /
NK106(me)010:4469: brag ri'i thel rnams zla ba chu shel gyis 'tsher ba'i phug dang /
NK106(me)010:4471: 'od ma'i ra bas bskor ba'i bsam gtan gyi gnas
NK106(me)010:4472: yid du 'ong ba de dag nyin par la rang
NK106(me)010:4473: dbang thob nas zhi gnas dang lhag mthong grub pa
NK106(me)010:4474: yid la byed pa des sa dang lam gyi them
NK106(me)010:4475: skas 'dzegs te thar pa chen po'i grong khyer du
NK106(me)010:4476: tshe 'di nyid la 'jug par shog cig ces pa'o
NK106(me)010:4478: nags na bya dang ri dgas dang //
NK106(me)010:4479: shing rnams mi snyan brjod mi byed //
NK106(me)010:4480: 'grogs na bde ba de dag dang //
NK106(me)010:4481: nam zhig bdag ni gnas par 'gyur //
NK106(me)010:4483: mthar gyis gzhan don la bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4484: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod bya'i phyir //
NK106(me)010:4485: mi yi srid par dge ba'i chos spyad de //
NK106(me)010:4486: zhi ba'i lam ldan yon tan tshogs mang bas //
NK106(me)010:4487: mtha' yas 'gro ba srid las sgrol bar shog /
NK106(me)010:4488: ding sang ni bdag gis phan pa mi 'grub pas gcug pu dben par gnas te /
NK106(me)010:4489: mi lus don yod par zhi ba'i chos rtse gcig spyad de /
NK106(me)010:4490: sangs rgyas pa na nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa'i sems can gyi don byed par shog cig ces so //
NK106(me)010:4491: dben pa la bskul ba'i gtam las /
NK106(me)010:4492: bdag gi tshig kyang mi rig par //
NK106(me)010:4493: gzhan la phan pa 'grub bo zhes //
NK106(me)010:4494: smra ba ji ltar smyon pa bzhin //
NK106(me)010:4495: de bas dben par gnas byas la //
NK106(me)010:4496: mthar gyis gzhan la phan bde bya //
NK106(me)010:4498: phyi rabs la gdams pa ni /
NK106(me)010:4499: tshul 'di zab mo'i chos kyi snying po ste //
NK106(me)010:4500: nges don gnad du dril ba'i lam yin pas //
NK106(me)010:4501: thar pa 'dod pas snying nas brtson bya zhing //
NK106(me)010:4502: nyin mtshan mi dal 'bad pas nyams su blangs //
NK106(me)010:4503: mdo rgyud kyi nges don gcig tu dril ba'i gnad yin pas /
NK106(me)010:4504: dad ldan rnams kyis le lo med par brtson pas nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK106(me)010:4505: yang nan tan du gdams pa /
NK106(me)010:4506: phyi rabs skal ldan dad dang ldan pa kun //
NK106(me)010:4507: yi ge 'di la rtag tu nan tan mdzod //
NK106(me)010:4508: rang gzhan srid pa'i rgya mtsho rab brgal nas //
NK106(me)010:4509: 'gro ba'i don gnyis lhun gyis grub par nges //
NK106(me)010:4510: rdo rje'i tshig gi gnas nges pa'i yi ge 'di la /
NK106(me)010:4511: skal ldan rnams kyis gces spras su mdzod cig pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4512: tshigs su bcad pa 'di gnyis kyis tshig dang don la spyi dang phyogs su gdams pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:4513: gang gis gang du gdams she na /
NK106(me)010:4514: mdo dang rgyud don man ngag snying po'i don //
NK106(me)010:4515: ma lus zab mo'i mig ldan rnal 'byor pa //
NK106(me)010:4516: dri med 'od zer snang bas brgyan pa des //
NK106(me)010:4517: gangs ri thod dkar mgul du legs par bkod //
NK106(me)010:4518: gsang sngags phyi nang gi rgyud dang man ngag gi
NK106(me)010:4519: gnas la lta ba'i blo gros kyis 'od zer 'phro
NK106(me)010:4520: ba des / ri'i rgyal po gangs ri thod dkar gyi mgul du legs par bkod pa yin no //
NK106(me)010:4521: ri de'i yon tan ni gnas la basngagasa pa rol mo'i dbyangs snyan du rtog par bya'o //
NK106(me)010:4522: bstan pa phyogs bcur rgyas pa'i bsngo ba ni /
NK106(me)010:4523: chos tshul nyi ma dri med 'od stong ldan //
NK106(me)010:4524: ye shes snang ldan ma rig mun sel gyis //
NK106(me)010:4525: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho rab tu skem byas te //
NK106(me)010:4526: thar gling snang bas phyogs bcur rgyas par shog /
NK106(me)010:4527: dus matha'i nyi ma 'od zer gyi dra ba 'bar
NK106(me)010:4528: ba'i rang bzhin dang mtshungs par chos kyi tshul rab
NK106(me)010:4529: tu 'bar zhing snang ba 'dis 'gro ba rnams kyi
NK106(me)010:4530: ma rig pa'i mun pa thams cad bsal te /
NK106(me)010:4531: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho bag chags dang bcas pa skem zhing /
NK106(me)010:4532: chos kyi tshul rmad du byung ba'i bstan pa thar
NK106(me)010:4533: gling snang ba'i sgron me 'bar ba phyogs kun du
NK106(me)010:4534: dar zhing rgyas par shog cig ces pa ni /
NK106(me)010:4535: gzugs can gyi gsal byed las shis pa brjod pa'i rgyan du brjod pa'o //
NK106(me)010:4536: de dag gis yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don bstan zin to //
NK106(me)010:4537: rang bzhin nye bar mdzes pa'i skyes bu la //
NK106(me)010:4538: sna tshogs rin chen rgyan gyis spras pa ltar //
NK106(me)010:4539: don zab rmad du byung ba'i chos tshul la //
NK106(me)010:4540: tshig don rnam bkra'i zab don 'grel 'di byas //
NK106(me)010:4541: dge ba 'di yis skye dgu'i 'jig rten du //
NK106(me)010:4542: bstan pa'i rgya mtsho yun ring gnas par shog /
NK106(me)010:4543: skyes bu mchog rnams sku tshe mtha' yas shing //
NK106(me)010:4544: chos rnga sgrogs pas 'jig rten mdzes gyur cig /
NK106(me)010:4545: rgyal khams kun tu rtag tu bde legs shog /
NK106(me)010:4546: dge dngos spyod pas thar pa'i lam zhugs te //
NK106(me)010:4547: gnas skabs mthar thug re ba rdzogs gyur nas //
NK106(me)010:4548: mgon po don gnyis 'byor pa mtha' yas shog /
NK106(me)010:4549: chos tshul rin chen srid gsum pad+mo'i gnyen //
NK106(me)010:4550: ma lus rang bzhin longs spyod rgyas pa yang //
NK106(me)010:4551: phyi ma'i mu mthar 'jig rten mig gyur te //
NK106(me)010:4552: 'dzam gling kun du dar zhing rgyas par shog //
NK106(me)010:4553: rdzogs pa chen po sgyu ma ngal gso'i 'grel pa shing rta bzang po zhes bya ba /
NK106(me)010:4554: bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung rab kyi gnas la mang du thos pa'i nor gyis phyug cing /
NK106(me)010:4555: nam mkha' ltar gos pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK106(me)010:4556: gyi sgo dang po thob nas theg pa mchog gi
NK106(me)010:4558: dpal u rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i zhabs
NK106(me)010:4559: kyis rjes su bzung ba'i rnal 'byor pa sna tshogs
NK106(me)010:4560: rang grol gyis gangs ri thod dkar gyi gnas u
NK106(me)010:4561: rgyan rdzong gi ri ngogs su sbyar ba rdzogs so
